# TODO: Translation updated at 2026-07-09 15:26

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:10
translate spanish d19a_f3d2bc65:

    # ER "...and that is why the soldiers need your presence there."
    ER "... y por eso los soldados necesitan tu presencia allí."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:11
translate spanish d19a_b0e21870:

    # ER "I hope you see my point, that we can not afford a delay, my Queen?"
    ER "Espero que entiendas mi postura: no podemos permitirnos una demora, mi Reina."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:14
translate spanish d19a_982c1f9d:

    # Q "Of course. Because the Sun and Moon themselves won't show up unless I am there to see to it..."
    Q "Por supuesto. Porque el Sol y la Luna no se dignarán a aparecer si no estoy yo allí para asegurarme..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:17
translate spanish d19a_60c1f3d8:

    # ER "My Queen, I am a simple man, but please do not speak such heresy in public. To suggest that this is not the case..."
    ER "Mi Reina, soy un hombre sencillo, pero le ruego que no pronuncie tales herejías en público. Sugerir que no es así..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:18
translate spanish d19a_bf7e9aeb:

    # "The man pauses, for a second, his expression clearly perturbed at the possibilities."
    "El hombre se detiene un instante, con la expresión claramente perturbada por las posibilidades."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:21
translate spanish d19a_0ec21e75:

    # ER "Anyway, this could turn into a significant territory loss in the area."
    ER "En cualquier caso, esto podría convertirse en una pérdida territorial significativa en la zona."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:24
translate spanish d19a_2444272e:

    # ER "There have been too many incidents. It is clear to me, at this point, that they do not intend to restrict their unnatural presence to the cover of the mist and the contaminated areas for much longer."
    ER "Ha habido demasiados incidentes. A estas alturas, me resulta evidente que no piensan restringir su presencia antinatural a la niebla y a las zonas contaminadas por mucho más tiempo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:27
translate spanish d19a_9af0440f:

    # ER "The Cairo outskirts might not be inhabitable to us..."
    ER "Las afueras de El Cairo quizás ya no sean habitables para nosotros..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:30
translate spanish d19a_e76a4c55:

    # ER "... But allowing them to expand their control is a potential strategic nightmare."
    ER "... Pero permitirles expandir su control sería una pesadilla estratégica."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:36
translate spanish d19a_05716ac7:

    # ER "My Queen, since the days you were elevated to the throne, there has never been a situation this volatile. If you do not act decisively, you might soon find your leadership and the primacy of Zeta put to the test."
    ER "Mi Reina, desde los días en que fue elevada al trono, jamás ha habido una situación tan volátil. Si no actúa con decisión, pronto podría ver su liderazgo y la primacía de Zeta puestos a prueba."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:37
translate spanish d19a_305ce6f6:

    # ER "A test that announces itself to be far greater than anything faced by your predecessor."
    ER "Una prueba que se perfila mucho mayor que cualquiera a la que se enfrentara su predecesor."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:38
translate spanish d19a_94a1b8a5:

    # ER "I ask you, my Queen, are you up to such a challenge?"
    ER "Le pregunto, mi Reina, ¿está a la altura de tal desafío?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:41
translate spanish d19a_f14998db:

    # Q "If I were not, would that not mean that you and your brethren have failed in preparing me for it?"
    Q "Si no lo estuviera, ¿no significaría eso que usted y sus hermanos han fallado en prepararme para ello?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:44
translate spanish d19a_f1721c39:

    # ER "..."
    ER "..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:46
translate spanish d19a_fb7d1b67:

    # ER "It would."
    ER "Así sería."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:49
translate spanish d19a_07267341:

    # ER "I will send word. The High Queen of Zeta, beloved by the Goddess Neith, will bless the troops' wit."
    ER "Enviaré el mensaje. La Gran Reina de Zeta, amada por la Diosa Neith, bendecirá el ingenio de las tropas."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:52
translate spanish d19a_763e4e5e:

    # ER "Tomorrow, I will venture to the outskirts and meet the legates in charge of the operation."
    ER "Mañana me aventuraré a las afueras y me reuniré con los legados a cargo de la operación."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:56
translate spanish d19a_b5847e90:

    # ER "You will hear from..."
    ER "Recibirás noticias de..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:57
translate spanish d19a_bdc61a01:

    # Q "..."
    Q "..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:60
translate spanish d19a_f1721c39_1:

    # ER "..."
    ER "..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:61
translate spanish d19a_deb3baf7:

    # Z "It seems I am too early."
    Z "Parece que he llegado demasiado pronto."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:62
translate spanish d19a_c9512b5a:

    # "Elder Radames turns towards you..."
    "El anciano Radames se gira hacia ti..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:65
translate spanish d19a_14d6a0dd:

    # ER "A happy accident, to be sure. I am pleased to have the chance to meet you."
    ER "Un feliz accidente, sin duda. Me complace tener la oportunidad de conocerle."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:66
translate spanish d19a_869ba695:

    # ER "You are Stalker [persistent.player_name], if I am not mistaken?"
    ER "¿Eres el Acechador [persistent.player_name], si no me equivoco?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:69
translate spanish d19a_2a9b1dd1:

    # ER "Your name is whispered in the halls of the Palace, lately. The favour of our divine ruler seems to elevate you to a high station."
    ER "Últimamente su nombre se susurra en los pasillos del Palacio. El favor que nuestra gobernante divina parece concederle lo eleva a una posición elevada."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:70
translate spanish d19a_063a44c3:

    # ER "A position of power, however volatile."
    ER "Una posición de poder, aunque volátil."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:73
translate spanish d19a_f51b72a9:

    # Z "Elder Radames, you are too kind. Your reputation dwarfs mine. It is not a secret that you are the most prominent of the Elders of Zeta."
    Z "Anciano Radames, es demasiado amable. Su reputación eclipsa la mía. No es un secreto que usted es el más prominente de los Ancianos de Zeta."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:76
translate spanish d19a_cfc93d89:

    # ER "A smooth talker too? I can see how our Queen might be intrigued by a man of such versatile talents, but you are mistaken."
    ER "¿También un buen orador? Entiendo cómo nuestra Reina podría sentirse intrigada por un hombre con talentos tan versátiles, pero se equivoca."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:77
translate spanish d19a_cb7a85fa:

    # ER "I am but one of many who dedicate their service and their life to the betterment and glory of Zeta and its Queen."
    ER "No soy más que uno de los muchos que dedican su servicio y su vida al engrandecimiento y la gloria de Zeta y de su Reina."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:80
translate spanish d19a_74a84479:

    # ER "...as, I am assured, do you. Even though the path you walk places you into a dependency from outside forces that might put your loyalties to the test."
    ER "...como, estoy seguro, también lo haces tú. Aunque el camino que recorres te coloca en una dependencia de fuerzas externas que podrían poner a prueba tus lealtades."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:81
translate spanish d19a_28eea2da:

    # ER "The very tools you use to ply your craft put you at odds with life, as I am sure you know. The tools are tolerated as a necessary evil, but for how long will that be justified or even viable?"
    ER "Las herramientas mismas que usa para ejercer su oficio lo ponen en contradicción con la vida, como bien sabe. Se toleran como un mal necesario, pero ¿cuánto tiempo será eso justificable o siquiera viable?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:82
translate spanish d19a_a7d6b75c:

    # ER "Tell me, Stalker [persistent.player_name], have you ever wondered what would happen to your profession if the Decayed no longer existed? Where would you go to keep your {i}engines{/i} running?"
    ER "Dígame, Acechador [persistent.player_name], ¿se ha preguntado alguna vez qué ocurriría con su profesión si los Decaídos dejaran de existir? ¿De dónde obtendría recursos para mantener sus {i}motores{/i} en marcha?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:83
translate spanish d19a_a83d492f:

    # "The distaste this man proves for even discussing a topic that clearly irks him, is evident in the manner in which his voice drops when he mentions the subject."
    "El disgusto que demuestra este hombre al hablar siquiera de un tema que claramente le irrita se hace evidente en la forma en que su voz se apaga al mencionarlo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:89
translate spanish d19a_90d7e13b:

    # Z "Elder Radames, the path of a Stalker can be shaped in many ways. Mine was forged on the anvil of the Academy, as a disciple to Zetan Stalkers."
    Z "Anciano Radames, el camino de un Acechador puede tomar muchas formas. El mío se forjó en el yunque de la Academia, como discípulo de los Acechadores de Zeta."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:90
translate spanish d19a_ec05d65e:

    # Z "Even so, my master taught me to adapt, to use all that was available to me, to stay true to my task and complete it by any means necessary."
    Z "Aun así, mi maestro me enseñó a adaptarme, a usar todo lo que estuviera a mi alcance, a mantenerme fiel a mi tarea y cumplirla por cualquier medio necesario."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:91
translate spanish d19a_2f9e7794:

    # Z "Should a day come when such means do not include a source of fuel, or the possibility to leverage what technology still comes to us by the quirks of fate, I shall pave my way by using what means are left to be used. Even the simplest of means will do."
    Z "Si llegara el día en que tales medios no incluyeran una fuente de combustible, o la posibilidad de aprovechar lo poco de tecnología que aún nos llega por caprichos del destino, me abriré camino con lo que quede. Incluso lo más simple servirá."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:94
translate spanish d19a_3b87dfb4:

    # ER "The natural way. Just like they used to, before our time."
    ER "El camino natural. Como solían hacerlo antes de nuestro tiempo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:95
translate spanish d19a_a602f292:

    # ER "I remember your master. He was a true Zetan, through and through. The thought occurs to me that he must have taught you the old ways. We will see..."
    ER "Recuerdo a tu maestro. Era un verdadero Zetano, de principio a fin. Se me ocurre que debió enseñarte los viejos métodos. Ya lo veremos..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:103
translate spanish d19a_abccc700:

    # Z "I don't see why it would happen. Old Cairo is uninhabitable to us anyway, and as long as the decayed are kept where they are..."
    Z "No veo por qué ocurriría. El Viejo Cairo es inhabitable para nosotros de todos modos, y mientras los Decaídos se mantengan donde están..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:106
translate spanish d19a_169a2f49:

    # ER "...and what if they won't be?"
    ER "... ¿y si no lo hacen?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:109
translate spanish d19a_c3b78367:

    # Z "The City has managed to keep them in check since before either of us was born."
    Z "La Ciudad ha logrado mantenerlos a raya desde antes de que cualquiera de nosotros naciera."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:112
translate spanish d19a_e2c4a0ae:

    # ER "The City has left this problem unchecked, to fester and grow like a malignant infection."
    ER "La Ciudad ha dejado este problema sin control, para que se pudra y crezca como una infección maligna."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:118
translate spanish d19a_0f96132f:

    # ER "But that is a matter for a different conversation."
    ER "Pero ese es un asunto para otra conversación."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:122
translate spanish d19a_cc7efe4a:

    # ER "A handshake. Here's to two righteous men working together. For the Queen."
    ER "Un apretón de manos. Brindemos por dos hombres rectos trabajando juntos. Por la Reina."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:125
translate spanish d19a_8e4fa43c:

    # Z "For the city."
    Z "Por la Ciudad."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:126
translate spanish d19a_ad229315:

    # ER "...and for the greater glory of the city of Zeta and the empire that will rise from it."
    ER "...y por la mayor gloria de la ciudad de Zeta y el imperio que de ella surgirá."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:129
translate spanish d19a_4f991e23:

    # ER "If our gracious Queen really does trust you the way everyone says she does, a time might come when your responsibilities will not be limited to murmuring your musings and suggestions in her ears in the privacy of her quarters."
    ER "Si nuestra bondadosa Reina realmente confía en ti como todos dicen, podría llegar el momento en que tus responsabilidades no se limiten a susurrar reflexiones y consejos en sus oídos en la privacidad de sus aposentos."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:130
translate spanish d19a_dfb965f7:

    # ER "You should be wary of this."
    ER "Debes tener cuidado con eso."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:133
translate spanish d19a_3f4dfa1a:

    # Z "I am."
    Z "Lo estoy."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:136
translate spanish d19a_a45698f0:

    # ER "Good. Then we shall have to trust the wisdom of the gods, who put a Stalker on her path."
    ER "Bien. Entonces tendremos que confiar en la sabiduría de los dioses, que pusieron a un Acechador en su camino."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:137
translate spanish d19a_e662090c:

    # ER "Who knows... It might even come to be that the many things you've seen, the contacts you have made, will turn into an advantage for the City."
    ER "Quién sabe... Puede que incluso las muchas cosas que has visto y los contactos que has hecho acaben convirtiéndose en una ventaja para la Ciudad."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:138
translate spanish d19a_be7c9de1:

    # ER "I shall be watching you, Stalker [persistent.player_name]."
    ER "Te estaré observando, Acechador [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:141
translate spanish d19a_f13ab4f0:

    # Z "Elder Radames."
    Z "Anciano Radames."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:144
translate spanish d19a_b308d5eb:

    # "He walks out..."
    "Se retira..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:147
translate spanish d19a_43183a48:

    # Q "Haaaaah....!!"
    Q "¡¡Haaaaah....!!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:148
translate spanish d19a_02ee72d1:

    # "She stretches with studied emphasis..."
    "Se estira con énfasis calculado..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:151
translate spanish d19a_ee79506b:

    # Q "Bless... the gods...!"
    Q "¡Benditos... sean los dioses...!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:154
translate spanish d19a_a1e1750c:

    # Q "{i}*yawns*{/i} another day is over..."
    Q "{i}*bostezo*{/i} otro día ha terminado..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:157
translate spanish d19a_9217753b:

    # Q "Guards, you can retire to the perimeter."
    Q "Guardias, pueden retirarse al perímetro."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:160
translate spanish d19a_03a5aa9f:

    # Q "And you, slaves, prepare the thermae. You will both attend to me."
    Q "Y vosotras, esclavas, preparad las termas. Ambas me atenderéis."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:163
translate spanish d19a_1b40c554:

    # "The guards and servants leave, giving you a brief moment of privacy..."
    "Los guardias y sirvientes se retiran, dándote un breve momento de privacidad..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:166
translate spanish d19a_b59f5ec7:

    # Q "You met Elder Radames. That was inevitable, I guess. Good timing... I was getting bored to death."
    Q "Conociste al Anciano Radames. Era inevitable, supongo. Bien sincronizado... me estaba muriendo de aburrimiento."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:167
translate spanish d19a_19d8516e:

    # Q "That said, you spoke truth about his reputation. Many a soldier would have paid for a private audience with the old man, or even just to shake his hand."
    Q "Dicho esto, tienes razón sobre su reputación. Más de un soldado habría pagado por una audiencia privada con el anciano, o simplemente por estrecharle la mano."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:170
translate spanish d19a_88f75c64:

    # Z "I'm an old man myself. We tend to be less impressionable, but from what I have heard, his reputation is well deserved."
    Z "Yo también soy un hombre viejo. Solemos ser menos impresionables, pero por lo que he oído, su reputación está bien ganada."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:173
translate spanish d19a_89f63253:

    # Z "The decayed must give him a serious headache. He made no mystery of where my dealings with them put me in his consideration."
    Z "Los Decaídos deben darle un fuerte dolor de cabeza. No hizo ningún misterio de lo que mis tratos con ellos significan en su consideración hacia mí."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:176
translate spanish d19a_9f3dd409:

    # "She looks into your eyes for a moment..."
    "Te mira a los ojos por un momento..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:179
translate spanish d19a_b0550bca:

    # Q "Of course. It's no secret he is a purist. But that does not mean he thinks you're working with the decayed. Give him time."
    Q "Por supuesto. No es un secreto que sea un purista. Pero eso no significa que crea que trabajas con los Decaídos. Dale tiempo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:182
translate spanish d19a_e40ddabc:

    # Z "If half of what they say about him is true, this wasn't an accidental encounter and he's had the time to ask around about me for a while now."
    Z "Si la mitad de lo que dicen de él es cierto, este no fue un encuentro accidental y ya ha tenido tiempo de preguntar sobre mí desde hace rato."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:187
translate spanish d19a_ec5ed7e2:

    # Q "Be that as it may, that's not necessarily a bad thing. Anyway, enough of that! I have had to think about politics for the whole day, and I am done with it."
    Q "Sea como sea, eso no es necesariamente algo malo. En fin, ¡basta ya! He tenido que pensar en política todo el día, y ya he acabado con eso."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:189
translate spanish d19a_d5b6bd80:

    # Q "Regarding your regular visits... I decided that there is little need for your continued help with menial tasks for now."
    Q "Respecto a tus visitas habituales... decidí que por ahora hay poca necesidad de tu ayuda en tareas menores."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:190
translate spanish d19a_99b12e16:

    # Q "I really appreciate your effort though, [persistent.player_name]."
    Q "Aun así, valoro mucho tu esfuerzo, [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:195
translate spanish d19a_f318ba69:

    # Q "I did however make progress with the Elder's location."
    Q "Sin embargo, he avanzado en la búsqueda de la ubicación del Anciano."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:198
translate spanish d19a_33ee3805:

    # Z "You did? That's good news. Let me hear it."
    Z "¿De veras? Es una buena noticia. Cuéntamelo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:201
translate spanish d19a_b9ffcfbb:

    # Q "I will, next time you and your [persistent.da] come to me."
    Q "Lo haré, la próxima vez que tú y tu [persistent.da] vengáis a verme."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:202
translate spanish d19a_5f431a52:

    # Q "The reason is, because I think it might be better if you took this one on together."
    Q "La razón es que creo que sería mejor que afrontéis esto juntos."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:205
translate spanish d19a_8de05760:

    # Z "I will let her know."
    Z "Se lo diré."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:208
translate spanish d19a_5a8cedd0:

    # Q "Whenever you're both ready, come to me."
    Q "Cuando ambos estéis listos, venid a mí."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:209
translate spanish d19a_54ee8d1c:

    # Q "From what I've gathered, you best prepare for a couple of days of travel..."
    Q "Por lo que he averiguado, será mejor que os preparéis para un par de días de viaje..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:214
translate spanish d19a_c6026f78:

    # Q "Let us focus perhaps... on what happened last time you were here...?"
    Q "Centrémonos quizás... ¿en lo que ocurrió la última vez que estuviste aquí...?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:217
translate spanish d19a_cc9c9f8e:

    # Z "Right... about that..."
    Z "Cierto... sobre eso..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:220
translate spanish d19a_0f1944c8:

    # Q "...!"
    Q "¡...!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:221
translate spanish d19a_4b7bf586:

    # "She leaps forward and gives you a quick, but aggressive kiss..."
    "Salta hacia ti y te da un beso rápido, pero agresivo..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:224
translate spanish d19a_da00ce85:

    # Q "Mh...."
    Q "Mh...."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:225
translate spanish d19a_5ab3574d:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:228
translate spanish d19a_1e573402:

    # Q "I..."
    Q "Yo..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:229
translate spanish d19a_6ce23221:

    # "She keeps kissing your lips..."
    "Sigue besándote..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:232
translate spanish d19a_37e1a390:

    # "...which you reciprocate, as you wrap your arms around her..."
    "... a lo que respondes, rodeándola con tus brazos..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:233
translate spanish d19a_5ab3574d_1:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:236
translate spanish d19a_2101e06b:

    # Q "Nh..."
    Q "Nh..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:239
translate spanish d19a_a50c13d5:

    # "You both enjoy the shortlived intimacy. She seems both more passionate and relaxed, this time around."
    "Ambos disfrutan de la fugaz intimidad. Esta vez ella parece más apasionada y también más relajada."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:242
translate spanish d19a_8f44e35f:

    # "You let go of each others lips..."
    "Separáis los labios..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:245
translate spanish d19a_8c5170d2:

    # Zw "That was a surprise."
    Zw "Eso fue una sorpresa."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:248
translate spanish d19a_f3f4140c:

    # Qw "It's just a thank you... for last night."
    Qw "Solo es un agradecimiento... por lo de anoche."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:251
translate spanish d19a_87367b5c:

    # Z "You're welcome."
    Z "De nada."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:254
translate spanish d19a_d3bcc9d3:

    # "She lets go, and moves towards her throne..."
    "Se aparta y se dirige hacia su trono..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:257
translate spanish d19a_c129ce23:

    # Q "Sadly... I don't have much time today. I am expecting guests, and you shouldn't stay too long if we want to avoid more rumors."
    Q "Por desgracia... hoy no tengo mucho tiempo. Estoy esperando invitados, y no deberías quedarte demasiado si queremos evitar más rumores."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:260
translate spanish d19a_8523a05d:

    # Z "Fair enough... but what did I come here for then, today?"
    Z "Está bien... pero entonces, ¿para qué vine hoy?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:263
translate spanish d19a_291af2b6:

    # Q "That was your decision, don't put that on me. That said, perhaps bring your [persistent.da] around, next time? I would like that."
    Q "Esa fue tu decisión, no me culpes a mí. Dicho esto, ¿por qué no traes a tu [persistent.da] la próxima vez? Me gustaría."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:266
translate spanish d19a_f1c7e3a8:

    # Q "Tell her that I have made progress with the Elder's location, and that I might have a new task for her."
    Q "Dile que he avanzado en la búsqueda de la ubicación del Anciano y que podría tener una nueva tarea para ella."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:267
translate spanish d19a_40c05e9e:

    # Q "In fact, it might be better if you took this one on together."
    Q "De hecho, puede que sea mejor que afrontéis esta tarea juntos."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:270
translate spanish d19a_91302a74:

    # Z "That's good news. I will let her know."
    Z "Es una buena noticia. Se lo diré."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:273
translate spanish d19a_5f34bc41:

    # Q "Yeah... from what I've gathered, it's going to be an exciting adventure."
    Q "Sí... por lo que he averiguado, será una aventura emocionante."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:274
translate spanish d19a_285f80f8:

    # Q "Anyway, whenever you're both ready, come to me. Prepare for at least a couple of days of travel..."
    Q "En fin, cuando estéis listos los dos, venid a mí. Preparaos para al menos un par de días de viaje..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:278
translate spanish d19a_c71ba421:

    # Q "Oh, and... don't keep your Queen waiting."
    Q "Ah, y... no hagas esperar a tu Reina."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:281
translate spanish d19a_1f309c68:

    # Q "I mean - You would not want me to complain about you to Elder Radames, would you?"
    Q "Quiero decir... no querrías que me quejara de ti al Anciano Radames, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:292
translate spanish d19b_910fccff:

    # Z "[S], I've got news about the Elder's text."
    Z "[S], tengo noticias sobre el texto del Anciano."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:293
translate spanish d19b_f07dc974:

    # S "Wait, what?"
    S "Espera, ¿qué?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:294
translate spanish d19b_97f86c5a:

    # "[S] quickly sits up, her interest clearly piqued..."
    "[S] se incorpora rápidamente, con el interés claramente despertado..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:297
translate spanish d19b_c90e3bf5:

    # S "Come on! Spill it!"
    S "¡Vamos! ¡Suéltalo!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:300
translate spanish d19b_84bf0e28:

    # S "What did she find out? Are we going somewhere?"
    S "¿Qué descubrió? ¿Vamos a algún sitio?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:303
translate spanish d19b_430156ee:

    # Z "I don't know any details, but she has made progress and has a new task for the both of us."
    Z "No sé los detalles, pero ha avanzado y tiene una nueva tarea para los dos."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:306
translate spanish d19b_4d4af19f:

    # S "She must have found a location for the hideout. Did she say how far away it is?"
    S "Debe haber encontrado la ubicación del escondite. ¿Dijo a qué distancia está?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:309
translate spanish d19b_f394ed01:

    # Z "She mentioned we would be away for at least two days, but considering the Elder had to reach his hideout by either camel or foot, I don't think we will be driving more than a couple hours."
    Z "Mencionó que estaríamos fuera al menos dos días, pero considerando que el Anciano tenía que llegar a su escondite en camello o a pie, no creo que tengamos que viajar en coche más de un par de horas."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:312
translate spanish d19b_1251b661:

    # S "Oh... that reminds me... I still haven't asked Mandisa to teach me about that crossbow."
    S "Oh... eso me recuerda... todavía no le he pedido a Mandisa que me enseñe sobre esa ballesta."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:315
translate spanish d19b_1de8289b:

    # S "What do you think? Do I have the time, or do we need to head out tomorrow?"
    S "¿Qué opinas? ¿Tengo tiempo, o tenemos que partir mañana?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:318
translate spanish d19b_3adadefa:

    # Z "No, no... we can let her wait a bit. I'm sure it won't hurt her, and the Elder is not going to be any deader."
    Z "No, no... podemos dejarla esperar un poco. Seguro que no le pasa nada, y el Anciano no va a estar más muerto."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:321
translate spanish d19b_73bdcb74:

    # S "I think I will go see Mandisa today, then. Maybe I'm lucky and she's free?"
    S "Creo que iré a ver a Mandisa hoy, entonces. ¿Quizás tenga suerte y esté libre?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:324
translate spanish d19b_88310737:

    # Z "{i}*chuckles*{/i} Why are you asking me? I don't know her schedule."
    Z "{i}*risilla*{/i} ¿Por qué me lo preguntas a mí? No conozco su horario."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:325
translate spanish d19b_532f3ce1:

    # Z "All I know is... she tends to keep busy."
    Z "Lo único que sé es... que suele estar ocupada."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:328
translate spanish d19b_98f4cc2e:

    # Z "Try it, see if you're lucky. Maybe she likes you well enough to make time for you anyway."
    Z "Inténtalo, a ver si tienes suerte. Quizá le gustes lo suficiente como para hacerte un hueco."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:331
translate spanish d19b_c19ac202:

    # "She smiles..."
    "Sonríe..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:334
translate spanish d19b_14924e89:

    # "One hour later..."
    "Una hora después..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:337
translate spanish d19b_14d84dd9:

    # S "Okay... I'm ready."
    S "Bien... estoy lista."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:345
translate spanish d19b_e0e097b1:

    # St "I wonder if it needs fixing and if she will know how to.."
    St "Me pregunto si necesitará arreglos y si ella sabrá cómo hacerlo..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:348
translate spanish d19b_d5e51387:

    # St "It really looks like an intricate piece of machinery..."
    St "Realmente parece una pieza de maquinaria intrincada..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:351
translate spanish d19b_4eab4b25:

    # St "...but if it helps me keep the bad guys at a distance, it's worth it."
    St "...pero si me ayuda a mantener a los malos a distancia, vale la pena."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:354
translate spanish d19b_f3383cdb:

    # S "Hm...."
    S "Hm...."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:358
translate spanish d19b_866e8611:

    # St "I can't wait to find out more!"
    St "¡No puedo esperar a descubrir más!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:361
translate spanish d19b_9669528e:

    # "Later..."
    "Más tarde..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:365
translate spanish d19b_a0f0df5f:

    # Ma "An ancient crossbow?"
    Ma "¿Una ballesta antigua?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:368
translate spanish d19b_ab7b7b59:

    # Ma "It has been a long time since I saw one in functional shape."
    Ma "Hace mucho que no veía una en condiciones funcionales."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:371
translate spanish d19b_da4ecef1:

    # Ma "You were wise to keep it. Although I would not put too much trust into its condition."
    Ma "Fuiste sabia en conservarla. Aunque no confiaría demasiado en su estado."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:374
translate spanish d19b_cbea8bb3:

    # Ma "Have you used it yet?"
    Ma "¿La has usado ya?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:376
translate spanish d19b_905291f4:

    # S "I... wanted your expert opinion first. Didn't want to accidentally break something."
    S "Yo... quería primero tu opinión experta. No quería romper algo por accidente."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:379
translate spanish d19b_4bd0e737:

    # Ma "Take a seat, [S]. Let's take a closer look together."
    Ma "Siéntate, [S]. Vamos a echarle un vistazo más de cerca juntas."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:382
translate spanish d19b_f880241b:

    # S "Yes, ma'am."
    S "Sí, señora."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:385
translate spanish d19b_39e0278a:

    # "A short while later..."
    "Un rato después..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:388
translate spanish d19b_dadaad89:

    # Ma "Well... as ugly as this thing is, its parts will most likely still work... at least for some time."
    Ma "Bueno... por fea que sea esta cosa, lo más probable es que sus piezas todavía funcionen... al menos por un tiempo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:389
translate spanish d19b_c47bac3f:

    # Ma "You will eventually have to replace the strings, but for now it should suffice."
    Ma "Tarde o temprano tendrás que reemplazar las cuerdas, pero por ahora debería bastar."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:390
translate spanish d19b_2a75850f:

    # Ma "I think my husband will like to make a sketch of it and study it for a while, if he has the chance."
    Ma "Creo que a mi esposo le gustará hacer un boceto de ella y estudiarla un tiempo, si tiene la oportunidad."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:393
translate spanish d19b_4c5a5fe1:

    # S "Do you think I will be able to use it on my next mission?"
    S "¿Crees que podré usarla en mi próxima misión?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:396
translate spanish d19b_82c31cdd:

    # Ma "Reliably? No."
    Ma "¿Con fiabilidad? No."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:399
translate spanish d19b_5dd19f81:

    # Ma "I will be blunt, [S]. You are dealing with a deadly but flawed weapon."
    Ma "Seré franca, [S]. Estás tratando con un arma letal pero defectuosa."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:400
translate spanish d19b_4134eccc:

    # Ma "You are untrained in its use and maintenance. It's a weapon that is somewhat laborious and slow to reload."
    Ma "No tienes entrenamiento en su uso ni en su mantenimiento. Es un arma algo laboriosa y lenta de recargar."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:401
translate spanish d19b_6de8198c:

    # Ma "After the first shot, successful if you're lucky, you are most likely going to find yourself in melee range."
    Ma "Tras el primer disparo, acertado si tienes suerte, lo más probable es que te encuentres en combate cuerpo a cuerpo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:402
translate spanish d19b_58624fa3:

    # Ma "In short... don't get too excited. Not to mention the fact that you're going to need specially made arrows."
    Ma "En resumen... no te emociones demasiado. Y sin mencionar que vas a necesitar flechas hechas especialmente."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:405
translate spanish d19b_971a98df:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:408
translate spanish d19b_728efe60:

    # Ma "{i}*sighs*{/i}"
    Ma "{i}*suspira*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:409
translate spanish d19b_774e658f:

    # Ma "Don't give me that face..."
    Ma "No me pongas esa cara..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:410
translate spanish d19b_1aca60b5:

    # Ma "Fine. Today I will teach you how to use it. You may take it home, but only for target practice."
    Ma "Está bien. Hoy te enseñaré a usarla. Puedes llevártela a casa, pero solo para práctica de tiro."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:413
translate spanish d19b_0a4e09c9:

    # Ma "For now, stick to what you know, what I taught you, and what you've trained with all your life."
    Ma "Por ahora, quédate con lo que ya sabes, lo que te enseñé y con lo que has entrenado toda tu vida."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:416
translate spanish d19b_f880241b_1:

    # S "Yes, ma'am."
    S "Sí, señora."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:421
translate spanish d19b_318567e6:

    # Ma "Now for something different... We haven't had the pleasure of speaking since you returned."
    Ma "Ahora, algo diferente... No hemos tenido el placer de hablar desde que regresaste."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:422
translate spanish d19b_a51fad7b:

    # Ma "Tell me, how did you fare in the Zone? One's first visit is ought to be a unique one."
    Ma "Dime, ¿cómo te fue en la Zona? La primera visita suele ser única."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:425
translate spanish d19b_c3f86757:

    # S "It certainly was. I... sometimes questioned whether what I saw was real or not."
    S "Sin duda lo fue. Yo... a veces dudaba de si lo que veía era real o no."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:428
translate spanish d19b_0997689d:

    # Ma "I hope our trainings proved fruitful in preparing you for these unforeseen events?"
    Ma "Espero que nuestros entrenamientos hayan servido para prepararte ante esos acontecimientos imprevistos."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:432
translate spanish d19b_e246992d:

    # S "...?"
    S "¿...?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:435
translate spanish d19b_5f365f8f:

    # Ma "..."
    Ma "..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:436
translate spanish d19b_7bd768e9:

    # C "Mistress, if you please..."
    C "Ama, si me permite..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:439
translate spanish d19b_5e86161e:

    # Sl "I have brought refreshments."
    Sl "He traído los refrescos."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:442
translate spanish d19b_52a64227:

    # Ma "What took you so long?"
    Ma "¿Qué te tomó tanto tiempo?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:443
translate spanish d19b_195c195f:

    # Sl "I apologize."
    Sl "Lo lamento."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:444
translate spanish d19b_2d00c0e2:

    # Ma "What is the correct form?"
    Ma "¿Cuál es la forma correcta?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:445
translate spanish d19b_7bc371e6:

    # Sl "..."
    Sl "..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:448
translate spanish d19b_2a179eef:

    # Sl "I apologiz-"
    Sl "Yo me disculp—"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:451
translate spanish d19b_da83c96c:

    # "She makes a disapproving sound."
    "Ella hace un sonido de desaprobación."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:454
translate spanish d19b_be6b627e:

    # Sl "I... don't understa-"
    Sl "Yo... no entien—"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:457
translate spanish d19b_76b85fc1:

    # Ma "You do not apologize. You beg for forgiveness."
    Ma "Tú no te disculpas. Tú ruegas por perdón."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:458
translate spanish d19b_7c1dd64d:

    # Ma "Now, repeat."
    Ma "Ahora, repite."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:461
translate spanish d19b_13cf0bd1:

    # Sl "I beg for forgiveness, Mistress."
    Sl "Ruego su perdón, Ama."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:464
translate spanish d19b_15caea75:

    # Ma "Good boy. Put down the drinks and step closer."
    Ma "Buen chico. Deja las bebidas y acércate."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:467
translate spanish d19b_17703dfa:

    # "He does as he is told, without making a sound."
    "Él obedece sin hacer un solo ruido."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:470
translate spanish d19b_32c9fbbc:

    # Ma "Our guest is my valued student and a newly made Stalker. She will come by a few more times over the coming days."
    Ma "Nuestra invitada es mi apreciada alumna y una recién convertida Acechadora. Vendrá unas cuantas veces más en los próximos días."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:473
translate spanish d19b_c4e828b3:

    # Ma "Should you be asked to, you will obey her commands and satisfy her requests as if they came from me."
    Ma "Si ella te lo pide, obedecerás sus órdenes y cumplirás sus peticiones como si vinieran de mí."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:474
translate spanish d19b_65550557:

    # Ma "Did I make myself clear?"
    Ma "¿He sido clara?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:477
translate spanish d19b_7795861c:

    # Sl "Yes, mistress."
    Sl "Sí, Ama."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:480
translate spanish d19b_823af04e:

    # Ma "Good."
    Ma "Bien."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:483
translate spanish d19b_f921d167:

    # Ma "Now, what did I say about my husband tonight?"
    Ma "Ahora dime, ¿qué dije sobre mi esposo esta noche?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:484
translate spanish d19b_f95b94bb:

    # Sl "You mentioned that he worked hard this week, and deserves your attention."
    Sl "Mencionaste que trabajó duro esta semana y que merece tu atención."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:485
translate spanish d19b_99201b61:

    # "The conversation blurs as [S]'s attention shifts towards her thoughts..."
    "La conversación se desvanece mientras la atención de [S] se pierde en sus pensamientos..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:486
translate spanish d19b_f729323f:

    # St "She is so strict... Just like when she would tutor me."
    St "Es tan estricta... Igual que cuando me daba clases."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:495
translate spanish d19b_mandisa_talk_971a98df:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:498
translate spanish d19b_mandisa_talk_50f3f395:

    # St "It's easy to see what my [persistent.dad] or her husband see in her."
    St "Es fácil ver lo que mi [persistent.dad] o su esposo ven en ella."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:499
translate spanish d19b_mandisa_talk_e0066696:

    # St "She is elegant, poised, and her words carry weight."
    St "Ella es elegante, segura, y sus palabras tienen peso."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:502
translate spanish d19b_mandisa_talk_3f36fb7a:

    # St "This dress really complements her figure."
    St "Ese vestido realmente realza su figura."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:503
translate spanish d19b_mandisa_talk_1aadac84:

    # St "Her presence and strength are what made me crush on her when I first met her. She's the one who first awoke desire in me and longing for another person."
    St "Su presencia y fortaleza fueron lo que me hicieron enamorarme de ella cuando la conocí. Fue la primera en despertar en mí el deseo y las ansias por otra persona."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:504
translate spanish d19b_mandisa_talk_849dfaa0:

    # St "It took me long enough, to get over my infatuation for her."
    St "Me tomó bastante tiempo superar mi enamoramiento por ella."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:507
translate spanish d19b_mandisa_talk_1becf10f:

    # "[S] remains in a contemplative silence as Mandisa chastises the new hire further."
    "[S] permanece en un silencio contemplativo mientras Mandisa reprende aún más al nuevo sirviente."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:514
translate spanish d19b_mandisa_talk_971a98df_1:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:517
translate spanish d19b_mandisa_talk_d39cb602:

    # "[S] observes the slave for a few seconds..."
    "[S] observa al esclavo durante algunos segundos..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:518
translate spanish d19b_mandisa_talk_91016151:

    # St "He... seems suitably cowed by Mandisa; intimidated."
    St "Parece... suficientemente intimidado por Mandisa; acobardado."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:519
translate spanish d19b_mandisa_talk_508a93f9:

    # St "She always makes sure her servants are good looking, even this new one."
    St "Ella siempre se asegura de que sus sirvientes sean atractivos, incluso este nuevo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:520
translate spanish d19b_mandisa_talk_9f020a5e:

    # St "I wonder how it came to be that she and not her husband is the head of her house..."
    St "Me pregunto cómo fue que ella, y no su esposo, terminó siendo la cabeza de su casa..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:525
translate spanish d19b44_e5d0e3a7:

    # Ma "...so that's decided then."
    Ma "...entonces, así queda decidido."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:530
translate spanish re_d19b44_33463532:

    # Ma "Speaking of our guest... what do you think of the new hire, [S]? Does he please your eyes?"
    Ma "Hablando de nuestra invitada... ¿qué opinas del nuevo, [S]? ¿Te agrada a la vista?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:531
translate spanish re_d19b44_ca60e284:

    # Ma "He does have talented hands. Would you like to try a neck massage?"
    Ma "Tiene manos talentosas. ¿Quieres probar un masaje en el cuello?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:538
translate spanish re_d19b44_85ec7946:

    # S "Neck massage? I don't know if..."
    S "¿Masaje en el cuello? No sé si..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:541
translate spanish re_d19b44_40cfd9bf:

    # Ma "Don't disappoint me, boy. Do your best."
    Ma "No me decepciones, chico. Haz tu mejor esfuerzo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:544
translate spanish re_d19b44_7795861c:

    # Sl "Yes, mistress."
    Sl "Sí, ama."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:547
translate spanish re_d19b44_76a4b457:

    # "He steps behind [S]..."
    "Él se coloca detrás de [S]..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:550
translate spanish re_d19b44_dfd3ea1e:

    # Sl "Lady [S], I will now put my hands on your shoulder."
    Sl "Dama [S], pondré ahora mis manos en sus hombros."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:553
translate spanish re_d19b44_d8b8b220:

    # Ma "Don't be afraid. She will not bite you."
    Ma "No tengas miedo. Ella no te morderá."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:556
translate spanish re_d19b44_d0f192a5:

    # St "What did I get myself into..."
    St "En qué me he metido..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:557
translate spanish re_d19b44_f8371633:

    # Sl "You are very tense, lady... I will have to apply a bit more force, if you don't mind."
    Sl "Está muy tensa, mi señora... tendré que aplicar un poco más de fuerza, si no le importa."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:560
translate spanish re_d19b44_92f20428:

    # S "Agh-!"
    S "¡Agh-!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:561
translate spanish re_d19b44_950d9fe2:

    # "[S] grits her teeth, as the slave works on the knots hiding under her skin."
    "[S] aprieta los dientes mientras el esclavo trabaja sobre los nudos ocultos bajo su piel."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:562
translate spanish re_d19b44_4cd70713:

    # St "Is he trying to kill me?!"
    St "¿¡Está intentando matarme!?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:565
translate spanish re_d19b44_42988010:

    # St "...oh."
    St "...oh."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:566
translate spanish re_d19b44_7ec72f28:

    # St "That feels... nice actually."
    St "Eso se siente... bien, de hecho."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:569
translate spanish re_d19b44_c0d54c37:

    # Ma "{i}*sigh*{/i} He doesn't really go for the soft touch, does he?"
    Ma "{i}*suspiro*{/i} No busca precisamente el toque suave, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:570
translate spanish re_d19b44_971a98df:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:573
translate spanish re_d19b44_434a50bf:

    # Ma "Which is not all too surprising, considering where he came from."
    Ma "Lo cual no sorprende tanto, considerando de dónde viene."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:576
translate spanish re_d19b44_5cdb151b:

    # S "W-where did he come from...?"
    S "¿D-de dónde viene...?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:579
translate spanish re_d19b44_30c5cec1:

    # Ma "He was the leader of a war tribe, once."
    Ma "Una vez fue líder de una tribu de guerra."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:582
translate spanish re_d19b44_36f539e2:

    # Ma "Supposedly, he roamed the dunes with a sizeable band."
    Ma "Supuestamente, vagaba por las dunas con una banda numerosa."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:583
translate spanish re_d19b44_31e1de9a:

    # Ma "Then he wandered a little too close to Zetan territories, and that was his undoing."
    Ma "Pero se acercó demasiado a los territorios de Zeta, y esa fue su perdición."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:586
translate spanish re_d19b44_18e71c55:

    # S "A... warlord...? Will he not try..."
    S "¿Un... caudillo...? ¿No intentará...?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:587
translate spanish re_d19b44_dda7fe6a:

    # St "His hands... it feels like he could kill me any moment, and yet..."
    St "Sus manos... parece que podría matarme en cualquier momento, y sin embargo..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:588
translate spanish re_d19b44_4549af35:

    # Ma "It took time to tame him, granted. But months of imprisonment in the darkest and smallest dungeon will break anyone's spirit."
    Ma "Tardó en ser domado, claro. Pero meses de encierro en el calabozo más oscuro y estrecho quiebran el espíritu de cualquiera."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:591
translate spanish re_d19b44_f00a900b:

    # Ma "Add to that regular beatings and torture.."
    Ma "Súmale palizas regulares y torturas..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:592
translate spanish re_d19b44_5da7e3ff:

    # Ma "The slave business is not for the faint of heart, but the results are undeniable."
    Ma "El negocio de los esclavos no es para los débiles de corazón, pero los resultados son innegables."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:593
translate spanish re_d19b44_312dfd5a:

    # Ma "I should mention that he might be motivated by the occasional reward, which is more than the average slave can ask for."
    Ma "Debo mencionar que puede motivarse con una recompensa ocasional, que ya es más de lo que cualquier esclavo promedio puede pedir."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:594
translate spanish re_d19b44_a10595f2:

    # Ma "I am not a cruel mistress, after all."
    Ma "Al fin y al cabo, no soy una ama cruel."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:595
translate spanish re_d19b44_d2cbae97:

    # Ma "But what do you think?"
    Ma "Pero dime, ¿qué opinas?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:598
translate spanish re_d19b44_4230d0ec:

    # S "Nh... He does seem well tamed..."
    S "Nh... Parece bastante bien domado..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:603
translate spanish re_d19b44_2c2dca91:

    # S "I could get used to this..."
    S "Podría acostumbrarme a esto..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:606
translate spanish re_d19b44_152c2fcf:

    # Ma "You are welcome to his services."
    Ma "Tienes permiso para usar sus servicios."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:607
translate spanish re_d19b44_97cc7c6b:

    # Ma "He knows better than to disappoint."
    Ma "Él sabe bien que no debe decepcionar."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:612
translate spanish re_d19b44_3fbe7695:

    # S "...but I prefer the massages I get at home."
    S "... pero prefiero los masajes que recibo en casa."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:615
translate spanish re_d19b44_9186cb80:

    # Ma "Hm... I guess the house of [persistent.player_name!c] has the resources to afford the services of the best of servants."
    Ma "Mmm... Supongo que la casa de [persistent.player_name!c] tiene recursos suficientes como para permitirse los servicios de los mejores sirvientes."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:616
translate spanish re_d19b44_25d1b778:

    # "Hesitant, [S] nodds, avoiding to comment further."
    "Vacilante, [S] asiente, evitando comentar más."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:620
translate spanish re_d19b44_e16ce50f:

    # Ma "Anyway, I think our guest has had enough. Come here."
    Ma "En fin, creo que nuestra invitada ha tenido suficiente. Ven aquí."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:623
translate spanish re_d19b44_940a4537:

    # Sl "Yes, Mistress Mandisa."
    Sl "Sí, Ama Mandisa."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:626
translate spanish re_d19b44_490b74b1:

    # "Good..."
    "Bien..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:629
translate spanish re_d19b44_c903f3c1:

    # Sl "Mistress... I... have a request."
    Sl "Ama... yo... tengo una petición."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:633
translate spanish re_d19b44_457cd8fc:

    # "Mandisa leands forward just a fraction, waiting for the man to continue."
    "Mandisa se inclina apenas un poco hacia adelante, esperando a que el hombre continúe."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:636
translate spanish re_d19b44_e2426bf1:

    # Sl "I would ask that you allow me to serve your pleasure..."
    Sl "Le pido que me permita servir a su placer..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:639
translate spanish re_d19b44_dda94569:

    # Sl "I know you have a long day ahead of you..."
    Sl "Sé que le espera un día largo..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:642
translate spanish re_d19b44_3c03aaab:

    # Ma "Quiet."
    Ma "Silencio."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:645
translate spanish re_d19b44_b1b82d1f:

    # Ma "[S], my slave is offering sexual service, but what he really wants is relief for himself. You see, my servants are not allowed to spill their seed without my permission."
    Ma "[S], mi esclavo ofrece un servicio sexual, pero lo que realmente busca es desahogarse. Verás, mis sirvientes no tienen permitido derramar su semilla sin mi permiso."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:646
translate spanish re_d19b44_c18fd15f:

    # Ma "I am inclined to grant his wish. Do you mind if I do?"
    Ma "Estoy dispuesta a concederle su deseo. ¿Te importa si lo hago?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:654
translate spanish re_d19b44_b1106150:

    # S "I don't mind. Please, this is your house."
    S "No me molesta. Por favor, esta es tu casa."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:657
translate spanish re_d19b44_07d08c06:

    # Ma "Your audacity, to ask this of me when I am entertaining a guest should have you flogged, but I am in a good mood. Don't worry, [S], it will not take long."
    Ma "Tu osadía, pedirme esto mientras recibo a una invitada debería merecerte azotes, pero estoy de buen humor. No te preocupes, [S], no tardará mucho."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:660
translate spanish re_d19b44_2c4d046d:

    # Ma "{i}*sigh*{/i} Most men are mere animals. And like animals, you have to take care of their basic needs."
    Ma "{i}*suspiro*{/i} La mayoría de los hombres son simples animales. Y como animales, hay que atender sus necesidades básicas."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:663
translate spanish re_d19b44_c55f4d44:

    # Sl "T-thank you, Mistress."
    Sl "G-gracias, Ama."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:666
translate spanish re_d19b44_512427f0:

    # Ma "Hm."
    Ma "Hm."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:667
translate spanish re_d19b44_a3c68a48:

    # S "...!"
    S "¡...!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:670
translate spanish re_d19b44_de76d2f6:

    # Ma "...Two weeks, since the last time, is it not?"
    Ma "...Dos semanas desde la última vez, ¿no es así?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:673
translate spanish re_d19b44_2c8b35f0:

    # "She looks over to [S]..."
    "Ella mira hacia [S]..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:674
translate spanish re_d19b44_0845585f:

    # Sl "Y-yes."
    Sl "S-sí."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:677
translate spanish re_d19b44_3905274c:

    # St "It's... very big. Does she also...?"
    St "Es... muy grande. ¿Acaso ella también...?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:678
translate spanish re_d19b44_7ed750ea:

    # Ma "Impressive, isn't it?"
    Ma "Impresionante, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:681
translate spanish re_d19b44_fdbcc0b6:

    # Ma "You have seen some of my other slaves during your time with me."
    Ma "Ya has visto a algunos de mis otros esclavos durante tu tiempo conmigo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:682
translate spanish re_d19b44_b2db516c:

    # Ma "You should know I always look for the best specimen. You could say I have a type."
    Ma "Debes saber que siempre busco los mejores ejemplares. Podrías decir que tengo un tipo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:688
translate spanish re_d19b44_c729e99b:

    # St "She must be using them, the same way that [persistent.dad] does with our..."
    St "Debe estar usándolos, igual que [persistent.dad] lo hace con nuestras..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:695
translate spanish re_d19b44_980fe68b:

    # S "I... my [persistent.dad] only owns female servants."
    S "Yo... mi [persistent.dad] solo posee sirvientas."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:698
translate spanish re_d19b44_c96a8f6f:

    # Ma "That does not mean you have to, once you have your own household."
    Ma "Eso no significa que tú tengas que hacerlo, cuando tengas tu propia casa."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:702
translate spanish d19b76_895362c4:

    # S "You said it wouldn't take long?"
    S "¿Dijiste que no tardaría mucho?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:705
translate spanish d19b76_31ae0c73:

    # Ma "I did. They know I don't have a lot of patience for them."
    Ma "Así es. Ellos saben que no tengo mucha paciencia con ellos."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:707
translate spanish d19b76_c4a563c2:

    # Ma "Now, give me one second."
    Ma "Ahora, dame un segundo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:710
translate spanish d19b76_7bc371e6:

    # Sl "..."
    Sl "..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:714
translate spanish d19b76_7f124c9e:

    # Sl "Nh..."
    Sl "Nh..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:717
translate spanish d19b76_2f6c9bff:

    # Sl "...!"
    Sl "¡...!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:720
translate spanish d19b76_4252ceb3:

    # Sl "Ks..."
    Sl "Ks..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:723
translate spanish d19b76_5f365f8f:

    # Ma "..."
    Ma "..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:724
translate spanish d19b76_29025ece:

    # St "Is he not... done yet?"
    St "¿Acaso no ha... terminado ya?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:725
translate spanish d19b76_42eb65c8:

    # "The slave breathes heavily..."
    "El esclavo respira con fuerza..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:728
translate spanish d19b76_a3e29f96:

    # Sl "Mgh..."
    Sl "Mgh..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:731
translate spanish d19b76_5f365f8f_1:

    # Ma "..."
    Ma "..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:732
translate spanish d19b76_8bcacd51:

    # Sl "T-thank you, Mistress. Thank you."
    Sl "G-gracias, Ama. Gracias."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:735
translate spanish d19b76_9ce9760e:

    # St "He came so much... from just that?!"
    St "¿Se corrió tanto... solo con eso?!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:738
translate spanish d19b76_be888dca:

    # Ma "As I said, I don't have a lot of patience for them, and they know their place."
    Ma "Como dije, no tengo mucha paciencia con ellos, y saben bien cuál es su lugar."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:739
translate spanish d19b76_d0f1405e:

    # Ma "Anyway... Are you ready for your first crossbow lesson, [S]?"
    Ma "En fin... ¿Estás lista para tu primera lección con la ballesta, [S]?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:742
translate spanish d19b76_f5959565:

    # S "Ehm... yes, absolutely! Thank you for teaching me."
    S "Ehm... sí, ¡por supuesto! Gracias por enseñarme."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:753
translate spanish d19b76_ec53dfcd:

    # S "I... ehm... would prefer if we start our training right away."
    S "Yo... ehm... preferiría que empezáramos el entrenamiento de inmediato."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:756
translate spanish d19b76_ad5c4e3c:

    # Ma "It looks like you have to wait another day, slave. Our young friend is in a hurry."
    Ma "Parece que tendrás que esperar otro día, esclavo. Nuestra joven amiga tiene prisa."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:757
translate spanish d19b76_7814b725:

    # Sl "Y-yes, Mistress..."
    Sl "S-sí, Ama..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:760
translate spanish d19b76_8add53be:

    # Ma "I would suggest we waste no time and go to the range."
    Ma "Sugiero que no perdamos tiempo y vayamos al campo de tiro."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:761
translate spanish d19b76_46327d7f:

    # Ma "Are you ready for your first crossbow lesson?"
    Ma "¿Estás lista para tu primera lección con la ballesta?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:764
translate spanish d19b76_5a44d8ee:

    # S "Yes! Thank you for your lessons."
    S "¡Sí! Gracias por tus enseñanzas."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:775
translate spanish d19b18_75218df1:

    # S "Oh, t-thank you, but I'm not in need of one."
    S "Oh, g-gracias, pero no lo necesito."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:778
translate spanish d19b18_05ed8c08:

    # Ma "Well then, it looks like you're of no use here anymore, slave."
    Ma "Bien, entonces parece que ya no sirves para nada aquí, esclavo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:779
translate spanish d19b18_7814b725:

    # Sl "Y-yes, Mistress..."
    Sl "S-sí, Ama..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:782
translate spanish d19b18_8add53be:

    # Ma "I would suggest we waste no time and go to the range."
    Ma "Sugiero que no perdamos tiempo y vayamos al campo de tiro."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:783
translate spanish d19b18_46327d7f:

    # Ma "Are you ready for your first crossbow lesson?"
    Ma "¿Estás lista para tu primera lección con la ballesta?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:786
translate spanish d19b18_5a44d8ee:

    # S "Yes! Thank you for your lessons."
    S "¡Sí! Gracias por tus enseñanzas."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:796
translate spanish d19b87_33a46fdf:

    # "Some time later..."
    "Un rato después..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:800
translate spanish d19b87_c44a3048:

    # Ma "Hold it steady..."
    Ma "Sujétala firme..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:803
translate spanish d19b87_e77b8e86:

    # S "It's... getting heavy."
    S "Se está... poniendo pesada."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:804
translate spanish d19b87_fb70d08c:

    # Ma "Heavier than your blade, yes. But you will have to get used to it."
    Ma "Más pesada que tu espada, sí. Pero tendrás que acostumbrarte."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:807
translate spanish d19b87_1a4810b8:

    # Ma "Now, eyes on the target, not the weapon..."
    Ma "Ahora, los ojos en el blanco, no en el arma..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:808
translate spanish d19b87_7ff9fc50:

    # S "Mhm..."
    S "Mhm..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:811
translate spanish d19b87_cb7b0f5a:

    # Ma "Pick a spot... don't eye the whole target. Aim for the center of it. Don't lose focus."
    Ma "Elige un punto... no mires todo el blanco. Apunta al centro. No pierdas la concentración."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:814
translate spanish d19b87_6e83d838:

    # Ma "I am holding your arm only for support. You have to do the aiming. Notice your arms shift to the target?"
    Ma "Solo sostengo tu brazo para darte apoyo. Tú tienes que apuntar. ¿Notas cómo tus brazos se alinean con el blanco?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:815
translate spanish d19b87_75fc3974:

    # S "I do..."
    S "Sí, lo noto..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:818
translate spanish d19b87_922f8a76:

    # S "Do I... hold my breath?"
    S "¿Debo... contener la respiración?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:819
translate spanish d19b87_83fecee7:

    # Ma "No... you breathe steady... feel the weight of the weapon settle. Breath comes into it only once you're on target."
    Ma "No... respira de forma constante... siente cómo el peso del arma se estabiliza. La respiración solo entra en juego cuando ya tienes el blanco."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:820
translate spanish d19b87_8c6b9360:

    # S "Yes..."
    S "Sí..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:823
translate spanish d19b87_971a98df:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:824
translate spanish d19b87_cba73f42:

    # St "She is... caressing my shoulder...?"
    St "¿Ella está... acariciando mi hombro...?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:825
translate spanish d19b87_ebf167c7:

    # Ma "Eyes on the target, [S]. You're not looking where you're supposed to."
    Ma "Ojos en el blanco, [S]. No estás mirando donde deberías."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:828
translate spanish d19b87_ce8226cf:

    # St "...!"
    St "¡...!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:831
translate spanish d19b87_834e4cc4:

    # Ma "Now... I will keep you steady, and you prepare to fire, understood?"
    Ma "Ahora... yo te mantendré firme, y tú prepárate para disparar, ¿entendido?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:832
translate spanish d19b87_8c6b9360_1:

    # S "Yes..."
    S "Sí..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:835
translate spanish d19b87_0b1b69c2:

    # Ma "Take one last moment to focus on the spot..."
    Ma "Tómate un último instante para enfocarte en el punto..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:838
translate spanish d19b87_4c561b60:

    # Ma "...and then..."
    Ma "...y luego..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:841
translate spanish d19b87_2094bf67:

    # Ma "...pull the trigger."
    Ma "...aprieta el gatillo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:848
translate spanish d19b87_971a98df_1:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:849
translate spanish d19b87_8dc1b890:

    # S "I missed."
    S "Fallé."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:853
translate spanish d19b87_57ba963f:

    # Ma "I think with such a wide shot, it's safe to say you are {i}not{/i} a natural talent."
    Ma "Con un tiro tan desviado, creo que está claro que {i}no{/i} eres un talento natural."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:856
translate spanish d19b87_971a98df_2:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:859
translate spanish d19b87_297d8794:

    # Ma "But... talent is one thing, and practice and the ability to learn another."
    Ma "Pero... el talento es una cosa, y la práctica y la capacidad de aprender son otra."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:860
translate spanish d19b87_7cf80704:

    # Ma "And since you always were stubborn, or motivated, I am confident you will get there, eventually."
    Ma "Y como siempre fuiste terca, o motivada, confío en que llegarás a lograrlo, tarde o temprano."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:863
translate spanish d19b87_81fcd542:

    # S "Thank you for investing time into this for me, Lady Mandisa."
    S "Gracias por dedicarme tu tiempo en esto, Lady Mandisa."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:872
translate spanish d19b87_8871bdf0:

    # Ma "Before you go, there is one thing I want to ask."
    Ma "Antes de que te vayas, hay algo que quiero preguntarte."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:875
translate spanish d19b87_820c6d4e:

    # S "Hm?"
    S "¿Hm?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:876
translate spanish d19b87_ae65f00c:

    # "Her tone shifts, as her voice deepens somewhat..."
    "Su tono cambia, mientras su voz se vuelve algo más grave..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:879
translate spanish d19b87_1d331a01:

    # Ma "I am not stupid. I noticed you staring at me today, while I was conversing with my slave. I've caught that stare before."
    Ma "No soy tonta. Te vi mirándome hoy, mientras hablaba con mi esclavo. Ya he captado esa mirada antes."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:880
translate spanish d19b87_255c2715:

    # Ma "I will be direct. You're into women, are you not?"
    Ma "Seré directa. ¿Te gustan las mujeres, verdad?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:881
translate spanish d19b87_5779c83f:

    # Ma "More explicitly. Are you interested in me?"
    Ma "Más concretamente. ¿Estás interesada en mí?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:887
translate spanish d19b87_e9f409ab:

    # S "T-that is {i}very{/i} direct.. I..."
    S "E-eso es {i}muy{/i} directo... yo..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:890
translate spanish d19b87_8b87db72:

    # Ma "Answer the question, [S]."
    Ma "Responde a la pregunta, [S]."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:891
translate spanish d19b87_29ac14fb:

    # S "I mean... perhaps? You are an elegant woman, and..."
    S "Quiero decir... ¿quizás? Eres una mujer elegante, y..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:892
translate spanish d19b87_8029c6a2:

    # "She clicks with her mouth in disappointment..."
    "Chasquea la lengua con decepción..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:893
translate spanish d19b87_971a98df_3:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:894
translate spanish d19b87_8c6b9360_2:

    # S "Yes..."
    S "Sí..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:897
translate spanish d19b87_391461aa:

    # Ma "I figured. Listen to me, [S]."
    Ma "Lo suponía. Escúchame, [S]."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:900
translate spanish d19b87_835411f3:

    # Ma "Your father asked that I keep our interactions purely limited to our lessons, and I have always respected this agreement, even though I did not agree with his reasoning."
    Ma "Tu padre pidió que mantuviera nuestras interacciones estrictamente limitadas a las lecciones, y siempre he respetado ese acuerdo, aunque no compartiera sus razones."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:901
translate spanish d19b87_3d6c926b:

    # Ma "But now those times are over, you are a fully fleshed Stalker and the person with whom I have a deal is you, not your father."
    Ma "Pero esos tiempos ya terminaron. Ahora eres una Acechadora hecha y derecha y la persona con quien tengo un trato eres tú, no tu padre."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:902
translate spanish d19b87_50336530:

    # Ma "Your father is not paying me for these lessons anymore, and we should talk price, before we continue."
    Ma "Tu padre ya no me paga por estas lecciones, y debemos hablar de precio antes de continuar."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:905
translate spanish d19b87_b976fe7b:

    # S "You are right! I should have thought of this myself. I am sorry. You should name your price!"
    S "¡Tienes razón! Yo misma debería haber pensado en eso. Lo siento. ¡Debes decirme tu precio!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:908
translate spanish d19b87_dee04344:

    # St "I am such an idiot! Have I offended her?"
    St "¡Soy una idiota! ¿La habré ofendido?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:911
translate spanish d19b87_7306166b:

    # Ma "Good, now that we understand each other, consider this. I do not want your coin, nor goods to barter."
    Ma "Bien, ahora que nos entendemos, considera esto. No quiero tu dinero ni bienes para intercambiar."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:912
translate spanish d19b87_94c7e575:

    # Ma "You will accompany me, for one night."
    Ma "Me acompañarás... por una noche."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:915
translate spanish d19b87_d39b16b9:

    # St "She is... oh, wow. What do I do now?"
    St "Ella... oh, dios. ¿Qué hago ahora?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:918
translate spanish d19b87_0c2a4459:

    # Ma "I will have you for the evening. You will dress up nicely for me, and come see me when you're ready."
    Ma "Te tendré para mí esa noche. Te vestirás bien para mí, y vendrás a verme cuando estés lista."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:923
translate spanish d19b87_22053bf6:

    # "Her heart skips a beat, when she realises what Mandisa is asking of her. She ponders for a second whether she should feel flattered, insulted, or intrigued by the implications..."
    "Su corazón da un vuelco al darse cuenta de lo que Mandisa le está pidiendo. Se pregunta un instante si debería sentirse halagada, insultada o intrigada por lo que eso implica..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:926
translate spanish d19b87_e1896b80:

    # S "I see..."
    S "Ya veo..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:929
translate spanish d19b87_9a9a8175:

    # St "I see? What am I even saying?!"
    St "¿Ya veo? ¡¿Qué demonios estoy diciendo?!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:930
translate spanish d19b87_ff6a9169:

    # St "Keep it together, [S]..."
    St "Contrólate, [S]..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:933
translate spanish d19b87_c950b5ef:

    # Ma "Then it is settled. I will look forward to seeing you again, [S]."
    Ma "Entonces está decidido. Espero volver a verte, [S]."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:934
translate spanish d19b87_da99d3e4:

    # Ma "And don't bring the crossbow. You will not be needing it."
    Ma "Y no traigas la ballesta. No la vas a necesitar."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:939
translate spanish d19b87_9553a2e4:

    # S "N-no, that must have been a coincidence."
    S "N-no, eso debe haber sido una coincidencia."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:940
translate spanish d19b87_0407455f:

    # S "You are a very elegant woman, Lady Mandisa, I was simply admiring your dress!"
    S "Eres una mujer muy elegante, Lady Mandisa, simplemente estaba admirando tu vestido."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:941
translate spanish d19b87_512427f0:

    # Ma "Hm."
    Ma "Hm."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:945
translate spanish d19b87_e3d38471:

    # Ma "I take it you are just like your [persistent.dad], can't keep his eyes off mine either."
    Ma "Supongo que eres igual que tu [persistent.dad], él tampoco puede apartar los ojos de mí."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:947
translate spanish d19b107_9066f184:

    # Ma "Regardless. You are welcome to join me again for your next lesson."
    Ma "En cualquier caso. Eres bienvenida a unirte de nuevo a mí en tu próxima lección."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:948
translate spanish d19b107_1fabdf0d:

    # Ma "Until then, I advise to not use the crossbow for anything other than practice. Use the arrows sparingly."
    Ma "Hasta entonces, te aconsejo no usar la ballesta para nada más que práctica. Usa las flechas con moderación."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:951
translate spanish d19b107_d2c95099:

    # S "Understood. Thank you again, lady Mandisa."
    S "Entendido. Gracias de nuevo, Lady Mandisa."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:954
translate spanish d19b107_4eec2351:

    # Ma "You can leave now, [S]. Until next time."
    Ma "Puedes irte ya, [S]. Hasta la próxima."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:958
translate spanish d19b107_4410e144:

    # "Later that same day..."
    "Más tarde ese mismo día..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:961
translate spanish d19b107_36fabe4b:

    # S "And yeah... so that's roughly what happened."
    S "Y sí... eso fue más o menos lo que pasó."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:964
translate spanish d19b107_fbaf8fc6:

    # Z "Interesting..."
    Z "Interesante..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:966
translate spanish d19b107_a8910463:

    # Z "I guess you're going to see Mandisa from a different perspective, then."
    Z "Supongo que vas a ver a Mandisa desde otra perspectiva, entonces."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:969
translate spanish d19b107_2b401328:

    # S "Yes, I suppose. Let's see... how it goes..."
    S "Sí, supongo. Veamos... cómo va..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:972
translate spanish d19b107_48ff71c2:

    # Z "About that crossbow... you're still taking it?"
    Z "Sobre la ballesta... ¿todavía piensas llevarla?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:975
translate spanish d19b107_6d4ac215:

    # S "Yes, but if push comes to shove, I will rely on my blades for now. Maybe I can get some practice in."
    S "Sí, pero si se complica, confiaré en mis espadas por ahora. Quizás consiga algo de práctica."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:978
translate spanish d19b107_4a932b8a:

    # S "Let me know when you want to go?"
    S "Avísame cuando quieras que vayamos, ¿sí?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:982
translate spanish d19b107_34011f06:

    # Z "Yes, but not today. And don't prepare too much just yet - let's visit the Queen first. We don't know where we're going."
    Z "Sí, pero no hoy. Y no te prepares demasiado todavía: primero visitemos a la Reina. No sabemos adónde vamos."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:993
translate spanish d19c_59656cf3:

    # "You and [S] walk towards the Palace where you're expecting to meet the Queen and a briefing for your next mission..."
    "Tú y [S] camináis hacia el Palacio, donde esperáis encontraros con la Reina y recibir un informe sobre vuestra próxima misión..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:998
translate spanish d19c_f0e8f4ad:

    # Q "{i}*humming*{/i}"
    Q "{i}*tarareando*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1001
translate spanish d19c_c67a9857:

    # Q "Oh, there you are.. Welcome."
    Q "Oh, ahí estáis... Bienvenidos."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1004
translate spanish d19c_f0d53c69:

    # Q "What's wrong, [S]? You look like I turned into a mummy?"
    Q "¿Qué pasa, [S]? ¿Tienes cara de que me hubiera convertido en una momia?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1007
translate spanish d19c_e396346d:

    # S "I... guess she does that now? What have I been missing...?"
    S "¿Yo... supongo que ahora hace eso? ¿Qué me he perdido...?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1010
translate spanish d19c_4f6489b9:

    # Z "You've been missing out on a number of things, yes... but this is new to me, too."
    Z "Te has perdido varias cosas, sí... pero esto también es nuevo para mí."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1013
translate spanish d19c_04213af8:

    # Q "Oh, you're talking about my attire?"
    Q "Oh, ¿habláis de mi atuendo?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1016
translate spanish d19c_48749507:

    # Q "Out of everyone in the palace, you two are the ones who are complaining?"
    Q "¿De todos en el palacio, sois vosotros dos los que os quejáis?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1020
translate spanish d19c_51be0606:

    # Q "Tell me, what is the point of having a palace dedicated in your name, if you can not walk around freely in it?"
    Q "Dime, ¿cuál es el sentido de tener un palacio dedicado a tu nombre, si no puedes caminar libremente por él?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1021
translate spanish d19c_4eb771ab:

    # Q "And before you ask, yes, people may stare when they think I am not looking, but they know their eyes would be forfeit if they did so openly."
    Q "Y antes de que preguntes, sí, la gente puede mirar cuando cree que no los veo, pero saben que sus ojos serían el precio si lo hicieran abiertamente."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1024
translate spanish d19c_33f56e62:

    # "The silk robe flows down her shoulders as she struts around with confidence."
    "La bata de seda se desliza por sus hombros mientras camina con confianza."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1025
translate spanish d19c_659d9f30:

    # S "Oh, I wasn't complaining, at all, really... But yes, I was wondering what people would say or do."
    S "Oh, no me estaba quejando, en absoluto... Pero sí, me preguntaba qué diría o haría la gente."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1028
translate spanish d19c_9037fde8:

    # "You walk up to her..."
    "Te acercas a ella..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1031
translate spanish d19c_880ec9d9:

    # Q "[persistent.player_name], did you give your [persistent.da] a new outfit? I might be having a competitor here."
    Q "[persistent.player_name], ¿le diste a tu [persistent.da] un atuendo nuevo? Puede que tenga aquí una competidora."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1034
translate spanish d19c_cf014f06:

    # Z "She wears it well, doesn't she?"
    Z "Le queda bien, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1037
translate spanish d19c_1a1d0235:

    # S "I am sure it's not as comfortable as yours, my Queen..."
    S "Estoy segura de que no es tan cómodo como el suyo, mi Reina..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1040
translate spanish d19c_01f869d9:

    # Q "Hm... I think I can agree with that."
    Q "Hm... Creo que puedo estar de acuerdo con eso."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1043
translate spanish d19c_84b49db8:

    # Q "Perhaps, when I tire of it, you will try it on?"
    Q "Quizá, cuando me canse de él, quieras probártelo tú."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1046
translate spanish d19c_8bda1abe:

    # Q "Regardless... you two are here to talk shop."
    Q "En fin... vosotros dos habéis venido a hablar de negocios."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1047
translate spanish d19c_45dae72b:

    # Q "And I am here trying to decide if I can take the risk of potentially rewriting the history and the entire law of the land, or whether I should just have you both executed and bury the whole thing."
    Q "Y yo estoy aquí intentando decidir si me arriesgo a reescribir la historia y toda la ley del reino, o si debería mandaros ejecutar a los dos y enterrar el asunto."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1050
translate spanish d19c_9654211a:

    # Q "So... needless to say, lots to think about. So exciting!"
    Q "Así que... sobra decirlo, tengo mucho en lo que pensar. ¡Qué emocionante!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1053
translate spanish d19c_c9085435:

    # "Her tone is both genuinely excited but also cold and calculating. Not for the first time, you can't help but think of the young Queen as a dangerously unpredictable viper."
    "Su tono es a la vez genuinamente emocionado, pero frío y calculador. No es la primera vez que no puedes evitar pensar en la joven Reina como en una víbora peligrosamente impredecible."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1054
translate spanish d19c_7299a929:

    # Z "So... What have you done?"
    Z "Entonces... ¿qué has hecho?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1057
translate spanish d19c_7dd6f436:

    # Q "Lost my perfect tan, is what I have done. I have spent so many hours buried in ancient tomes in the windowless depth of my personal library."
    Q "Perder mi bronceado perfecto, eso es lo que he hecho. He pasado tantas horas enterrada en tomos antiguos en lo más profundo y sin ventanas de mi biblioteca personal."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1060
translate spanish d19c_eb9458d6:

    # Q "My findings are worth it though. It turns out a certain Elder Paris has indeed been one of the founding Elders of this city."
    Q "Pero mis hallazgos valieron la pena. Resulta que cierto Anciano Paris fue, de hecho, uno de los ancianos fundadores de esta ciudad."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1061
translate spanish d19c_54073a27:

    # Q "His name however seems to have been purged by most of the ancient records, going back all the way to the first Queens."
    Q "Sin embargo, su nombre parece haber sido borrado de la mayoría de los registros antiguos, remontándose hasta las primeras Reinas."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1062
translate spanish d19c_85011feb:

    # Q "I suspect that his discontent with the shape the city was taking was noticed and mostly redacted from any official acts towards the end of his life."
    Q "Sospecho que su descontento con la forma que estaba tomando la ciudad fue notado y en gran parte eliminado de los actos oficiales hacia el final de su vida."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1065
translate spanish d19c_062dc921:

    # Q "So there's a possibility that his legacy, his mysterious cave has been lost or destroyed over time."
    Q "Así que existe la posibilidad de que su legado, su misteriosa cueva, se haya perdido o destruido con el tiempo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1068
translate spanish d19c_4406c334:

    # S "But... We're hoping for that not to be the case?"
    S "Pero... ¿esperamos que no sea el caso?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1071
translate spanish d19c_166f332f:

    # Q "Eeeexactly."
    Q "Eeeexacto."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1074
translate spanish d19c_52f26021:

    # Q "And in order to find out if there is anything left in this supposed cave of his, I have determined a shortlist of possible locations where it might have been."
    Q "Y para averiguar si queda algo en esa supuesta cueva suya, he preparado una lista corta de posibles ubicaciones donde pudo haber estado."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1079
translate spanish d19c_161fa5fd:

    # "She hops off the table..."
    "Se baja de la mesa..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1082
translate spanish d19c_06360c84:

    # Q "And here it is..."
    Q "Y aquí está..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1085
translate spanish d19c_ca0dbd83:

    # Q "...all the information I found about his possible hideout, and the area surrounding it."
    Q "... toda la información que encontré sobre su posible escondite, y el área que lo rodea."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1086
translate spanish d19c_9626b3da:

    # Q "I wrote it down neatly, so you can study my findings and determine where to go from there."
    Q "Lo escribí todo con cuidado, para que podáis estudiar mis hallazgos y decidir a dónde ir a partir de ahí."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1089
translate spanish d19c_6f3ae31b:

    # Q "That way, you can go out and enjoy the adventure, while I am stuck here doing gods know whatever the next pestering Elder needs me to do."
    Q "Así podréis salir a disfrutar de la aventura, mientras yo me quedo aquí haciendo, dios sabe qué, lo que el próximo anciano molesto me pida."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1094
translate spanish d19c_1d8159d4:

    # Q "Anyway, let me tell you my conclusions."
    Q "En fin, dejad que os cuente mis conclusiones."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1095
translate spanish d19c_ef194477:

    # Q "What I found out, is that back in the day, the Elder was recorded as being often away from the Palace, and preferring to reside in the remnants of an underground temple."
    Q "Lo que descubrí es que, en su época, se registraba que el Anciano solía estar lejos del Palacio, prefiriendo residir en los restos de un templo subterráneo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1096
translate spanish d19c_b64a406d:

    # Q "I believe the temple predated our founders. It is very likely the place he used as a private study or library. The one we know about, that he is supposed to have destroyed."
    Q "Creo que el templo es anterior a nuestros fundadores. Es muy probable que fuera el lugar que usaba como estudio o biblioteca privada. El mismo del que sabemos, y que se supone que destruyó."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1097
translate spanish d19c_0634b54d:

    # Q "His advanced age, failing health and need for secrecy make me think that whatever he saved from the fire... Well, he must have hidden it not too far away from there."
    Q "Su avanzada edad, la salud debilitada y la necesidad de secretismo me hacen pensar que lo que sea que salvara del fuego... lo debió ocultar no muy lejos de allí."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1098
translate spanish d19c_3c80daca:

    # Z "That makes sense."
    Z "Tiene sentido."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1101
translate spanish d19c_d66d131a:

    # Q "The problem is that there are no records of where that secondary place might be."
    Q "El problema es que no hay registros de dónde podría estar ese segundo lugar."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1104
translate spanish d19c_9c3643ef:

    # Q "Now listen closely. I have collected every scrap of information we have about the immediate surroundings to his ancient dwelling."
    Q "Ahora escuchad con atención. He recopilado cada fragmento de información que tenemos sobre los alrededores inmediatos de su antigua morada."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1105
translate spanish d19c_1e483ae4:

    # Q "Only a few of the current settlements and markers have remained the same, but I have a strong suspicion that one of those will prove to be what we're looking for."
    Q "Solo unos pocos de los asentamientos y señales actuales se han mantenido iguales, pero sospecho firmemente que uno de esos será lo que buscamos."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1106
translate spanish d19c_3f661a3c:

    # Q "The only way forward is to go there and verify what information we have with whatever inkling the current locals might have."
    Q "La única forma de avanzar es ir allí y verificar la información que tenemos con lo que los lugareños actuales puedan saber."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1109
translate spanish d19c_865a8cb8:

    # Z "So, we must find the ancient residence of an Elder from four centuries ago, by asking the locals. I don't see a problem with that."
    Z "Así que debemos encontrar la antigua residencia de un Anciano de hace cuatro siglos preguntando a los lugareños. No le veo el problema."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1112
translate spanish d19c_de5f5150:

    # S "Hey, I'll take this over chasing a lone scout in the middle of a place riddled with anomalies any day."
    S "Oye, yo prefiero esto antes que perseguir a un explorador solitario en medio de un lugar plagado de anomalías."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1113
translate spanish d19c_bba099e0:

    # S "I'm looking forward to it actually. We'd still be in Zetan territory, wouldn't we?"
    S "La verdad es que tengo muchas ganas. Seguiríamos estando en territorio zetano, ¿no?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1116
translate spanish d19c_214de277:

    # Z "Whatever place an old man like him could reach by foot or camel, it can't be too far away. So yes, we would be."
    Z "Cualquier lugar al que un viejo como él pudiera llegar a pie o en camello, no puede estar demasiado lejos. Así que sí, lo estaríamos."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1119
translate spanish d19c_6b20715d:

    # Z "However, that is not a guarantee of safety. There are plenty of settlers who have mixed feelings about being under the rule of Zeta, even now. They might cause a problem."
    Z "Sin embargo, eso no garantiza seguridad. Hay muchos colonos que aún hoy tienen sentimientos encontrados sobre estar bajo el dominio de Zeta. Podrían causar problemas."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1120
translate spanish d19c_010a3499:

    # S "Noted... Anyway, that's pretty exciting! It's been a while since we went on a proper scavenger hunt."
    S "Anotado... De todos modos, ¡es bastante emocionante! Hace tiempo que no vamos a una auténtica búsqueda de tesoros."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1123
translate spanish d19c_cc44489e:

    # S "Remember that evening on top of the pyramid, watching the sun set?"
    S "¿Recuerdas aquella tarde en lo alto de la pirámide, viendo ponerse el sol?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1124
translate spanish d19c_671ed0d5:

    # Z "I do... perhaps there will be another moment like that."
    Z "Sí lo recuerdo... quizá haya otro momento así."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1127
translate spanish d19c_bdc61a01:

    # Q "..."
    Q "..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1128
translate spanish d19c_88a3a22c:

    # S "I hope so... Maybe this time we avoid the mortal peril to get there?"
    S "Eso espero... ¿Quizá esta vez evitemos el peligro mortal para llegar allí?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1129
translate spanish d19c_cc429a50:

    # Z "{i}*chuckles*{/i} Maybe. But then, would we really appreciate the moment?"
    Z "{i}*risilla*{/i} Quizá. Pero entonces, ¿realmente apreciaríamos el momento?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1132
translate spanish d19c_7279bb98:

    # Q "Okay, that's very cute, but I'm still here, in case you forgot."
    Q "Está bien, muy tierno todo, pero sigo aquí, por si lo habíais olvidado."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1135
translate spanish d19c_8b8e32e6:

    # S "Right, uh... what were you saying?"
    S "Cierto, eh... ¿qué estabas diciendo?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1138
translate spanish d19c_c305b435:

    # Q "Nothing... I was about to give you the pages..."
    Q "Nada... Estaba a punto de daros las páginas..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1139
translate spanish d19c_5cac09c6:

    # Q "...and then you can go on your adventure, and have fun and all that."
    Q "... y luego podéis iros a vuestra aventura, divertiros y todo eso."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1142
translate spanish d19c_8305c54a:

    # S "Okay, I'll take them."
    S "De acuerdo, me las llevaré."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1145
translate spanish d19c_7cc4614c:

    # "She hands [S] a scroll enveloping multiple fading sheets of papyrus..."
    "Ella le entrega a [S] un rollo que envuelve varias hojas de papiro desvaídas..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1148
translate spanish d19c_bdc11729:

    # Q "There, you have it. Now, if you'll excuse me, I have a tight schedule today."
    Q "Ahí tienes. Ahora, si me disculpáis, hoy tengo una agenda apretada."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1151
translate spanish d19c_afde4b8f:

    # Zt "Her sudden mood shift is evident..."
    Zt "Su repentino cambio de humor es evidente..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1154
translate spanish d19c_b69f6cb8:

    # Z "We will be going then."
    Z "Entonces nos marchamos."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1157
translate spanish d19c_1015e0b3:

    # S "See you in two days, I assume?"
    S "¿Nos vemos en dos días, supongo?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1160
translate spanish d19c_69dedc2b:

    # Q "Will you be leaving tonight?"
    Q "¿Partiréis esta noche?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1163
translate spanish d19c_52243927:

    # S "I thought so. Unless my esteemed mentor wants to spend one last night with my [persistent.mom]?"
    S "Ya me lo imaginaba. ¿A menos que mi estimado mentor quiera pasar una última noche con mi [persistent.mom]?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1166
translate spanish d19c_e23f43e0:

    # Z "Your esteemed mentor is ready to go."
    Z "Tu estimado mentor está listo para marchar."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1167
translate spanish d19c_95cfba88:

    # S "Perfect! Okay, see you soon, {i}my Queen{/i}!"
    S "¡Perfecto! Bien, nos vemos pronto, {i}mi Reina{/i}!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1171
translate spanish d19c_f7a694d6:

    # Q "Be safe, and bring results."
    Q "Cuidaos, y traed resultados."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1178
translate spanish d19c_6be12aa4:

    # "You make your way home, and start packing immediately."
    "Regresas a casa y comienzas a hacer las maletas de inmediato."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1179
translate spanish d19c_a533d809:

    # "After having said your goodbyes to your other women, [S] hops on the back of the truck, ready to go."
    "Tras despedirte de tus otras mujeres, [S] sube a la parte trasera del camión, lista para partir."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1188
translate spanish d19d_d9380a3b:

    # Z "Are you sure you didn't forget anything? Water, tent?"
    Z "¿Segura de que no olvidaste nada? ¿Agua, tienda de campaña?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1189
translate spanish d19d_479e53dd:

    # Z "The bed of the truck is suspiciously empty."
    Z "La parte trasera del camión está sospechosamente vacía."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1192
translate spanish d19d_6e954649:

    # S "Good thing you have me, huh? It's all in there. Take a look under the backseats!"
    S "Menos mal que me tienes, ¿eh? Está todo ahí. ¡Mira debajo de los asientos traseros!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1195
translate spanish d19d_b19d68eb:

    # Z "I trust you. Anyway, for a change, if we missed anything, the settlements around the area can provide."
    Z "Confío en ti. De todos modos, por una vez, si olvidamos algo, los asentamientos de la zona podrán proveernos."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1198
translate spanish d19d_1044d50b:

    # Z "This will be our first trip together, since before the Zone."
    Z "Este será nuestro primer viaje juntas, desde antes de la Zona."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1199
translate spanish d19d_e13c6e75:

    # Z "Do you feel any different?"
    Z "¿Te sientes diferente?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1202
translate spanish d19d_f145bf38:

    # S "Yeah, I do. I am less concerned in a way, now that I have you with me; but also, more focused at the same time."
    S "Sí, lo hago. Estoy menos preocupada en cierto modo, ahora que te tengo conmigo; pero al mismo tiempo, también más concentrada."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1205
translate spanish d19d_51373078:

    # Z "Well... I will do my best to keep you safe, but I expect you to do the same. We travel as equals, today."
    Z "Bueno... Haré lo mejor para mantenerte a salvo, pero espero que tú hagas lo mismo. Hoy viajamos como iguales."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1208
translate spanish d19d_82e27a40:

    # Z "Time to run this engine. Ready?"
    Z "Hora de poner este motor en marcha. ¿Lista?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1209
translate spanish d19d_5acb2568:

    # S "Ready!"
    S "¡Lista!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1219
translate spanish d19d_d07539a7:

    # S "{i}*humming*{/i}"
    S "{i}*tarareando*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1225
translate spanish d19d_290d545b:

    # S "What is..."
    S "¿Qué es...?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1235
translate spanish d19d_fd50fa62:

    # S "Huh...?"
    S "¿Eh...?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1236
translate spanish d19d_d6280ebc:

    # Z "Who's this..."
    Z "¿Quién es este...?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1239
translate spanish d19d_a74ca9c6:

    # S "Well... that's unexpected..."
    S "Vaya... esto sí que no lo esperaba..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1240
translate spanish d19d_b7403a90:

    # S "I didn't realise we had a guest..."
    S "No me di cuenta de que teníamos invitado..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1245
translate spanish d19d_04dd8070:

    # Z "{size=-3}Who is that, [S]!?"
    Z "{size=-3}¿Quién es, [S]!?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1248
translate spanish d19d_f37c038c:

    # C "Start this damned thing already!"
    C "¡Arranca esta maldita cosa de una vez!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1251
translate spanish d19d_552d577c:

    # Z "[S], what is going on?!"
    Z "¡[S], qué está pasando?!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1254
translate spanish d19d_dd42540b:

    # S "Oh, nothing to worry about..."
    S "Oh, nada de qué preocuparse..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1257
translate spanish d19d_985b5271:

    # S "...at least I believe so..."
    S "... al menos eso creo..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1260
translate spanish d19d_60f2fbbd:

    # S "Come on, show him who's under that mask. Unless you want to stay here for a little longer..."
    S "Vamos, enséñale quién está bajo esa máscara. A menos que quieras quedarte aquí un rato más..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1272
translate spanish d19d_36206b78:

    # Z "I'll be damned...{w=2}{nw}"
    Z "Que me parta un rayo...{w=2}{nw}"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1275
translate spanish d19d_ddab59ac:

    # S "How did nobody notice? You're the most important person in the city!{w=3.5}{nw}"
    S "¿Cómo es que nadie se dio cuenta? ¡Eres la persona más importante de la ciudad!{w=3.5}{nw}"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1278
translate spanish d19d_f08cdc87:

    # Q "I am taking a long rest in my chambers. And I have a certain someone who keeps this a secret.{w=4.5}{nw}"
    Q "Estoy tomando un largo descanso en mis aposentos. Y tengo a cierta persona que mantiene esto en secreto.{w=4.5}{nw}"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1281
translate spanish d19d_594cf47b:

    # S "You heard our majesty, [persistent.dad]. Do we take off?{w=2}{nw}"
    S "Ya oíste a su majestad, [persistent.dad]. ¿Despegamos?{w=2}{nw}"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1285
translate spanish d19d_0cb7c265:

    # Z "{i}*laughs*{/i} You better sit down, my Queen. It's going to get bumpy, and we don't want you falling off.{w=4.6}{nw}"
    Z "{i}*risas*{/i} Será mejor que te sientes, mi Reina. Esto se va a mover, y no queremos que te caigas.{w=4.6}{nw}"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1294
translate spanish d19d_02739c17:

    # S "So... you never mentioned you were planning to join us last time we met."
    S "Entonces... nunca mencionaste que planeabas unirte a nosotros la última vez que nos vimos."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1297
translate spanish d19d_cfd6bfa8:

    # Q "Well, this matter concerns me too, no?"
    Q "Bueno, este asunto también me concierne a mí, ¿no?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1300
translate spanish d19d_453120f1:

    # Q "I can't let you have all the fun for yourselves."
    Q "No puedo dejar que os llevéis toda la diversión."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1303
translate spanish d19d_00313f8d:

    # Q "...plus, I've been wanting to do this for a long time."
    Q "... además, llevo mucho tiempo queriendo hacer esto."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1304
translate spanish d19d_a571e9a8:

    # Q "You know, being without a retinue coddling me constantly."
    Q "Ya sabes, estar sin un séquito mimándome constantemente."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1307
translate spanish d19d_c0e41075:

    # S "Are you sure about this? Venturing outside the walls of Zeta alone?"
    S "¿Estás segura de esto? ¿Aventurarte fuera de los muros de Zeta sola?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1310
translate spanish d19d_5c7d9f43:

    # "She moves over..."
    "Ella se acerca..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1313
translate spanish d19d_8181db88:

    # Q "Well, I am not alone, am I?"
    Q "Bueno, no estoy sola, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1314
translate spanish d19d_a5ffa857:

    # Q "I am sure your [persistent.dad] will do his best to protect his Queen."
    Q "Estoy segura de que tu [persistent.dad] hará lo mejor para proteger a su reina."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1315
translate spanish d19d_aba48dfe:

    # Q "And I am assuming, so will you."
    Q "Y supongo que tú también lo harás."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1318
translate spanish d19d_fe82c0e0:

    # S "We might, but won't people notice your absence?"
    S "Puede ser, pero... ¿no notarán la gente tu ausencia?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1321
translate spanish d19d_87f1f8e0:

    # Q "For all they know, I feel a bit under the weather and retreated to my private chambers for a bit."
    Q "Para lo que ellos saben, me siento un poco indispuesta y me he retirado a mis aposentos privados un tiempo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1322
translate spanish d19d_510e3239:

    # Q "And as I said, that guard that likes to pose as your [persistent.dad]'s wench can keep secrets..."
    Q "Y como dije, esa guardia que disfruta haciéndose pasar por la fulana de tu [persistent.dad] sabe guardar secretos..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1323
translate spanish d19d_32bd5125:

    # Q "...as for the rest, well... they know better than asking prying questions."
    Q "... en cuanto al resto, bueno... saben que es mejor no hacer preguntas indiscretas."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1326
translate spanish d19d_53ff1ace:

    # S "So, I take it this is your first time riding a car? It's a bit more comfortable than a camel."
    S "Entonces, ¿supongo que es tu primera vez viajando en coche? Es un poco más cómodo que un camello."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1327
translate spanish d19d_80bc95b8:

    # Q "It's definitely more noisy, is it like this all the time?"
    Q "Definitivamente es más ruidoso, ¿es así todo el tiempo?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1328
translate spanish d19d_0e49705d:

    # S "Eh, you get used to it."
    S "Eh, te acostumbras."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1331
translate spanish d19d_adb492cc:

    # Zt "That adds some layers of responsibility. Stay focused, [persistent.player_name]..."
    Zt "Eso añade unas cuantas capas de responsabilidad. Concéntrate, [persistent.player_name]..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1332
translate spanish d19d_4cdf8522:

    # Zt "...all you have to do is somehow avoid anyone seeing the Queen of Zeta in your trunk..."
    Zt "... lo único que tienes que hacer es evitar que alguien vea a la Reina de Zeta en tu maletero..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1335
translate spanish d19d_542b320c:

    # Q "So... do you think you can bring me along that easily?"
    Q "Entonces... ¿crees que puedes llevarme así de fácil?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1336
translate spanish d19d_01503437:

    # Q "I might have not thought this through that much after all."
    Q "Puede que al final no lo haya pensado tan bien."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1339
translate spanish d19d_f10bb418:

    # S "We will manage, [persistent.dad] always says to roll with the punches."
    S "Nos las arreglaremos, [persistent.dad] siempre dice que hay que adaptarse a los golpes."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1342
translate spanish d19d_541d69f1:

    # S "It will be fun to watch you cope without servants and guards ready to throw their lives away to bring you a cup of tea..."
    S "Será divertido verte arreglártelas sin sirvientes ni guardias dispuestos a dar la vida por traerte una taza de té..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1345
translate spanish d19d_b16e440d:

    # Q "I mean... don't think I have never been on an adventure like this! I have made {i}countless{/i} trips to the outside..."
    Q "Oye... ¡no creas que nunca he estado en una aventura así! He hecho {i}incontables{/i} viajes al exterior..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1346
translate spanish d19d_6148f29e:

    # S "Without the guards?"
    S "¿Sin guardias?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1347
translate spanish d19d_d1d34329:

    # Q "Um..."
    Q "Eh..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1348
translate spanish d19d_08f54e47:

    # S "...and glamour?"
    S "... ¿y sin glamour?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1349
translate spanish d19d_c610cdee:

    # Q "Look... there's a first time for everything, alright? And it's not like I have been trained only in paperwork and prayers."
    Q "Mira... siempre hay una primera vez para todo, ¿vale? Y no es que me hayan entrenado solo en papeleo y oraciones."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1354
translate spanish d19d_6a4c582a:

    # Z "Alright, ladies... Considering the circumstances, we have a change of plans."
    Z "Muy bien, damas... Teniendo en cuenta las circunstancias, tenemos un cambio de planes."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1355
translate spanish d19d_bfbd0cbc:

    # Z "We will spend our nights here, away from the settlements."
    Z "Pasaremos las noches aquí, lejos de los asentamientos."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1359
translate spanish d19d_20fd986c:

    # "Later that evening..."
    "Más tarde esa misma noche..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1363
translate spanish d19d_c4ae1e14:

    # "The air is getting colder, and the lantern in your tent will soon be the only thing visible for a long way in every direction."
    "El aire se vuelve más frío, y la linterna en tu tienda pronto será lo único visible a lo largo de un buen trecho en todas las direcciones."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1364
translate spanish d19d_ae58893f:

    # "Hidden amongst the ruins, you wait for the girls to join you, so you can all prepare for the coming day, which promises to be eventful."
    "Escondido entre las ruinas, esperas a que las chicas se unan a ti, para que todos podáis prepararos para el día que viene, que promete ser movido."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1367
translate spanish d19d_19f7b1e3:

    # Q "[S]? Are you coming?"
    Q "¿[S]? ¿Vienes?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1370
translate spanish d19d_47d0c294:

    # S "Yes... just... ngh..."
    S "Sí... solo... ngh..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1371
translate spanish d19d_a96e7627:

    # S "Give me a moment, okay!"
    S "¡Dame un momento, ¿vale?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1374
translate spanish d19d_4302c644:

    # Q "Whatever you're doing, your [persistent.dad] is asking for you."
    Q "Hagas lo que hagas, tu [persistent.dad] te está llamando."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1377
translate spanish d19d_408086bf:

    # S "Well, tell my [persistent.dad] he's a lovely man, but that he should have let me pack the trunk this time."
    S "Pues dile a mi [persistent.dad] que es un hombre encantador, pero que esta vez debería haberme dejado hacer el equipaje."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1380
translate spanish d19d_94afa018:

    # S "I'm looking for some of the water canteens...-"
    S "Estoy buscando algunas cantimploras de agua..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1381
translate spanish d19d_778e5513:

    # S "Oh there you are..."
    S "Oh, aquí estás..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1384
translate spanish d19d_c59adcc7:

    # S "On my way. Anything else you guys need?"
    S "Ya voy. ¿Necesitáis algo más?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1387
translate spanish d19d_68f206c9:

    # Q "Yeah... the scrolls, remember?"
    Q "Sí... los pergaminos, ¿recuerdas?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1390
translate spanish d19d_34f46930:

    # S "Oh, right..."
    S "Ah, cierto..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1394
translate spanish d19d_bdc61a01:

    # Q "..."
    Q "..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1397
translate spanish d19d_919e3b16:

    # Q "I can see you checking me out, [persistent.player_name]..."
    Q "Puedo ver que me estás mirando, [persistent.player_name]..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1400
translate spanish d19d_b3240418:

    # Z "Is that a bad thing?"
    Z "¿Eso es algo malo?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1403
translate spanish d19d_738b22bd:

    # Q "No... not really."
    Q "No... no realmente."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1408
translate spanish d19d_213176f2:

    # S "There you go."
    S "Aquí tienes."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1411
translate spanish d19d_13e687b3:

    # S "So... Now that you're officially travelling with us, I have to ask..."
    S "Entonces... ahora que viajas oficialmente con nosotros, tengo que preguntar..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1412
translate spanish d19d_0d8f15d8:

    # S "What do I call you by? Because last time I checked, Queen Merneith is merely a title."
    S "¿Cómo debo llamarte? Porque la última vez que lo comprobé, Reina Merneith era solo un título."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1415
translate spanish d19d_ac9fff8b:

    # Q "But it's appropriate, isn't it?"
    Q "Pero es apropiado, ¿no?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1418
translate spanish d19d_faeaccbc:

    # S "Nope, no chance. I'm not going to call you that out here. You don't want to be identified, do you?"
    S "No, ni de broma. No voy a llamarte así aquí afuera. No querrás ser identificada, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1423
translate spanish d19d_7c885117:

    # Q "Well, in that case... you call me Neith."
    Q "Bueno, en ese caso... llámame Neith."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1426
translate spanish d19d_eb59eb18:

    # S "...Neith?"
    S "... ¿Neith?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1429
translate spanish d19d_a47001df:

    # Z "Neith? As in the Goddess of creation, Neith?!"
    Z "¿Neith?, ¡¿como la Diosa de la creación, Neith?!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1432
translate spanish d19d_5caf72bd:

    # Ne "Yes... why be a chosen of Neith, as I am sure you know is one of my titles, if you can be the goddess herself?"
    Ne "Sí... ¿por qué ser una elegida de Neith, que como sabes es uno de mis títulos, si puedes ser la diosa misma?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1435
translate spanish d19d_98b5f53a:

    # Ne "Besides... it's just a name for you to use. And I never had my own name anyway."
    Ne "Además... es solo un nombre para que uses. Y en realidad nunca tuve un nombre propio."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1438
translate spanish d19d_bc20e9a3:

    # S "We should make sure nobody catches the Queen of Zeta engaging in blasphemy.."
    S "Deberíamos asegurarnos de que nadie pille a la Reina de Zeta cometiendo blasfemia..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1441
translate spanish d19d_ba29cf59:

    # Ne "Growing up at the Palace, I learned quickly that there is a reason why most rules are indeed for thee, but not for me."
    Ne "Creciendo en el Palacio, aprendí rápido que hay una razón por la que la mayoría de las reglas son para los demás, pero no para mí."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1444
translate spanish d19d_e54bcdd0:

    # Ne "In the end, if I am the one saying it, is it really blasphemy?"
    Ne "Al final, si soy yo quien lo dice, ¿realmente es blasfemia?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1447
translate spanish d19d_56c827dc:

    # S "{i}*giggles*{/i}"
    S "{i}*risilla*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1448
translate spanish d19d_ad7a5a56:

    # Z "Alright, [S], {i}Neith{/i}... come sit down."
    Z "Muy bien, [S], {i}Neith{/i}... venir, sentaros."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1451
translate spanish d19d_0cca8624:

    # "Moments later..."
    "Momentos después..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1454
translate spanish d19d_212f32a4:

    # Z "Okay, what am I looking at... faint walls, and a monument in the center..."
    Z "Bien, ¿qué estoy viendo...? Muros desvanecidos y un monumento en el centro..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1455
translate spanish d19d_a2ff7e02:

    # Z "That must be the hub you were talking about?"
    Z "¿Ese debe ser el centro del que hablabas?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1456
translate spanish d19d_f11263c6:

    # Ne "Yes. The most prominent settlement in this region. Ruled by a free trader, he has his own security enforcers."
    Ne "Sí. El asentamiento más importante de esta región. Gobernado por un comerciante libre, tiene a sus propios guardias de seguridad."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1457
translate spanish d19d_1758cacf:

    # Ne "Like many settlements and bazaars in the belt region, he gets to do whatever he wants, as long as he pays his tax and lets my soldiers pass."
    Ne "Al igual que en muchos asentamientos y zocos de la región del cinturón, puede hacer lo que quiera, siempre y cuando pague sus impuestos y deje pasar a mis soldados."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1460
translate spanish d19d_a5e9e45b:

    # Z "The odds are at least some of these people have come to Zeta in the past, and likely know your face... and you know what that means."
    Z "Es probable que al menos algunos de esta gente haya ido a Zeta en el pasado, y seguramente conozcan tu rostro... y sabes lo que eso significa."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1463
translate spanish d19d_a210e6ee:

    # Ne "Yes... I suppose I will have to wait here for your return."
    Ne "Sí... supongo que tendré que esperar aquí a que volváis."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1466
translate spanish d19d_371b4c24:

    # Z "I don't think leaving you alone is a good idea either."
    Z "Tampoco creo que dejarte sola sea buena idea."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1467
translate spanish d19d_42f1a825:

    # Z "I understand this is not what you had in mind, but you're too important. I will not risk the ruler of Zeta being caught like a common stray by some roving bandits. Not on my watch."
    Z "Entiendo que no es lo que tenías en mente, pero eres demasiado importante. No arriesgaré que la gobernante de Zeta sea capturada como una vagabunda por unos bandidos errantes. No mientras yo esté al mando."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1470
translate spanish d19d_1a8fb43a:

    # Ne "Oh my, I knew I was important, but this is the first time I actually hear it from you..."
    Ne "Vaya... sabía que era importante, pero es la primera vez que lo escucho de ti..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1473
translate spanish d19d_ddb141fa:

    # Z "I'm serious... I think it's best that I should go alone."
    Z "Hablo en serio... creo que lo mejor es que vaya yo solo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1476
translate spanish d19d_83724f47:

    # S "Why not me? Perhaps they're more responsive to a young charming woman?"
    S "¿Por qué no yo? Quizá reaccionen mejor ante una joven encantadora."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1479
translate spanish d19d_bf38ff92:

    # Z "Perhaps..."
    Z "Tal vez..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1483
translate spanish d19d_5ab3574d:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1484
translate spanish d19d_7a2f536d:

    # Z "Yeah... I will think about it."
    Z "Sí... lo pensaré."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1487
translate spanish d19d_a02aad74:

    # S "[persistent.dad!c], I am serious. Intimidation doesn't need to be the only way..."
    S "[persistent.dad!c], lo digo en serio. La intimidación no tiene por qué ser la única forma..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1492
translate spanish d19d_576fd833:

    # Ne "Well, intimidation does have its place, sometimes..."
    Ne "Bueno, la intimidación también tiene su lugar, a veces..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1495
translate spanish d19d_9101e082:

    # Ne "Don't you feel suitably impressed, when your [persistent.dad] is huffing and puffing his chest?"
    Ne "¿Acaso no te impresiona lo suficiente cuando tu [persistent.dad] resopla y saca pecho?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1498
translate spanish d19d_56c827dc_1:

    # S "{i}*giggles*{/i}"
    S "{i}*risilla*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1499
translate spanish d19d_515b3815:

    # S "I am sure I don't know what you're talking about..."
    S "Estoy segura de que no sé de qué hablas..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1502
translate spanish d19d_05d876fd:

    # Ne "Is that so..."
    Ne "¿Ah, sí...?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1505
translate spanish d19d_ee3248ce:

    # Ne "...you don't mind if I get ready for bed while we talk, right?"
    Ne "... no te importa si me preparo para dormir mientras hablamos, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1508
translate spanish d19d_c85e8e75:

    # Z "Be my guest..."
    Z "Siéntete como en tu casa..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1511
translate spanish d19d_f82c82a3:

    # Z "Okay, what's this..."
    Z "Vale, ¿y esto qué es...?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1512
translate spanish d19d_9fb4f4bc:

    # Z "\"The oldest living neighbour in the area.\""
    Z "\"El vecino más anciano de la zona.\""

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1515
translate spanish d19d_90f675d7:

    # S "Some sort of lone wolf in the desert? Perhaps he's knowledgeable, I assume?"
    S "¿Algún tipo de lobo solitario en el desierto? Supongo que debe ser sabio, ¿no?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1518
translate spanish d19d_6ad92cb9:

    # Ne "According to our records, he has frequent interactions with our trading caravans."
    Ne "Según nuestros registros, tiene frecuentes tratos con nuestras caravanas comerciales."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1521
translate spanish d19d_fb65e183:

    # Ne "It is unlikely he's trading wares worthy of a caravan stop."
    Ne "Es poco probable que comercie con bienes que justifiquen una parada de caravanas."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1522
translate spanish d19d_569c8f85:

    # Ne "But if he has information, it's worth seeking him out."
    Ne "Pero si tiene información, vale la pena visitarlo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1525
translate spanish d19d_89c3c779:

    # Z "I see."
    Z "Ya veo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1528
translate spanish d19d_845fd8df:

    # Z "I think you two can stay here for this one. I think I will have more of a chance."
    Z "Creo que vosotras dos podéis quedaros aquí en esta ocasión. Creo que yo tendré más posibilidades."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1529
translate spanish d19d_7805bc06:

    # Z "Perhaps I can convince him to share some secrets, if he has any to share."
    Z "Quizá pueda convencerlo de compartir algunos secretos, si es que tiene."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1532
translate spanish d19d_1afe242a:

    # S "Perhaps he responds better to someone with more life experience. I don't think I'll object on this one."
    S "Quizá responda mejor a alguien con más experiencia de vida. No creo que me oponga en esta ocasión."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1539
translate spanish d19d_00a230c7:

    # Ne "Maybe you tell him that the Queen of Zeta is hoping to reward you for your efforts..."
    Ne "Quizá le digas que la Reina de Zeta espera recompensarte por tus esfuerzos..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1542
translate spanish d19d_5ab3574d_1:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1543
translate spanish d19d_3a1d57f8:

    # "Despite the circumstances, you clearly sense the flirty undertones of her voice, and you can't help but stare at her for a long moment."
    "A pesar de las circunstancias, percibes claramente el tono coqueto en su voz, y no puedes evitar quedarte mirándola un largo instante."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1544
translate spanish d19d_02c3157b:

    # S "So what's the third one?"
    S "Entonces, ¿cuál es el tercero?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1550
translate spanish d19d_3b61f554:

    # Z "Yeah, uhm..."
    Z "Sí, ehm..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1552
translate spanish d19d_ede3167f:

    # Z "Let's see..."
    Z "Veamos..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1553
translate spanish d19d_c9def78d:

    # Z "Ruins. Could this be the Elder's residence?"
    Z "Ruinas. ¿Podría ser esta la residencia del Anciano?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1554
translate spanish d19d_07f5bda0:

    # Ne "No. I am told this place is older still, and it doesn't fit the description."
    Ne "No. Me dijeron que este lugar es aún más antiguo, y no encaja con la descripción."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1555
translate spanish d19d_e35c79a7:

    # Ne "I can't even tell if this was actually ever in use."
    Ne "Ni siquiera puedo decir si alguna vez llegó a usarse."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1556
translate spanish d19d_7019cea5:

    # Ne "And now, more than a hundred years later, there is barely anything left."
    Ne "Y ahora, más de cien años después, apenas queda nada."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1558
translate spanish d19d_81bb92c1:

    # Ne "Judging by the type of architecture however..."
    Ne "Aunque, juzgando por el tipo de arquitectura..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1559
translate spanish d19d_2f7f5e9f:

    # "She pauses..."
    "Ella hace una pausa..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1562
translate spanish d19d_29dd1d74:

    # Ne "...I hope that there is still something to discover."
    Ne "... espero que aún haya algo por descubrir."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1565
translate spanish d19d_aabc21cc:

    # Z "...uncover indeed."
    Z "... descubrir, sin duda."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1568
translate spanish d19d_df5c0b36:

    # "Her hands slowly scour her lower abdomen..."
    "Sus manos recorren lentamente su bajo vientre..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1569
translate spanish d19d_2e99de4e:

    # "...she has your attention, now."
    "... ahora sí que tiene tu atención."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1572
translate spanish d19d_61836b52:

    # Ne "I think that should be enough of that for tonight, don't you agree?"
    Ne "Creo que eso es suficiente por esta noche, ¿no crees?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1573
translate spanish d19d_7d485899:

    # Ne "Sneaking away from my quarters took a lot of effort, and I am getting all sleepy..."
    Ne "Escabullirme de mis aposentos me costó bastante, y ahora me está entrando sueño..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1576
translate spanish d19d_b775abb3:

    # Ne "I wonder... does any one of you mind giving me a leg massage?"
    Ne "Me pregunto... ¿alguno de vosotros quiere darme un masaje en las piernas?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1577
translate spanish d19d_580e4d57:

    # Ne "...I have been running a lot today."
    Ne "...hoy he corrido mucho."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1580
translate spanish d19d_bfcc7648:

    # "You can't help but find her suddenly demure behaviour refreshing and enticing. The only appropriate answer is..."
    "No puedes evitar que su repentino comportamiento tímido te resulte refrescante y tentador. La única respuesta adecuada es..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1581
translate spanish d19d_6120acc2:

    # Z "Yes... I will."
    Z "Sí... yo lo haré."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1584
translate spanish d19d_9b327276:

    # S "Have you no shame, trying to hog my [persistent.dad] like that?"
    S "¿No tienes vergüenza, intentando acaparar a mi [persistent.dad] así?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1587
translate spanish d19d_5df71100:

    # Ne "So...? Are you saying you wouldn't do the same??"
    Ne "¿Y...? ¿Acaso dices que tú no harías lo mismo??"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1590
translate spanish d19d_7092cd27:

    # Ne "I'm just a tired Queen hoping for some relief for my sore legs. Is that so wrong.?"
    Ne "Solo soy una Reina cansada que espera un poco de alivio para sus piernas doloridas. ¿Está tan mal?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1593
translate spanish d19d_f4f19251:

    # Ne "What if I were to take my skirt off and lay down. Would you give me a hand?"
    Ne "¿Y si me quitara la falda y me tumbara? ¿Me echarías una mano?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1596
translate spanish d19d_36b24e4d:

    # Z "Why not? I think we're done here anyway."
    Z "¿Por qué no? Creo que ya hemos terminado aquí de todos modos."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1599
translate spanish d19d_b1362e03:

    # Ne "See? He agrees."
    Ne "¿Lo ves? El está de acuerdo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1602
translate spanish d19d_9be4275b:

    # S "Yeah... I'm sure he does."
    S "Sí... Estoy segura de que sí."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1605
translate spanish d19d_a5a9131b:

    # Ne "Hm..."
    Ne "Hm..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1607
translate spanish d19d_a790b443:

    # Ne "Judging by the type of architecture however, I hope that there is still something to discover."
    Ne "Aunque, juzgando por el tipo de arquitectura, espero que aún haya algo por descubrir."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1610
translate spanish d19d_0d2c95c1:

    # Ne "Anyway, I think that should be enough of that for tonight, don't you agree?"
    Ne "En fin, creo que eso es suficiente por esta noche, ¿no crees?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1611
translate spanish d19d_7d485899_1:

    # Ne "Sneaking away from my quarters took a lot of effort, and I am getting all sleepy..."
    Ne "Escabullirme de mis aposentos me costó bastante, y ahora me está entrando sueño..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1614
translate spanish d19d_587e6042:

    # "She lays down on the other side of the tent..."
    "Se tumba al otro lado de la tienda..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1617
translate spanish d19d_47624b7e:

    # Ne "This is a good spot."
    Ne "Este es un buen sitio."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1620
translate spanish d19d_c07a3678:

    # Ne "Hnnnngh...!"
    Ne "¡Hnnnngh...!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1623
translate spanish d19d_b039f360:

    # Ne "Mh..."
    Ne "Mh..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1626
translate spanish d19d_3cd1364b:

    # Ne "I am relaxed, now, and ready for my massage."
    Ne "Ahora sí que estoy relajada... y lista para mi masaje."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1629
translate spanish d19d_7ae2fc74:

    # Zt "...she's back to being a spoiled Queen. That didn't take long..."
    Zt "...ell avolvió a ser una Reina mimada. No tardó mucho..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1633
translate spanish d19d_c0ebc222:

    # Ne "As I said, my legs are quite sore. I would appreciate your focus on them, today."
    Ne "Como dije, tengo las piernas bastante adoloridas. Agradecería que te concentraras en ellas hoy."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1635
translate spanish d19d_e81b1918:

    # Ne "My legs are quite sore. I would appreciate your focus on them, today."
    Ne "Mis piernas están bastante doloridas. Agradecería que te concentres en ellas hoy."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1639
translate spanish d19d_ff518ef8:

    # Ne "Go on..."
    Ne "Vamos..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1643
translate spanish d19d_89af00c1:

    # Ne "...I don't think I need to convince you."
    Ne "... no creo que necesite convencerte."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1644
translate spanish d19d_57f76457:

    # Zt "Godbless... those legs!"
    Zt "Dios bendiga... ¡esas piernas!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1646
translate spanish d19d_a45fd9bc:

    # Ne "...A man like you should have no issues with it."
    Ne "... Un hombre como tú no debería tener problemas con eso."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1649
translate spanish d19d_7e974cce:

    # Z "Excuse me, [S], apparently our royal guest needs special accomodations..."
    Z "Discúlpame, [S], al parecer nuestra invitada real necesita atenciones especiales..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1652
translate spanish d19d_5fa2931b:

    # "You move towards and kneel next to Neith..."
    "Te acercas y te arrodillas junto a Neith..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1655
translate spanish d19d_0d2591ef:

    # Z "A leg massage, you say. It does sound like you're missing your servants already."
    Z "¿Un masaje en las piernas, dices? Suena como si ya echaras de menos a tus sirvientes."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1656
translate spanish d19d_8cc36959:

    # Ne "{i}*she pouts*{/i}"
    Ne "{i}*hace un puchero*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1659
translate spanish d19d_c8f91c7c:

    # Z "So you want me to fill in for them, hm?"
    Z "Así que quieres que los reemplace, ¿eh?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1662
translate spanish d19d_9a3a4e28:

    # Ne "I would hope so. I am sure you have some talent, in that area."
    Ne "Eso espero. Estoy segura de que tienes talento en esa área."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1665
translate spanish d19d_b9f4daff:

    # Z "You know I do."
    Z "Sabes que sí."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1670
translate spanish d19d_795c4e99:

    # Z "Listen, {i}Neith{/i}. You're not in the palace anymore. In fact, springing this surprise on us... You're lucky I don't send you packing."
    Z "Escucha, {i}Neith{/i}. Ya no estás en el palacio. De hecho, al sorprendernos con esto... tienes suerte de que no te mande de vuelta."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1673
translate spanish d19d_614a2a3c:

    # Ne "..."
    Ne "..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1674
translate spanish d19d_8911254c:

    # Z "If you are going to be with us, at least try to be less of an entitled brat."
    Z "Si vas a estar con nosotros, al menos intenta ser menos una mocosa mimada."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1677
translate spanish d19d_6652f0a0:

    # Ne "You are right. Still, will you help me?"
    Ne "Tienes razón. Aun así, ¿me ayudarás?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1680
translate spanish d19d_fb8d4f4c:

    # Z "Of course I will."
    Z "Por supuesto que sí."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1684
translate spanish d19d_4a33df5d:

    # "You look for a moment at her quite muscular thighs, lost in thought."
    "Miras por un momento sus muslos bastante musculosos, perdido en tus pensamientos."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1685
translate spanish d19d_ee50a5ae:

    # "Surprise changes to your circumstances are nothing new to you, after so many years on the road."
    "Los cambios inesperados en tus circunstancias no son nada nuevo para ti, después de tantos años en el camino."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1686
translate spanish d19d_8e114fc8:

    # "This one however, you realise, could backfire spectacularly. You resolve to appease the young Queen, for now."
    "Aunque este, lo sabes bien, podría salir terriblemente mal. Decides complacer a la joven Reina, por ahora."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1689
translate spanish d19d_e711dd5e:

    # "As you run your hands over her legs, you can feel a few tight knots and start applying yourself on them."
    "Mientras deslizas tus manos por sus piernas, sientes algunos nudos tensos y comienzas a trabajar sobre ellos."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1690
translate spanish d19d_a86a19a0:

    # Ne "Oh... yes, there..."
    Ne "Oh... sí, ahí..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1693
translate spanish d19d_0bd01c15:

    # Z "Does it hurt if I do this? Let me know if you prefer me to put less pressure."
    Z "¿Duele si hago esto? Avísame si prefieres que ponga menos presión."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1694
translate spanish d19d_9a78ede9:

    # Ne "No, no... it's what I need."
    Ne "No, no... justo lo que necesito."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1697
translate spanish d19d_48805bf4:

    # Z "Did you run all the way to our place, today?"
    Z "¿Corriste todo el camino hasta nuestra casa, hoy?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1698
translate spanish d19d_a5c50e3b:

    # Ne "Mostly yes... mh..."
    Ne "En su mayoría sí... mh..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1699
translate spanish d19d_723c4be1:

    # Ne "...I didn't want to... be noticed."
    Ne "... no quería... ser vista."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1702
translate spanish d19d_5969c00b:

    # Ne "Ah, yes...!"
    Ne "¡Ah, sí...!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1703
translate spanish d19d_4cd022a9:

    # Zt "And now, the other leg..."
    Zt "Y ahora, la otra pierna..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1704
translate spanish d19d_30ae9ee6:

    # Ne "Gods... this is nice... I'm getting sleepy."
    Ne "Dioses... esto está bien... me estoy quedando dormida."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1707
translate spanish d19d_489b3dd6:

    # Ne "I will close my eyes for a bit, if you don't mind..."
    Ne "Voy a cerrar los ojos un rato, si no te importa..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1710
translate spanish d19d_f8c8ec8e:

    # "You let your silence be your reply, as you watch the young woman relax under your ministrations."
    "Dejas que tu silencio sea la respuesta, mientras observas a la joven relajarse bajo tus caricias."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1713
translate spanish d19d_d196ec3c:

    # Ne "Mhh..."
    Ne "Mhh..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1716
translate spanish d19d_f0bc9cb5:

    # Zt "Back to this spot..."
    Zt "De vuelta a este punto..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1717
translate spanish d19d_580cc58a:

    # Ne "I think... I won't last long, [persistent.player_name]..."
    Ne "Creo... que no aguantaré mucho, [persistent.player_name]..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1720
translate spanish d19d_a5a9131b_1:

    # Ne "Hm..."
    Ne "Hm..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1721
translate spanish d19d_3f7bbca1:

    # "You use less strength as you keep kneading her muscles..."
    "Usas menos fuerza mientras sigues amasando sus músculos..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1724
translate spanish d19d_971a98df:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1727
translate spanish d19d_614a2a3c_1:

    # Ne "..."
    Ne "..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1728
translate spanish d19d_bec63512:

    # "Before you know it, \"Neith\" is already snoozing gently."
    "Antes de darte cuenta, \"Neith\" ya está dormida suavemente."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1731
translate spanish d19d_45709312:

    # Zw "Well... that was easy..."
    Zw "Bueno... eso fue fácil..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1734
translate spanish d19d_0a2e2cc4:

    # Sw "Uhm... [persistent.dad], can I ask something...?"
    Sw "Uhm... [persistent.dad], ¿puedo preguntarte algo...?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1741
translate spanish d19d_957e3e94:

    # "You turn around, and find your [persistent.da] suspiciously lean forward..."
    "Te giras y ves a tu [persistent.da] inclinada hacia delante de forma sospechosa..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1743
translate spanish d19d_c18fbd2d:

    # "You turn around, and find [S] suspiciously lean forward..."
    "Te giras y ves a [S] inclinada hacia delante de forma sospechosa..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1744
translate spanish d19d_5ab3574d_2:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1750
translate spanish d19d_ec5f4231:

    # Sw "Would you mind giving me one, too...?"
    Sw "¿Te importaría darme uno a mí también...?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1753
translate spanish d19d_01fde1f4:

    # Zw "Are we feeling a little jealous?"
    Zw "¿Nos sentimos un poco celosas?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1756
translate spanish d19d_f7288b51:

    # S "I don't know. Would it get me a massage if I was?"
    S "No lo sé. ¿Me darían un masaje si lo hiciera?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1759
translate spanish d19d_4ae13ef7:

    # S "...Would it?"
    S "... ¿Lo haría?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1762
translate spanish d19d_b341b552:

    # Z "It would."
    Z "Sí lo haría."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1765
translate spanish d19d_a9d42e34:

    # S "So that's a yes, then?"
    S "Entonces es un sí, ¿no?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1766
translate spanish d19d_f3c060f9:

    # "She smiles confidently..."
    "Ella sonríe con seguridad..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1769
translate spanish d19d_f55efeea:

    # Z "Lay down already."
    Z "Túmbate de una vez."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1772
translate spanish d19d_2efa0c89:

    # "It doesn't take long for [S] to succumb to the same slumber as her royal companion. You stay awake a little longer, keeping guard, but you don't see any signs of peril."
    "No pasa mucho tiempo hasta que [S] sucumbe al mismo sueño que su compañera real. Te quedas despierto un poco más, montando guardia, pero no ves señales de peligro."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1773
translate spanish d19d_8eee6322:

    # "Finally, you too manage to fall asleep for the rest of the night."
    "Finalmente, tú también logras dormir el resto de la noche."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1775
translate spanish d19d_4cc5803e:

    # "The next morning..."
    "A la mañana siguiente..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:1778
translate spanish d19d_b1aeb283:

