# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2735
translate spanish d19e61_c65a784c:

    # "Looking to the right, [S] spots another figure lying on an expensive couch."
    "Mirando hacia la derecha, [S] ve otra figura recostada en un lujoso diván."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2738
translate spanish d19e61_6035f7db:

    # St "Is that his concubine? Must be..."
    St "¿Esa es su concubina? Debe de serlo..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2741
translate spanish d19e61_44d43825:

    # St "She's looking at me. Why is everyone in this place staring at me today?!"
    St "Me está mirando. ¡¿Por qué todo el mundo en este lugar me mira hoy?!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2744
translate spanish d19e61_9b7e813a:

    # "The girl looks over to her right, in the direction of the chief..."
    "La chica mira hacia su derecha, en dirección al jefe..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2745
translate spanish d19e61_d3b6b5dc:

    # St "Maybe she's waiting for me to introduce myself."
    St "Tal vez espera que me presente."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2748
translate spanish d19e61_70228f8c:

    # S "{i}Ahem...{/i} I need to wake up the chief."
    S "{i}Ejem...{/i} Necesito despertar al jefe."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2751
translate spanish d19e61_79ad9d4a:

    # S "Excuse me, can you wake up for a second?"
    S "Perdona, ¿puedes despertarte un momento?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2754
translate spanish d19e61_2386c2b9:

    # C2 "Ngghhhaaa..."
    C2 "Ngghhhaaa..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2755
translate spanish d19e61_0ac10564:

    # "He enhales deeply and loud..."
    "Inhala profunda y ruidosamente..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2756
translate spanish d19e61_8a5306bf:

    # S "Helloo... do you hear me?"
    S "Holaaa... ¿me escuchas?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2757
translate spanish d19e61_abb123c2:

    # S "{i}*sigh*{/i}"
    S "{i}*suspiro*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2760
translate spanish d19e61_546c87c4:

    # C2 "Kgh...?"
    C2 "¿Kgh...?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2761
translate spanish d19e61_72507dd8:

    # C2 "Who is..."
    C2 "¿Quién es...?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2764
translate spanish d19e61_92d81f05:

    # C2 "Oh, I fell asleep again, didn't I?"
    C2 "Oh, me quedé dormido otra vez, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2767
translate spanish d19e61_14643476:

    # C2 "H-hello, pretty lady. Just give me a moment to get up."
    C2 "H-hola, linda dama. Solo dame un momento para levantarme."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2770
translate spanish d19e61_00098b83:

    # St "Here we go..."
    St "Aquí vamos..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2773
translate spanish d19e61_cf68489b:

    # S "I don't want to interrupt your nap, sir, but I come in the name of the Palace."
    S "No quiero interrumpir su siesta, señor, pero vengo en nombre del Palacio."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2774
translate spanish d19e61_cb94a24d:

    # "He moans loudly as he gets up with obvious discomfort..."
    "Gime fuerte mientras se levanta con evidente incomodidad..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2777
translate spanish d19e61_c0d2c9d6:

    # C2 "You... speak for the Palace?"
    C2 "¿Tú... hablas por el Palacio?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2778
translate spanish d19e61_3831d7dc:

    # C2 "Then we should introduce ourselves properly."
    C2 "Entonces deberíamos presentarnos como corresponde."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2781
translate spanish d19e61_fb9a5c81:

    # St "Fine... whatever."
    St "Bien... lo que sea."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2784
translate spanish d19e61_a3b63a42:

    # C2 "My name is Domitius. I own this cozy little place. Other people address me by my title, but what is a title? Just Domitius will do."
    C2 "Mi nombre es Domitius. Soy dueño de este acogedor lugar. Otros me llaman por mi título, pero ¿qué es un título? Solo Domitius está bien."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2785
translate spanish d19e61_b1ccbb74:

    # Domi "...and who are you?"
    Domi "... ¿y tú quién eres?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2788
translate spanish d19e61_15ff0fde:

    # S "[S]. I'm a Stalker, charged by your Queen, Merneith, blessed be her name, ruler by divine right of the city of Zeta and all its domains."
    S "[S]. Soy una Acechadora, enviada por su Reina, Merneith, bendito sea su nombre, soberana por derecho divino de la ciudad de Zeta y todos sus dominios."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2789
translate spanish d19e61_57c5d281:

    # S "I was told by her, that maybe you could help me find something."
    S "Ella me dijo que quizá podrías ayudarme a encontrar algo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2792
translate spanish d19e61_ee331fd3:

    # Domi "The Queen knows about me? Well, of course, why wouldn't she?! How exciting!"
    Domi "¿La Reina sabe de mí? ¡Pues claro, por qué no habría de hacerlo?! ¡Qué emocionante!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2795
translate spanish d19e61_5777be7b:

    # Domi "Sit with me, pretty Stalker. Let's have a chat."
    Domi "Siéntate conmigo, linda Acechadora. Charlemos un rato."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2796
translate spanish d19e61_b970faac:

    # Domi "Don't worry, I mean no harm. The wasteland ends where my tent begins, as I always say."
    Domi "No te preocupes, no pretendo hacerte daño. El yermo termina donde empieza mi tienda, como siempre digo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2801
translate spanish d19e61_3e7e5c14:

    # St "Sitting next to him? That's not suspicious..."
    St "¿Sentarme junto a él? Sí, nada sospechoso..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2802
translate spanish d19e61_39217e2a:

    # St "At least he's not aggressive or disrespectful, like that guy before. And yet..."
    St "Al menos no es agresivo ni irrespetuoso, como el tipo de antes. Y aun así..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2808
translate spanish d19e89_5093afe6:

    # S "I don't really have time to sit down for this. I am on something of a schedule."
    S "Realmente no tengo tiempo para sentarme a esto. Tengo un horario que seguir."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2809
translate spanish d19e89_f448cd86:

    # S "You can just answer my question, and I could pay in gold, if you desire compensation."
    S "Solo tienes que responder a mi pregunta y, si deseas una compensación, te pagaré en oro."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2812
translate spanish d19e89_19445a34:

    # Domi "Oh... I am sorry, but I do insist on talking face to face, when discussing important matters. The Queen wants something?"
    Domi "Oh... Lo siento, pero insisto en hablar cara a cara cuando se trata de asuntos importantes. ¿La Reina quiere algo?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2813
translate spanish d19e89_aaf84f59:

    # Domi "The choice is yours, pretty lady. Will you let me help you?"
    Domi "La elección es tuya, linda dama. ¿Me dejarás ayudarte?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2816
translate spanish d19e89_22fc6214:

    # St "He's insisting, great."
    St "Está insistiendo, genial."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2820
translate spanish d19e89_5cac8f4c:

    # St "I'm not sure about this, but I don't want to lose the opportunity."
    St "No estoy segura de esto, pero no quiero perder la oportunidad."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2823
translate spanish d19e89_a9a33d1d:

    # S "Sure... let us sit together. But you should know that time is of essence for me."
    S "De acuerdo... sentémonos juntos. Pero debería saber que el tiempo es esencial para mí."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2826
translate spanish d19e89_5bf1c269:

    # S "Perfect. Come, you can sit with me."
    S "Perfecto. Ven, puedes sentarte conmigo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2829
translate spanish d19e89_0cca8624:

    # "Moments later..."
    "Unos instantes después..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2832
translate spanish d19e89_2ddf2746:

    # St "This was a mistake..."
    St "Esto fue un error..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2835
translate spanish d19e89_9859771c:

    # St "He's just sitting there, looking at me."
    St "Solo está sentado ahí, mirándome."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2838
translate spanish d19e89_3489e0e2:

    # Domi "Now that we sit together, I can see that you are a nice girl. What is a Stalker looking for in this place?"
    Domi "Ahora que estamos sentados juntos, puedo ver que eres una buena chica. ¿Qué busca una Acechadora en este lugar?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2839
translate spanish d19e89_68a78144:

    # S "I am looking for the remains of an old temple. It is supposed to be the last residence of one of the founders of Zeta."
    S "Estoy buscando los restos de un antiguo templo. Se supone que fue la última residencia de uno de los fundadores de Zeta."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2840
translate spanish d19e89_d74378cd:

    # Domi "I might know how to find the place you are talking about."
    Domi "Podría saber cómo encontrar el lugar del que hablas."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2841
translate spanish d19e89_6599397f:

    # Domi "Over time, the many caravans and traders visiting my little corner of the desert have shared their knowledge of the surroundings. I have compiled their tales into a map."
    Domi "Con el tiempo, muchas caravanas y comerciantes que han visitado mi pequeño rincón del desierto han compartido su conocimiento de los alrededores. He recopilado sus historias en un mapa."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2842
translate spanish d19e89_d7008180:

    # Domi "But what do you think you will find there, that hasn't been pillaged yet, over the years?"
    Domi "Pero ¿qué crees que encontrarás allí, que no haya sido saqueado ya con los años?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2845
translate spanish d19e89_0c7bef59:

    # St "He might be a slob, but if I was standing next to him, he would be towering over me in every way..."
    St "Podrá ser un cerdo, pero si estuviera de pie junto a él, me superaría en todos los sentidos..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2848
translate spanish d19e89_7983e817:

    # S "I don't presume to know the Queen's reasons for wanting to find the place."
    S "No me atrevo a presumir cuáles son las razones de la Reina para querer encontrar el lugar."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2851
translate spanish d19e89_b8bbb4ce:

    # St "I shouldn't tell him about the Elder's hidden cave."
    St "No debería contarle sobre la cueva oculta del Anciano."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2854
translate spanish d19e89_9c04d35f:

    # Domi "I have met other Stalkers, pretty lady. They don't seem to care too much about Zeta."
    Domi "He conocido a otros Acechadores, linda dama. No parecen preocuparse demasiado por Zeta."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2855
translate spanish d19e89_4df0e163:

    # Domi "I once hired one to find mushrooms for me. He failed to find them."
    Domi "Una vez contraté a uno para que me buscara hongos. No logró encontrarlos."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2856
translate spanish d19e89_30770880:

    # Domi "Very disappointing..."
    Domi "Muy decepcionante..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2857
translate spanish d19e89_9bc52771:

    # Domi "Maybe you will not disappoint? Yes?"
    Domi "¿Quizá tú no me decepciones? ¿Sí?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2860
translate spanish d19e89_87a56f99:

    # Domi "Oh well, I unfortunately cannot think of such a temple of the top of my head. But for a fine lady like you..."
    Domi "Oh bueno, por desgracia no puedo pensar en un templo así de inmediato. Pero para una dama tan fina como tú..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2861
translate spanish d19e89_d8636ce3:

    # St "This is getting awkward again... are people always this brazen outside Zeta?"
    St "Esto se está poniendo incómodo otra vez... ¿la gente siempre es tan descarada fuera de Zeta?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2862
translate spanish d19e89_cf181277:

    # St "Maybe I can try turning this to my advantage."
    St "Quizá pueda intentar darle la vuelta a esto en mi beneficio."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2865
translate spanish d19e89_d7edd71b:

    # Domi "...I think I would be willing to give you one of my maps."
    Domi "... Creo que estaría dispuesto a darte uno de mis mapas."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2868
translate spanish d19e89_3b5a8bf1:

    # Domi "Luckily, Domitius thought of circumstances like these."
    Domi "Por suerte, Domicius pensó en circunstancias como estas."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2871
translate spanish d19e89_1dd060f3:

    # "He lets out a chuckle..."
    "Suelta una risita..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2872
translate spanish d19e89_98b5560a:

    # St "And now he's staring..."
    St "Y ahora se queda mirando..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2875
translate spanish d19e89_602807b1:

    # Domi "It's always a pleasure to talk to well behaved ladies."
    Domi "Siempre es un placer hablar con damas bien educadas."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2876
translate spanish d19e89_d6d9240e:

    # St "Does he... not care to at least pretend?!"
    St "¡¿Es que... ni siquiera se molesta en fingir?!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2878
translate spanish d19e89_0c6484e9:

    # St "{i}*sighs*{/i} At least this one is not throwing his hands at me."
    St "{i}*suspiro*{/i} Al menos este no me está echando las manos encima."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2879
translate spanish d19e89_321bdc82:

    # St "The men in this place have no shame."
    St "Los hombres de este lugar no tienen vergüenza."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2882
translate spanish d19e89_4abbec80:

    # Domi "And somehow, I see qualities in you that my future wife sadly does not possess."
    Domi "Y de alguna manera, veo en ti cualidades que mi futura esposa lamentablemente no posee."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2885
translate spanish d19e89_d4dbab28:

    # St "His... future wife?"
    St "¿Su... futura esposa?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2888
translate spanish d19e89_a4883b72:

    # "Looking over to the couch, the girl looks back at them, a stern, determined look on her face..."
    "Al mirar hacia el diván, la chica los observa de vuelta, con un gesto severo y decidido en el rostro..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2889
translate spanish d19e89_19bdba02:

    # St "If looks could kill, I wonder if I would be dying, or maybe the fat guy..."
    St "Si las miradas mataran, me pregunto si sería yo la que estaría muriendo, o tal vez el gordo..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2892
translate spanish d19e89_7cb1c0a6:

    # C4 "..."
    C4 "..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2893
translate spanish d19e89_1fdd974e:

    # S "How... You are betrothed?"
    S "Cómo... ¿estais comprometidos?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2894
translate spanish d19e89_c7ac5571:

    # Domi "Oh, yes, we are! Her name is Abena. She's beautiful, isn't she?"
    Domi "Oh, sí, lo estamos. Su nombre es Abena. Es hermosa, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2895
translate spanish d19e89_58380256:

    # Domi "A passing trader informed me about her uncle's farm's whereabouts. I had him brought to me, and she came along."
    Domi "Un comerciante de paso me informó del paradero de la granja de su tío. Hice que me lo trajeran, y ella vino con él."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2896
translate spanish d19e89_1da03224:

    # Domi "I knew she was everything I want in a concubine, so I made him sell her to me."
    Domi "Sabía que ella era todo lo que quería en una concubina, así que hice que me la vendiera."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2897
translate spanish d19e89_4d40dd34:

    # Domi "The poor thing is terribly underfed, so I am having her fed properly. Put some meat on her bones."
    Domi "La pobre está terriblemente desnutrida, así que estoy haciendo que la alimenten bien. Que ponga algo de carne en sus huesos."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2898
translate spanish d19e89_cec86236:

    # Domi "She's still a virgin too. Paid extra for that. She will learn to love me, I am sure."
    Domi "Además sigue siendo virgen. Pagué extra por eso. Aprenderá a amarme, estoy seguro."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2899
translate spanish d19e89_9abae055:

    # Domi "What a day that will be."
    Domi "¡Qué día tan maravilloso será ese!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2902
translate spanish d19e89_fa1e3582:

    # "He suddenly places his meaty hand on [S]'s hip, casually."
    "De repente coloca su mano carnosa en la cadera de [S], con naturalidad."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2903
translate spanish d19e89_300ecd64:

    # St "What is he-?!"
    St "¡¿Qué está-?!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2906
translate spanish d19e89_8a939a8d:

    # Domi "Apologies for the distraction, pretty lady. Let us get back to your request."
    Domi "Disculpa la distracción, linda dama. Volvamos a tu petición."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2910
translate spanish d19e89_6f0b50d6:

    # St "How dare he touch me like that, I should speak up..."
    St "Cómo se atreve a tocarme así, debería decir algo..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2912
translate spanish d19e89_f15ca374:

    # St "Gods, no one in this place knows how to treat a woman..."
    St "Dioses, nadie en este lugar sabe cómo tratar a una mujer..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2915
translate spanish d19e89_18c0d330:

    # Domi "If I give you the map, I expect compensation in return."
    Domi "Si te doy el mapa, espero una compensación a cambio."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2916
translate spanish d19e89_9004ed27:

    # Domi "Whatever it is you are looking for, this map will surely guide you there."
    Domi "Sea lo que sea que busques, este mapa seguramente te guiará hasta allí."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2919
translate spanish d19e89_d2012122:

    # St "Compensation?"
    St "¿Compensación?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2922
translate spanish d19e89_09843bd5:

    # S "...You're looking for gold? For the map."
    S "... ¿Buscas oro? ¿Por el mapa?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2925
translate spanish d19e89_29968e10:

    # Domi "Oh no, young woman. I do not want for coin."
    Domi "Oh no, jovencita. No quiero monedas."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2928
translate spanish d19e89_b8a07962:

    # "His hand moves towards [S]..."
    "Su mano se desliza hacia [S]..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2941
translate spanish d19e124_daa0a824:

    # S "{i}*gasp*{/i}"
    S "{i}*jadeo*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2942
translate spanish d19e124_00ca00b3:

    # S "What are you..."
    S "¿Qué estás...?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2945
translate spanish d19e124_820c62e9:

    # Domi "{i}*chuckles*{/i}"
    Domi "{i}*risilla*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2948
translate spanish d19e124_b1cc6791:

    # Domi "This is what I want."
    Domi "Esto es lo que quiero."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2949
translate spanish d19e124_96dd3081:

    # St "He just... ripped down my shirt?!"
    St "El acaba de... ¡¿arrancarme el top?!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2952
translate spanish d19e124_228e4d3e:

    # "As his hands slide over [S]'s figure, she realises that he isn't just fat, he's a veritable giant."
    "Mientras sus manos recorren la figura de [S], ella se da cuenta de que no es solo gordo, es un auténtico gigante."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2953
translate spanish d19e124_fd2fe8e6:

    # Domi "Mh... trust me, young Stalker. I have many maps. But first..."
    Domi "Mh... confía en mí, joven Acechadora. Tengo muchos mapas. Pero primero..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2956
translate spanish d19e124_6747167c:

    # Domi "{i}*suck*{/i}"
    Domi "{i}*chupar*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2957
translate spanish d19e124_88aedf2f:

    # St "What is he doing?!"
    St "¡¿Qué está haciendo?!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2960
translate spanish d19e124_8f6b8b9e:

    # S "D-Domitius?!"
    S "¡¿D-Domitius?!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2961
translate spanish d19e124_39d920bf:

    # Domi "Mmh..."
    Domi "Mmh..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2964
translate spanish d19e124_563f4a61:

    # "It all happened so fast. From one moment to another, [S] was exposed, and the big man who resembles more of a dumb child than a trader was all over her..."
    "Todo ocurrió tan rápido. De un momento a otro, [S] estaba expuesta, y el hombre enorme, que parecía más un niño torpe que un comerciante, estaba encima de ella..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2967
translate spanish d19e124_5dc1d6c1:

    # Domi "Nha..."
    Domi "Nha..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2970
translate spanish d19e124_6747167c_1:

    # Domi "{i}*suck*{/i}"
    Domi "{i}*chupar*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2973
translate spanish d19e124_792d8300:

    # "As [S] tries to make sense of the situation, his big lips envelop her nipples in a hungry yet gentle manner."
    "Mientras [S] intenta asimilar la situación, sus labios enormes envuelven sus pezones de forma hambrienta pero suave."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2976
translate spanish d19e124_5e9b7aae:

    # St "I need to..."
    St "Necesito..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2979
translate spanish d19e124_1a56a166:

    # S "Nh..."
    S "Nh..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2982
translate spanish d19e124_1984b684:

    # Domi "Ah..."
    Domi "Ah..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2983
translate spanish d19e124_31e0fb76:

    # St "Stop this!"
    St "¡Detente!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2986
translate spanish d19e124_13499d7f:

    # S "What are you doing?!"
    S "¿Qué estás haciendo?!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2989
translate spanish d19e124_c04c88a7:

    # "She breaks free..."
    "Ella se suelta..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2992
translate spanish d19e124_cf856a06:

    # S "T-this is unheard of, Domitius!"
    S "¡E-esto es inaudito, Domitius!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2993
translate spanish d19e124_6c518dec:

    # Domi "Peace, pretty lady. Are you upset? I mean no disrespect."
    Domi "Tranquila, linda dama. ¿Estás molesta? No quise faltarte al respeto."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2994
translate spanish d19e124_2e90f7cd:

    # St "Is he... dense or something?! Perhaps..."
    St "¿Está... tonto o qué?! Quizá..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2997
translate spanish d19e124_017f1268:

    # S "Domitius... I am willing to forget this indiscretion and not report it... but you will give me what I came for."
    S "Domitius... estoy dispuesta a olvidar esta indiscreción y no reportarla... pero me darás lo que vine a buscar."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:2998
translate spanish d19e124_5936719b:

    # S "The map."
    S "El mapa."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3001
translate spanish d19e124_3fd24042:

    # St "Here goes nothing..."
    St "Allá vamos..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3004
translate spanish d19e124_a6142d8c:

    # Domi "Make the report, I don't mind. Though handing over the map would ease your distress, Lady Stalker."
    Domi "Haz el reporte, no me importa. Aunque entregarte el mapa aliviaría tu angustia, Dama Acechadora."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3007
translate spanish d19e124_2b6fc3ac:

    # St "He keeps staring at my... am I just a piece of meat to him?!"
    St "Sigue mirando mis... ¿Soy solo un pedazo de carne para él?!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3008
translate spanish d19e124_a361c53d:

    # S "Focus, Domitius. My eyes are up here!"
    S "Concéntrate, Domitius. ¡Mis ojos están aquí arriba!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3011
translate spanish d19e124_ddc76ddb:

    # S "Fine, I won't make the report."
    S "Está bien, no haré el reporte."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3014
translate spanish d19e124_4589a49f:

    # Domi "Perfect. I am glad we are becoming friends."
    Domi "Perfecto. Me alegra que estemos haciéndonos amigos."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3017
translate spanish d19e124_9185f389:

    # St "He's at it, again. And wait...- what {i}friends{/i}?!"
    St "Ya está otra vez. Y espera... ¿qué {i}amigos{/i}?!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3020
translate spanish d19e124_a60ecce9:

    # "With one concentrated effort, he bends over and pulls a map from the stash under his bed."
    "Con un esfuerzo concentrado, se inclina y saca un mapa del escondite bajo su cama."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3021
translate spanish d19e124_0e862ec4:

    # "He offers it with a smirk. Snatching it impatiently, she rushes out of the tent..."
    "Lo ofrece con una sonrisa burlona. Ella lo arrebata con impaciencia y sale corriendo de la tienda..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3028
translate spanish d19e113_ab093955:

    # S "W-wait... I'm not sure what you think you are doing."
    S "E-espera... no estoy segura de lo que crees que estás haciendo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3031
translate spanish d19e113_f40cacad:

    # Domi "I was just showing you what I had in mind..."
    Domi "Solo te estaba mostrando lo que tenía en mente..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3036
translate spanish d19e113_2af10cea:

    # St "Maybe I can convince him..."
    St "Quizá pueda convencerlo..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3039
translate spanish d19e113_c836ab4b:

    # S "Well, Lord Domitius..."
    S "Bueno, Lord Domitius..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3042
translate spanish d19e113_0db9c2a8:

    # S "...as a Lady I should have a say in this, don't you think?"
    S "... como Dama debería tener algo que decir en esto, ¿no crees?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3043
translate spanish d19e113_61fac20d:

    # S "Tell me, what would you have me do?"
    S "Dime, ¿qué quieres que haga?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3046
translate spanish d19e113_4960fa56:

    # Domi "You are unfairly beautiful, Lady Stalker. I wish to see... more of you."
    Domi "Eres injustamente hermosa, Dama Acechadora. Deseo ver... más de ti."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3047
translate spanish d19e113_7b1f8ab5:

    # Domi "And you know my intended... she still holds out on me."
    Domi "Y ya sabes, mi prometida... todavía se resiste a mí."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3050
translate spanish d19e113_723480a3:

    # S "Yes... and...?"
    S "Sí... ¿y...?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3053
translate spanish d19e113_9878518d:

    # Domi "Would you offer me some relief?"
    Domi "¿Me ofrecerías algo de alivio?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3056
translate spanish d19e113_23815abc:

    # St "Oh, great. Because he wasn't strange enough already."
    St "Oh, genial. Como si no fuera ya bastante raro."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3059
translate spanish d19e113_faa91922:

    # S "I could... but what will you do in return?"
    S "Podría... pero ¿qué harás tú a cambio?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3062
translate spanish d19e113_496fb95e:

    # S "A girl like me needs to make sure she isn’t exploited by big, strong men like you."
    S "Una chica como yo debe asegurarse de no ser explotada por hombres grandes y fuertes como tú."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3063
translate spanish d19e113_364554c8:

    # S "You understand that, right?"
    S "Lo entiendes, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3064
translate spanish d19e113_ffad7ae9:

    # Domi "I... uh... I do."
    Domi "Yo... eh... sí."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3065
translate spanish d19e113_d2bc5fc2:

    # Domi "I would give you pleasure too."
    Domi "Yo también podría darte placer."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3068
translate spanish d19e113_2777c3ce:

    # St "Seriously? Idiot..."
    St "¿En serio? Idiota..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3071
translate spanish d19e113_37ee994c:

    # S "Pleasure is hardly my purpose here, Domitius. Though I daresay I am skilled at providing it."
    S "El placer difícilmente es mi propósito aquí, Domitius. Aunque debo decir que soy bastante hábil dándolo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3072
translate spanish d19e113_5f67494b:

    # S "Remember the map you mentioned? About that place I am looking for?"
    S "¿Recuerdas el mapa que mencionaste? Sobre ese lugar que estoy buscando."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3075
translate spanish d19e113_125831a4:

    # Domi "I... could give you my map."
    Domi "Yo... podría darte mi mapa."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3078
translate spanish d19e113_e68c7c7c:

    # S "Of course. Though you understand that I must leave and ensure these maps are not a forgery?"
    S "Por supuesto. Aunque entiendes que debo irme y asegurarme de que estos mapas no sean una falsificación, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3081
translate spanish d19e113_3f42156e:

    # S "...but after that, there would be nothing standing in our way. What do you think?"
    S "... pero después de eso, no habría nada que se interponga en nuestro camino. ¿Qué opinas?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3084
translate spanish d19e113_8e912731:

    # Domi "This... is a good idea, young Stalker."
    Domi "Esto... es una buena idea, joven Acechadora."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3087
translate spanish d19e113_40db696b:

    # Domi "I... I will look for the map."
    Domi "Yo... buscaré el mapa."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3090
translate spanish d19e113_0f6f782b:

    # S "Thank you, Domitius."
    S "Gracias, Domitius."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3091
translate spanish d19e113_8c379f23:

    # St "Hurry up..."
    St "Date prisa..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3094
translate spanish d19e113_6d57cd9c:

    # "With one concentrated effort, he bends over and pulls a map from the stash under his bed and hands it over to [S]."
    "Con un esfuerzo concentrado, se inclina, saca un mapa del escondite bajo su cama y se lo entrega a [S]."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3097
translate spanish d19e113_83881de8:

    # S "It's good to be friends with big, strong men like you. See you soon, Domitius."
    S "Es bueno ser amiga de hombres grandes y fuertes como tú. Nos vemos pronto, Domitius."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3102
translate spanish d19e113_7ef8f8e4:

    # "Clutching the map, she rushes from the tent and makes her way back to camp..."
    "Aferrando el mapa, sale corriendo de la tienda y se dirige de nuevo al campamento..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3110
translate spanish d19e113_ab1167da:

    # S "I... think I will pass, thank you."
    S "Yo... creo que paso, gracias."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3115
translate spanish d19e113_fe877715:

    # "She gets up and quickly moves away..."
    "Se levanta y se aleja rápidamente..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3118
translate spanish d19e113_9f6e54ae:

    # Domi "Such a shame, young Stalker. If you change your mind, I am always here to help you!"
    Domi "Qué lástima, joven Acechadora. Si cambias de opinión, siempre estaré aquí para ayudarte."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3121
translate spanish d19e113_3866112d:

    # St "What an odd creature. I'm leaving."
    St "Qué criatura tan extraña. Me voy."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3124
translate spanish d19e113_5ad18b3f:

    # "Deciding not to engage with the free trader any further, she leaves the bazaar, heading back to camp empty-handed."
    "Decidiendo no tratar más con el comerciante libre, abandona el bazar y vuelve al campamento con las manos vacías."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3130
translate spanish d19e113_a4757ee0:

    # "I don't like him, screw this."
    "No me gusta, que le den."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3133
translate spanish d19e113_8e41215b:

    # S "I am not going to sit down for this."
    S "No voy a sentarme para esto."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3136
translate spanish d19e113_e455e808:

    # Domi "That is unfortunate, but perhaps you change your mind later? You can think about it."
    Domi "Qué pena, pero quizá cambies de opinión más tarde. Piénsalo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3139
translate spanish d19e113_19835bf5:

    # S "I doubt it. I am leaving."
    S "Lo dudo. Me voy."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3144
translate spanish d19e113_5ad18b3f_1:

    # "Deciding not to engage with the free trader any further, she leaves the bazaar, heading back to camp empty-handed."
    "Decidiendo no tratar más con el comerciante libre, abandona el bazar y vuelve al campamento con las manos vacías."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3154
translate spanish d19e113_7219e652:

    # "After an uncomfortable walk through the dusty desert, [S] arrived at the market settlement."
    "Tras una incómoda caminata por el polvoriento desierto, [S] llegó al asentamiento del mercado."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3155
translate spanish d19e113_ba2a5f57:

    # "The storm is not within dangerous proximity, but still most people seem to be prepared to wait it out in the relative shelter of their tents..."
    "La tormenta no está peligrosamente cerca, pero aun así la mayoría parece dispuesta a esperarla bajo el refugio relativo de sus tiendas..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3159
translate spanish d19e113_871a538c:

    # St "Here we are..."
    St "Ya estamos aquí..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3162
translate spanish d19e113_557840d1:

    # St "This place really looks deserted... let's see..."
    St "Este lugar realmente parece desierto... veamos..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3165
translate spanish d19e113_afddcde9:

    # "She notices a big tent at the distance and makes her way there..."
    "Ve una gran tienda a lo lejos y se dirige hacia allí..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3168
translate spanish d19e113_b709b895:

    # "Approaching the dimly lit tent, [S] notices it seems to be partially shuttered, and guards are nowhere to be found."
    "Al acercarse a la tienda tenuemente iluminada, [S] nota que parece estar medio cerrada y no hay guardias a la vista."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3171
translate spanish d19e113_028892ef:

    # St "This must be the main tent. Whoever is here must probably know a couple of things..."
    St "Esta debe de ser la tienda principal. Quien esté aquí probablemente sepa un par de cosas..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3174
translate spanish d19e113_d6263d6e:

    # St "Let's see who's inside..."
    St "Veamos quién está dentro..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3177
translate spanish d19e113_1d492261:

    # St "...Huh?!"
    St "... ¡¿Eh?!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3180
translate spanish d19e113_ff94b08e:

    # "Inside the tent, [S] sees the figure of a bulging man laying down with a young woman on his side..."
    "Dentro de la tienda, [S] ve la figura de un hombre corpulento recostado con una joven a su lado..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3182
translate spanish d19e113_569c3016:

    # St "I will never get used to see an empty bazar outside of business hours..."
    St "Nunca me acostumbraré a ver un bazar vacío fuera del horario de comercio..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3185
translate spanish d19e113_5c3adaf2:

    # St "I guess they aren't taking any risks with the storm in the vicinity."
    St "Supongo que no quieren correr riesgos con la tormenta tan cerca."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3193
translate spanish d19e209_8f0d01fd:

    # "It seems that the man is fast asleep, whereas the expression of the woman remains indescribable, in the penumbra."
    "Parece que el hombre duerme profundamente, mientras que la expresión de la mujer permanece indescriptible, en la penumbra."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3196
translate spanish d19e209_38394611:

    # "The snoring of the man is the only sound that fills the room, until a quiet whisper of metal against fabric disturbs the peace of the scene."
    "El ronquido del hombre es el único sonido que llena la estancia, hasta que un suave susurro de metal contra tela perturba la paz de la escena."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3201
translate spanish d19e209_26b942db:

    # Ab "..."
    Ab "..."

