    C3 "..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3308
translate spanish d19e226_66a16386:

    # St "She saw me..."
    St "Ella me ha visto..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3311
translate spanish d19e226_681117f7:

    # "A moment passes, as the women look at each other..."
    "Pasa un momento, mientras las mujeres se miran..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3314
translate spanish d19e226_545a8730:

    # "...before the murderer jumps to her feet and silently approaches [S]..."
    "... antes de que la asesina se ponga en pie y se acerque silenciosamente a [S]..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3319
translate spanish d19e226_bf7d4443:

    # Ab "You... you were here before. He used you, too."
    Ab "Tú... tú estuviste aquí antes. Él también te usó."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3321
translate spanish d19e226_93fa2216:

    # Ab "You... you were here before."
    Ab "Tú... tú estuviste aquí antes."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3323
translate spanish d19e226_590833a1:

    # C3 "You saw everything, didn't you?"
    C3 "Lo viste todo, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3327
translate spanish d19e226_ef328b9a:

    # Ab "He was a pig. A blade in his throat was his only salvation."
    Ab "Era un cerdo. Una hoja en su garganta fue su única salvación."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3330
translate spanish d19e226_a3f7db46:

    # "Her expression is determined, but her voice is shaking. This must have been her first kill."
    "Su expresión es decidida, pero su voz tiembla. Debe de haber sido su primera muerte."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3334
translate spanish d19e226_86c6db22:

    # Ab "I was raised to accept the rules of these lands, told that this is how things work out here. I was sold to lay with him by my own kin."
    Ab "Me criaron para aceptar las reglas de estas tierras, me dijeron que así es como funcionan las cosas aquí. Mi propia familia me vendió para yacer con él."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3336
translate spanish d19e226_c1e02609:

    # C3 "I was raised to accept the rules of these lands, told that this is how things work out here. I was sold to lay with him by my own kin."
    C3 "Me criaron para aceptar las reglas de estas tierras, me dijeron que así es como funcionan las cosas aquí. Mi propia familia me vendió para yacer con él."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3340
translate spanish d19e226_30785bd7:

    # Ab "Whatever plans he had for me... are not of my concern anymore..."
    Ab "Cualesquiera que fueran sus planes para mí... ya no son de mi incumbencia..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3342
translate spanish d19e226_1ebf6295:

    # C3 "Whatever plans he had for me... are not of my concern anymore..."
    C3 "Cualesquiera que fueran sus planes para mí... ya no son de mi incumbencia..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3346
translate spanish d19e226_d02b7a98:

    # Ab "You came looking for a map. He fooled you."
    Ab "Viniste buscando un mapa. Te engañó."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3347
translate spanish d19e226_508a9935:

    # Ab "Search under his bed, quickly."
    Ab "Busca bajo su cama, rápido."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3350
translate spanish d19e226_ac07f838:

    # Ab "May the desert path a better way for you."
    Ab "Que el camino del desierto te lleve por una senda mejor."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3352
translate spanish d19e226_f84ad16d:

    # C3 "If you were looking to rob him, I will not stop you."
    C3 "Si estabas buscando robarlo, no te detendré."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3355
translate spanish d19e226_7b226fc1:

    # C3 "All I ask is to not stand in my way."
    C3 "Solo te pido que no te interpongas en mi camino."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3358
translate spanish d19e226_1d7d8797:

    # S "I will not. I am just looking for information about a location around here."
    S "No lo haré. Solo busco información sobre un lugar de por aquí."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3361
translate spanish d19e226_8566bb76:

    # C3 "...Search under his bed. Whatever personal things he had, he kept them there. He won't need them anymore..."
    C3 "... Busca bajo su cama. Todo lo personal que tenía, lo guardaba ahí. Ya no lo necesitará más..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3366
translate spanish d19e226_9f8442cc:

    # "Without uttering a sound, the girl vanishes into the night."
    "Sin emitir un sonido, la chica se desvanece en la noche."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3367
translate spanish d19e226_276d58bb:

    # "She didn't lie about the information: Looking under the bed, [S] spots a stash of potential maps."
    "Ella no mintió sobre la información: al mirar bajo la cama, [S] encuentra un alijo de posibles mapas."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3368
translate spanish d19e226_2c68038e:

    # "Finding what she came for, she turns around, and leaves the camp as quietly as she entered it..."
    "Al encontrar lo que vino a buscar, se da la vuelta y abandona el campamento tan silenciosamente como entró..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3384
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_60e1b0c8:

    # Z "This place is smaller than I thought."
    Z "Este lugar es más pequeño de lo que pensaba."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3387
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_601b6e61:

    # Z "Alright, let's see who's the big guy in this camp..."
    Z "Bien, veamos quién es el pez gordo en este campamento..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3390
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_e0233280:

    # "You take a look at the people idling around, or selling wares..."
    "Miras a la gente que vaga por ahí o que vende mercancías..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3393
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_2240e77d:

    # Zt "That woman, she carries herself like a Stalker."
    Zt "Esa mujer... se mueve como una Acechadora."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3394
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_ff7c5546:

    # Zt "I wouldn't be surprised if she was one. Better not risk giving the game away."
    Zt "No me sorprendería que lo fuera. Mejor no arriesgarse a delatarme."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3397
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_a82c4743:

    # "Your eyes roam around the place..."
    "Tus ojos recorren el lugar..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3400
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_1f3b7436:

    # Zt "Just traders and adventurers. That's exactly what I need."
    Zt "Solo comerciantes y aventureros. Justo lo que necesito."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3403
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_9da4e095:

    # "You approach two men standing at a stall, with the intention of asking for directions to whoever runs this place."
    "Te acercas a dos hombres que están en un puesto, con la intención de preguntar por el responsable del lugar."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3406
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_5efe20e8:

    # Man "It's a good blade... how did you obtain it?"
    Man "Es una buena hoja... ¿cómo la conseguiste?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3409
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_737c29d3:

    # Merch "That's none of your business."
    Merch "Eso no es asunto tuyo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3410
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_4eb7d85d:

    # Merch "You want it or not?"
    Merch "¿La quieres o no?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3413
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_9793990b:

    # Man "That depends... you think it can bite through leather armor with this?"
    Man "Depende... ¿crees que podría atravesar armadura de cuero con esto?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3416
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_5b91368f:

    # Merch "If that was what a sabre did, why wear leather armour in the first place?"
    Merch "Si eso fuera lo que hace un sable, ¿para qué usar armadura de cuero en primer lugar?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3419
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_6bf78ab8:

    # Z "I am looking for information, and have coin to pay for it. Are you interested?"
    Z "Busco información, y tengo monedas para pagarla. ¿Interesados?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3422
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_16f056a7:

    # Man "Bah, leave him, he knows nothing. I am your man..."
    Man "Bah, déjalo, no sabe nada. Yo soy tu hombre..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3423
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_27254bd5:

    # Man "So, why don't you show me some of that coin, to start the conversation?"
    Man "Así que... ¿por qué no me enseñas algunas de esas monedas para empezar la conversación?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3426
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_c2d3f496:

    # Z "Nice try. I'll go find someone with more common sense than sense of humour."
    Z "Buen intento. Buscaré a alguien con más sentido común que sentido del humor."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3429
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_d70a22fe:

    # Man "Wait, wait... Not so fast! I can get you the information you need, I promise."
    Man "¡Espera, espera...! ¡No tan rápido! Puedo darte la información que necesitas, lo prometo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3430
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_20016eab:

    # Man "So tell me... What is it you're looking for?"
    Man "Así que dime... ¿Qué es lo que buscas?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3433
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_ac143056:

    # Z "I understand this pigsty is run by someone. Now, you clearly can't be that someone, so what I need from you is directions."
    Z "Tengo entendido que este chiquero lo dirige alguien. Claramente no eres tú, así que lo que necesito son direcciones."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3436
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_ed4c6a3d:

    # Man "What the fuck is that supposed to mean?"
    Man "¿Qué carajos se supone que significa eso?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3439
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_80ed9d27:

    # Z "It means I have no time for your shit. What's the name of who runs this place, and where can I find him?"
    Z "Significa que no tengo tiempo para tus tonterías. ¿Cómo se llama el que dirige este lugar y dónde puedo encontrarlo?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3442
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_f7b74ca7:

    # Man "Fine... It's Domitius you want. The fat one, in the tent behind you."
    Man "Está bien... Quieres a Domitius. El gordo, en la tienda detrás de ti."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3445
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_2107d6ef:

    # Merch "Wait! Where are you going?! Let's do business first."
    Merch "¡Espera! ¿A dónde vas? Hagamos negocios primero."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3448
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_e807dcca:

    # Merch "All this cheapskate here knows is haggling and not buying anything..."
    Merch "Todo lo que este tacaño sabe hacer es regatear y no comprar nada..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3453
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_cb0d2f92:

    # Man "Maybe if you sold anything worthwhile, one would consider it."
    Man "Quizá si vendieras algo que valiera la pena, uno lo consideraría."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3456
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_b593e484:

    # Merch "Don't listen to him! My collection of goods is vast and rare!"
    Merch "¡No le hagas caso! ¡Mi colección de bienes es vasta y rara!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3459
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_c7897b41:

    # Merch "This Spice for instance, it will make your blood boil, if you understand what I mean..."
    Merch "Esta Especia, por ejemplo, hará hervir tu sangre, si entiendes lo que quiero decir..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3460
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_8bc86e97:

    # Merch "I will tell you this, give this to a lady and you may very well wish you didn't, because she's going to pounce on you like a sand-stalked lynx under the blood-red sun!"
    Merch "Te diré esto: si le das esto a una dama, puede que luego desees no haberlo hecho, porque se te lanzará encima como un lince del desierto bajo el sol rojo sangre."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3464
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_07647e60:

    # Zt "I'm not a man for Spice. But perhaps my new friends over in Adira would be interested..."
    Zt "No soy un hombre de Especias. Pero quizá mis nuevos amigos en Adira estarían interesados..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3468
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_0e626cf0:

    # Z "I'll take a bag. Package them well, I will travel long before finding a use for it."
    Z "Tomaré una bolsa. Empáquenla bien, viajaré bastante antes de darle uso."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3471
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_fe4d694f:

    # Merch "I knew I liked you the moment you approached me."
    Merch "Supe que me caías bien en cuanto te me acercaste."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3476
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_de1148ed:

    # "He takes out the bag, and hands it over for some coin..."
    "Saca la bolsa y la entrega a cambio de unas monedas..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3479
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_3f7e8faa:

    # Merch "Best of luck with whatever you're searching for."
    Merch "Buena suerte con lo que sea que estés buscando."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3482
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_eefbabe4:

    # Merch "Now what about you? I'm getting tired of your face, it reminds me of my ballsack. You gonna pay up or leave?!"
    Merch "¿Y tú qué? Me estoy cansando de tu cara, me recuerda a mi escroto. ¿Vas a pagar o te largas?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3485
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_9ac99c71:

    # Z "I am not interested in your spices, or any of the other things you're selling."
    Z "No me interesan tus especias, ni ninguna de las otras cosas que vendes."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3486
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_dd0fe53f:

    # Z "I am here on other matters."
    Z "Estoy aquí por otros asuntos."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3489
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_4461fd5e:

    # Merch "Sure, you're the one missing out. If you change your mind, you know I'm here."
    Merch "Claro, el que pierde eres tú. Si cambias de opinión, ya sabes dónde encontrarme."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3494
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_15407191:

    # Z "Neither my women nor I consume such junk. I am here for other matters."
    Z "Ni mis mujeres ni yo consumimos esa basura. Estoy aquí por otros asuntos."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3497
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_4461fd5e_1:

    # Merch "Sure, you're the one missing out. If you change your mind, you know I'm here."
    Merch "Claro, el que pierde eres tú. Si cambias de opinión, ya sabes dónde encontrarme."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3503
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_33f5b937:

    # "You turn around and approach the tent..."
    "Das media vuelta y te acercas a la tienda..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3506
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_733120e2:

    # Zt "The big chief... inside here. He's quite hard to miss."
    Zt "El gran jefe... está aquí dentro. Es difícil no notarlo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3509
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_7f7e4f88:

    # Zt "I don't like this guy. I've seen enough camps and settlements during my years. This is never a good sign."
    Zt "Este tipo no me gusta. He visto suficientes campamentos y asentamientos a lo largo de los años. Nunca es buena señal."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3512
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_fbfd284c:

    # "Looking to the right, you spot a young woman lying on an expensive couch."
    "Al mirar a la derecha, ves a una joven recostada en un lujoso diván."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3515
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_8a4fa77c:

    # Zt "Must be his concubine... She certainly has the looks for one."
    Zt "Debe de ser su concubina... Sin duda tiene la apariencia para ello."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3518
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_b0e7a80e:

    # "The girl looks to her right, where the supposed chief is laying..."
    "La chica mira hacia su derecha, donde yace el supuesto jefe..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3521
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_9df5da4b:

    # Z "Guess she's waiting for me to do something."
    Z "Supongo que espera a que yo haga algo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3524
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_0bf54769:

    # C3 "{i}*snoring*{/i}"
    C3 "{i}*ronquidos*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3525
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_ca3b0505:

    # Zt "He's snoring like my old car. I hope it rests well out there."
    Zt "Ronca como mi viejo coche. Espero que descanse bien allá afuera."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3528
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_2ed49855:

    # Z "I don't like to disturb the sleep of a man leading a camp, but I have no other choice."
    Z "No me gusta interrumpir el sueño de un hombre que lidera un campamento, pero no tengo otra opción."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3529
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_d78fad67:

    # "You speak loudly, giving him no choice but to wake up..."
    "Hablas en voz alta, sin darle otra opción que despertarse..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3532
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_db8d97d2:

    # C3 "{i}*snor-*{/i}...huh...?"
    C3 "{i}*ron-*{/i}... ¿eh...?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3535
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_46102134:

    # C3 "Uh..."
    C3 "Uh..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3536
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_8d32bbae:

    # Z "Are you Domitius? I've been told you are the man to look for in this place."
    Z "¿Eres Domitius? Me han dicho que eres el hombre al que debo buscar en este lugar."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3539
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_08a25eb2:

    # Domi "Depends on who's asking..."
    Domi "Depende de quién pregunte..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3542
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_a44f03da:

    # Zt "Great... one of those."
    Zt "Genial... uno de esos."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3543
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_54655eca:

    # Z "Someone that's looking for information and is willing to spare a few coins for it."
    Z "Alguien que busca información y está dispuesto a gastar unas monedas por ella."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3546
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_646a4d94:

    # Domi "And you thought it is polite to wake up a man having a hard-earned rest?"
    Domi "¿Y pensaste que era educado despertar a un hombre que se gana su descanso con esfuerzo?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3551
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_382830c2:

    # Domi "I told you [Ab], people out here have no manners."
    Domi "Te lo dije, [Ab], la gente de aquí no tiene modales."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3554
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_26b942db:

    # Ab "..."
    Ab "..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3555
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_0f95ca38:

    # Domi "Don't look away, beautiful Abena. Your uncle wouldn't like that."
    Domi "No apartes la mirada, hermosa Abena. A tu tío no le gustaría eso."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3556
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_1419d0b7:

    # Domi "You are lucky you ended up with me and not one of those low-lives."
    Domi "Eres afortunada de haber acabado conmigo y no con uno de esos despojos."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3559
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_e287f7dc:

    # Z "And you are lucky you ran into an agent of the palace, and not the Queen herself."
    Z "Y tú eres afortunado de encontrarte con un agente del palacio y no con la propia Reina."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3560
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_99732870:

    # Domi "..."
    Domi "..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3561
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_e11aa07d:

    # "He frowns..."
    "El frunce el ceño..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3564
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_711a0071:

    # Domi "And what it is that you want?"
    Domi "¿Y qué es lo que quieres?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3567
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_601f8958:

    # Domi "On second thought, don't bother. I am not in the mood to conduct business after such a rough wakeup."
    Domi "Pensándolo bien, no te molestes. No estoy de humor para hacer negocios después de un despertar tan brusco."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3568
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_cc944fd9:

    # Domi "I would rather prefer to spend some time with my lovely [Ab] instead."
    Domi "Prefiero pasar un rato con mi encantadora [Ab]."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3569
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_4692fd8a:

    # Domi "Goodbye, agent of the palace."
    Domi "Adiós, agente del palacio."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3572
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_42be9197:

    # "You briefly consider teaching this man some humility..."
    "Por un momento consideras enseñarle un poco de humildad a este hombre..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3575
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_9dc9f1a9:

    # "...but looking around you, you're not sure how quickly the situation may get out of hand."
    "...pero al mirar alrededor, no estás seguro de lo rápido que la situación podría salirse de control."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3578
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_6282bbf0:

    # "You look back at the girl, who is still looking at you."
    "Vuelves a mirar a la chica, que sigue observándote."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3579
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_8b4a188a:

    # "While there might be more to her story, you are here for something else..."
    "Aunque puede haber más en su historia, tú estás aquí por otra cosa..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3582
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_5b33b9fd:

    # Domi "{i}*snoring*{/i}"
    Domi "{i}*ronquidos*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3583
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_efa2fecb:

    # Z "{i}*sigh*{/i}"
    Z "{i}*suspiro*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3584
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_09a4ea20:

    # Zt "This is not worth it. I have to try somewhere else."
    Zt "Esto no vale la pena. Tendré que probar en otro sitio."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3600
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_83c97849:

    # Zt "Here I am again... and as expected, the place is emptied out."
    Zt "Aquí estoy de nuevo... y como era de esperar, el lugar está vacío."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3603
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_292ea9e6:

    # Zt "A storm like this is a chance for unconventional approaches..."
    Zt "Una tormenta como esta es una oportunidad para enfoques poco convencionales..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3606
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_cedcff6c:

    # "You walk over to the main tent. The torches inside are lit, and the guard from before is no longer there."
    "Caminas hacia la tienda principal. Las antorchas dentro están encendidas y el guardia de antes ya no está allí."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3609
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_0f3877f0:

    # "You look inside, and spot familiar figures close together..."
    "Miras dentro y distingues figuras familiares, muy juntas..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3610
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_b7142cfe:

    # Zt "That's the concubine. Is he... sleeping?"
    Zt "Esa es la concubina. ¿Está... durmiendo?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3612
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_ee70a4c5:

    # Zt "It was to be expected that the bazaar is empty during a time like this."
    Zt "Era de esperar que el bazar estuviera vacío en un momento como este."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3615
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_0906ff83:

    # Zt "That will make it more difficult to find out who runs this camp."
    Zt "Eso hará más difícil descubrir quién dirige este campamento."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3618
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_a83ed4f5:

    # "Strolling around, you approach a large tent, halfway covered up. The torches inside are lit."
    "Deambulando, te acercas a una gran tienda, medio cubierta. Las antorchas dentro están encendidas."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3619
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_4b3646a9:

    # Zt "This looks promising. But it is also quiet... people are resting."
    Zt "Esto parece prometedor. Pero también está silencioso... la gente está descansando."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3622
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_dd1896b2:

    # "You look inside, and spot two figures, close to each other..."
    "Miras dentro y ves dos figuras, muy juntas..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3623
translate spanish d19e_mc_bazaar_c2a406e0:

    # "Trying to not be spotted immediately, you stay quiet, and see what scene unfolds in front of you."
    "Intentando no ser descubierto de inmediato, te quedas en silencio y observas cómo se desarrolla la escena frente a ti."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3630
translate spanish d19e240_220f67fa:

    # "She looks at you, you look at her. Many seconds pass..."
    "Ella te mira, tú la miras. Pasan muchos segundos..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3633
translate spanish d19e240_7831bcf7:

    # "...before she gets up."
    "...hasta que se levanta."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3636
translate spanish d19e240_b0974a67:

    # "She stands in front of you, angry and determined, yet unsure and nervous. This was her first kill."
    "Se planta frente a ti, enfadada y decidida, pero también insegura y nerviosa. Este fue su primer asesinato."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3640
translate spanish d19e240_06880296:

    # C3 "...W-who are you? Don't come closer. I will kill again if I have to."
    C3 "... ¿Q-quién eres tú? No te acerques. Mataré otra vez si tengo que hacerlo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3643
translate spanish d19e240_7e481a40:

    # Z "Calm down. Whatever happened here is none of my concern."
    Z "Cálmate. Lo que haya pasado aquí no es asunto mío."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3644
translate spanish d19e240_764da2c8:

    # Z "I am looking for the person that runs this place. I have some questions for him."
    Z "Busco a la persona que dirige este lugar. Tengo algunas preguntas para él."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3647
translate spanish d19e240_3060555f:

    # "She looks at you, concerned..."
    "Ella te mira, preocupada..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3650
translate spanish d19e240_3777d5b6:

    # C3 "You found him, but... it might be difficult to get the answers you seek."
    C3 "Lo encontraste, pero... puede que sea difícil conseguir las respuestas que buscas."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3653
translate spanish d19e240_efa2fecb:

    # Z "{i}*sigh*{/i}"
    Z "{i}*suspiro*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3656
translate spanish d19e240_34d7c3c9:

    # Z "I was hoping he could tell me about a place I am looking for."
    Z "Esperaba que pudiera hablarme de un lugar que estoy buscando."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3659
translate spanish d19e240_1ccb0b51:

    # C3 "Search under his bed. Whatever personal things he had, he kept them there. He won't need them anymore..."
    C3 "Busca debajo de su cama. Cualquier cosa personal que tuviera, la guardaba allí. Ya no las necesitará más..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3662
translate spanish d19e240_df6a3ad1:

    # Z "I will. And you better drop the weapon, before they see it."
    Z "Lo haré. Y será mejor que sueltes el arma antes de que la vean."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3665
translate spanish d19e240_a47e6099:

    # C3 "This blade is my way out of this place."
    C3 "Esta hoja es mi forma de salir de este lugar."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3668
translate spanish d19e240_6de99b89:

    # C3 "Goodbye, and thank you... for staying quiet."
    C3 "Adiós, y gracias... por guardar silencio."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3674
translate spanish d19e240_9f8442cc:

    # "Without uttering a sound, the girl vanishes into the night."
    "Sin emitir un sonido, la chica se desvanece en la noche."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3675
translate spanish d19e240_04aa4907:

    # "She didn't lie about the information: Looking under the bed, you spot a stash of potential maps."
    "No mintió sobre la información: al mirar debajo de la cama, encuentras un escondite con posibles mapas."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3676
translate spanish d19e240_2db633cb:

    # "Finding what you apparently came for, you turn around and leave the camp as swiftly as you entered it..."
    "Encontrando lo que aparentemente buscabas, das media vuelta y abandonas el campamento tan rápido como entraste..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3682
translate spanish d19e240_d5923831:

    # Ab "You were here before. Y-you saw him. He was a pig."
    Ab "Estuviste aquí antes. L-lo viste. Era un cerdo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3685
translate spanish d19e240_7e481a40_1:

    # Z "Calm down. Whatever happened here is none of my concern."
    Z "Cálmate. Lo que haya pasado aquí no es asunto mío."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3686
translate spanish d19e240_4ebdb8d1:

    # Z "I was planning to squeeze something out of him, anyway."
    Z "De todas formas pensaba sacarle algo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3689
translate spanish d19e240_24c9771d:

    # Z "Looks like that won't be necessary anymore."
    Z "Parece que ya no será necesario."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3692
translate spanish d19e240_e3913cb0:

    # Ab "You... were looking for a place."
    Ab "Tú... estabas buscando un lugar."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3695
translate spanish d19e240_fa4e6809:

    # Z "I am, yes. Do you know anything?"
    Z "Sí, así es. ¿Sabes algo?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3698
translate spanish d19e240_5ff10239:

    # Ab "Search under his bed. Whatever personal things he had, he kept them there. He won't need them anymore..."
    Ab "Busca debajo de su cama. Cualquier cosa personal que tuviera, la guardaba allí. Ya no las necesitará más..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3701
translate spanish d19e240_df6a3ad1_1:

    # Z "I will. And you better drop the weapon, before they see it."
    Z "Lo haré. Y será mejor que sueltes el arma antes de que la vean."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3704
translate spanish d19e240_d81629d3:

    # Ab "This blade is my way out of this place."
    Ab "Esta hoja es mi salida de este lugar."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3707
translate spanish d19e240_bfbdb402:

    # Ab "Goodbye, and thank you... for staying quiet."
    Ab "Adiós, y gracias... por guardar silencio."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3713
translate spanish d19e240_9f8442cc_1:

    # "Without uttering a sound, the girl vanishes into the night."
    "Sin decir una palabra, la chica se esfuma en la noche."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3714
translate spanish d19e240_04aa4907_1:

    # "She didn't lie about the information: Looking under the bed, you spot a stash of potential maps."
    "No mintió sobre la información: al mirar debajo de la cama, encuentras un escondite con posibles mapas."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3715
translate spanish d19e240_2db633cb_1:

    # "Finding what you apparently came for, you turn around and leave the camp as swiftly as you entered it..."
    "Encontrando lo que aparentemente buscabas, das media vuelta y abandonas el campamento tan rápido como entraste..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3732
translate spanish d19e_ruins_dcc83e04:

    # Z "Here we are, my Queen. Want me to help you out?"
    Z "Aquí estamos, mi Reina. ¿Quieres que te ayude a bajar?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3733
translate spanish d19e_ruins_68c3fbe1:

    # Ne "No thanks, I do in fact enjoy not being pampered, for once."
    Ne "No, gracias. De hecho, disfruto de no ser mimada, por una vez."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3736
translate spanish d19e_ruins_d5ace18a:

    # "She hops out of the trunk..."
    "Ella salta del maletero..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3739
translate spanish d19e_ruins_a5a9131b:

    # Ne "Hm..."
    Ne "Hm..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3742
translate spanish d19e_ruins_70f5b916:

    # Ne "To think these were abandoned centuries ago..."
    Ne "Pensar que esto fue abandonado hace siglos..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3743
translate spanish d19e_ruins_4c83eeb1:

    # Ne "...did they ever imagine a Queen coming to this place?"
    Ne "... ¿acaso imaginaron alguna vez que una Reina vendría a este lugar?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3749
translate spanish d19e_ruins_df9f9915:

    # "As you approach the ruins, you find yourself facing the remains of a large entrance..."
    "Al acercarte a las ruinas, te encuentras frente a los restos de una gran entrada..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3752
translate spanish d19e_ruins_905bd983:

    # Z "With the way it looks, you would think these are the remains of a past civilization."
    Z "Por cómo se ve, dirías que son los restos de una civilización pasada."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3753
translate spanish d19e_ruins_2b101e04:

    # S "Maybe they are... have you wondered if Zeta ever changed during these years?"
    S "Quizás lo sean... ¿te has preguntado si Zeta cambió en todos estos años?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3754
translate spanish d19e_ruins_6a5d632c:

    # S "I mean... four hundred years is a long time. What do you say, Neith?"
    S "Quiero decir... cuatrocientos años es mucho tiempo. ¿Qué opinas, Neith?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3757
translate spanish d19e_ruins_0e9ad079:

    # Ne "When I was being raised by the Elders, Radames used to tell me:"
    Ne "Cuando los Ancianos me criaban, Ramades solía decirme:"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3758
translate spanish d19e_ruins_34acbef4:

    # Ne "\"When you ascend to the throne, you will incarnate the great paradox of ruling Zeta. You will have the absolute authority, eternal incarnation of the Gods and their constant values, yet the sole shaper of law and tradition.\""
    Ne "\"Cuando asciendas al trono, encarnarás la gran paradoja de gobernar Zeta. Tendrás la autoridad absoluta, eterna encarnación de los dioses y de sus valores constantes, y aun así serás la única creadora de la ley y la tradición.\""

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3759
translate spanish d19e_ruins_88d24d3c:

    # "[S] looks at the Queen with a puzzled expression"
    "[S] mira a la Reina con expresión confundida."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3760
translate spanish d19e_ruins_8be74c2a:

    # Ne "Yes, I don't get it either. Am I supposed to keep to the traditional ways the Queen represents, or am I supposed to change everything?"
    Ne "Sí, yo tampoco lo entiendo. ¿Se supone que debo mantener las formas tradicionales que representa la Reina, o se supone que debo cambiarlo todo?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3762
translate spanish d19e_ruins_95ba8f53:

    # Z "Elder Radames? He raised you?"
    Z "¿El Anciano Radames? ¿Él te crió?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3763
translate spanish d19e_ruins_549de752:

    # Ne "In a manner of speaking. One of the Elders' tasks is to educate the next queen. There are many tutors; he just happens to speak the loudest, more often than not."
    Ne "Por así decirlo. Una de las tareas de los Ancianos es educar a la próxima reina. Hay muchos tutores; él simplemente resulta ser el que habla más alto, la mayoría de las veces."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3764
translate spanish d19e_ruins_3d129d33:

    # S "The Academy teaches us that the Queens of the city are chosen at birth, with the assistance of the gods."
    S "La Academia enseña que las Reinas de la ciudad son elegidas al nacer, con la asistencia de los dioses."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3767
translate spanish d19e_ruins_cf51cdb8:

    # Ne "Yes, but what happens if she has an accident as a child? Or falls ill?"
    Ne "Sí, pero ¿qué pasa si tiene un accidente de niña? ¿O enferma?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3768
translate spanish d19e_ruins_4189be7e:

    # Ne "I've mentioned it before. Living it from the inside, it's easy to become cynical about the whole \"holyness of the Queen\" thing."
    Ne "Ya lo he mencionado antes. Viviéndolo desde dentro, es fácil volverse cínica con todo eso de la \"santidad de la Reina\"."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3769
translate spanish d19e_ruins_94282d27:

    # Ne "\"Miracles are flawless... until they are touched by reality. That is why the Holy Queen must remain at a distance.\" is another one of his little gems."
    Ne "\"Los milagros son perfectos... hasta que los toca la realidad. Por eso la Reina Sagrada debe permanecer a distancia.\" Esa era otra de sus pequeñas joyas."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3770
translate spanish d19e_ruins_10f94682:

    # Ne "Gods forbid that the common folk of Zeta realise that their beloved Queen eats, sleeps and shits like them."
    Ne "Dioses no quieran que el pueblo de Zeta descubra que su querida Reina come, duerme y caga como ellos."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3773
translate spanish d19e_ruins_1fe2fe10:

    # Ne "I do wonder if what we see here is everything there is. They seem to have added catacombs even to the first ever structures, to seek refuge of the holy storms."
    Ne "Me pregunto si lo que vemos aquí es todo lo que hay. Parece que añadieron catacumbas incluso a las primeras estructuras, para refugiarse de las tormentas sagradas."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3776
translate spanish d19e_ruins_dcfdd618:

    # "She ponders..."
    "Ella reflexiona..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3779
translate spanish d19e_ruins_9ae45ccc:

    # S "The question is why parts of it are well preserved, and others crumbled. Did it happen... naturally?"
    S "La pregunta es por qué unas partes están bien conservadas y otras se derrumbaron. ¿Ocurrió... de forma natural?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3784
translate spanish d19e_ruins_1fc2f770:

    # Ne "There is only one way to find out! Let us hope there's more than rubble around these corners."
    Ne "¡Solo hay una forma de averiguarlo! Esperemos que haya algo más que escombros tras estas esquinas."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3787
translate spanish d19e_ruins_a5a9131b_1:

    # Ne "Hm..."
    Ne "Hm..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3790
translate spanish d19e_ruins_a1e39092:

    # S "Do you see anything?"
    S "¿Ves algo?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3793
translate spanish d19e_ruins_28d1ad3b:

    # Ne "I will let you know, perhaps there's an entrance hidden under the sands."
    Ne "Ya te diré, quizá haya una entrada escondida bajo la arena."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3796
translate spanish d19e_ruins_83c60d74:

    # Ne "...I didn't come here for nothing."
    Ne "...no vine hasta aquí para nada."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3799
translate spanish d19e_ruins_13ec68e6:

    # Ne "{i}*humming*{/i}"
    Ne "{i}*tarareando*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3802
translate spanish d19e_ruins_cee81c69:

    # Ne "...hm?"
    Ne "... ¿hm?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3805
translate spanish d19e_ruins_132f5c39:

    # Z "I don't want to ruin her fun, but the chance of finding hidden catacombs in a place like this..."
    Z "No quiero arruinarle la diversión, pero la probabilidad de encontrar catacumbas ocultas en un sitio así..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3808
translate spanish d19e_ruins_cd59efa0:

    # S "I know, I do feel bad for her a little bit though."
    S "Lo sé, aunque me da un poco de pena por ella."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3811
translate spanish d19e_ruins_153cf896:

    # S "I mean, she risked so much to be with us. And all she can do is look around through some old, desolated ruins."
    S "Quiero decir, arriesgó tanto para estar con nosotros... y lo único que puede hacer es mirar entre unas ruinas viejas y desoladas."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3814
translate spanish d19e_ruins_e95b3a31:

    # Z "Who knows... We might still get lucky."
    Z "Quién sabe... todavía podemos tener suerte."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3817
translate spanish d19e_ruins_9064b6c0:

    # S "And what have you found out so far on this journey?"
    S "¿Y qué has descubierto hasta ahora en este viaje?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3825
translate spanish d19e178x12_773fae8a:

    # Z "I found out how I regret not taking you two with me much sooner."
    Z "He descubierto cuánto lamento no haberlas llevado conmigo mucho antes."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3826
translate spanish d19e178x12_d3ab39cf:

    # Z "The pride I feel when my [persistent.da] is by my side. And I don't mind the royal brat spicing things up."
    Z "El orgullo que siento cuando mi [persistent.da] está a mi lado. Y no me molesta que la mocosa real le ponga un poco de picante."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3829
translate spanish d19e178x12_01bc2be5:

    # S "Aww... you're so sweet, [persistent.dad]..."
    S "Ohh... eres tan dulce, [persistent.dad]..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3834
translate spanish d19e178x12_26e708f4:

    # Z "I found out how distracting it can be to have two pretty girls by your side."
    Z "He descubierto lo distraído que puede ser tener a dos chicas guapas a tu lado."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3835
translate spanish d19e178x12_c2ce1e87:

    # Z "Do I lead you, or stay behind you two? I can't decide which angle is more appealing."
    Z "¿Debo ir delante de vosotras, o quedarme detrás? No logro decidir qué vista me resulta más atractiva."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3838
translate spanish d19e178x12_9e0b1006:

    # S "Oh, how unfortunate. That reminds me, you didn't get to do anything more than massage our legs last night. Does it hurt?"
    S "Oh, qué mala suerte. Eso me recuerda que anoche no hiciste más que masajearnos las piernas. ¿Te duele?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3841
translate spanish d19e178x12_54622edf:

    # S "I am no longer your apprentice. You could have just asked, you know?"
    S "Ya no soy tu aprendiz. Podrías haberlo pedido sin más, ¿sabes?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3844
translate spanish d19e178x12_43403739:

    # "Your eye is drawn towards her open cleavage..."
    "Tu mirada se dirige a su escote abierto..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3845
translate spanish d19e178x12_3abcc55b:

    # S "I think we could both use a bit of relaxation."
    S "Creo que los dos necesitamos un poco de relajación."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3848
translate spanish d19e178x12_e5492b40:

    # S "What do you say, let's find a quiet place, so you can release your tensions inside me?"
    S "¿Qué dices? Busquemos un lugar tranquilo... para que liberes tus tensiones dentro de mí."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3851
translate spanish d19e178x12_0048a582:

    # Z "You have grown so much, lately. I am still adjusting to you being this direct with what you want."
    Z "Has crecido tanto últimamente... aún me estoy acostumbrando a que seas tan directa con lo que quieres."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3855
translate spanish d19e178x12_c2e18e53:

    # S "Like father, like [persistent.da], I assume..."
    S "De tal padre, tal [persistent.da], supongo..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3861
translate spanish d19e178x12_5d3bbd94:

    # Ne "RRRRRAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAH!!!!! GODS BE DAMMED!"
    Ne "¡¡¡RRRRRAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAH!!!!! ¡MALDITOS SEAN LOS DIOSES!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3862
translate spanish d19e178x12_c26f86f5:

    # S "Neith?!"
    S "¿¡Neith!?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3865
translate spanish d19e178x12_72dcd13c:

    # "You rush over to her..."
    "Corres hacia ella..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3868
translate spanish d19e178x12_ab6ded49:

    # S "W-why would you shout like that? You gave me a fright."
    S "¿P-por qué gritaste así? Me diste un susto."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3869
translate spanish d19e178x12_73cc6c92:

    # S "...also, why are you up there?"
    S "...además, ¿por qué estás ahí arriba?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3874
translate spanish d19e178x12_9d996ecc:

    # "You hear her huffing and puffing..."
    "La escuchas resoplar y jadear..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3877
translate spanish d19e178x12_03349cb1:

    # Ne "No reason."
    Ne "Por nada."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3880
translate spanish d19e178x12_3bacee98:

    # Ne "Dust, silence, empty stones and disappointment. That's all that's here. And then there's me, foolish enough to think I'd find anything."
    Ne "Polvo, silencio, piedras vacías y decepción. Eso es todo lo que hay aquí. Y luego estoy yo, bastante tonta como para pensar que encontraría algo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3881
translate spanish d19e178x12_b9b41313:

    # Ne "Figures. I leave it all behind for ruins that can't even give me the courtesy of being interesting."
    Ne "Ya lo decía yo. Lo dejo todo atrás por unas ruinas que ni siquiera tienen la cortesía de ser interesantes."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3884
translate spanish d19e178x12_f2eb9429:

    # Z "Calm down, girl. We just started our journey."
    Z "Cálmate, niña. Apenas hemos empezado nuestro viaje."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3887
translate spanish d19e178x12_7d6aa783:

    # Ne "A journey to where? Another desolated pile of rocks that are about as pointless as these?!"
    Ne "¿Un viaje a dónde? ¿A otro montón de piedras desoladas tan inútiles como estas?!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3889
translate spanish d19e178x12_0259d052:

    # Ne "And on top of that, half the time I'm sitting in your tent all this time because I can't be seen for even {i}one second{/i} by anyone who might know my face!"
    Ne "¡Y encima, paso la mitad del tiempo metida en tu tienda porque no puedo dejar que nadie me vea ni por {i}un segundo{/i} si pudiera reconocer mi cara!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3890
translate spanish d19e178x12_035d8604:

    # Ne "Because I'm supposed to be locked up in the Palace and the very notion of me being anywhere else than on my throne would collapse the world!"
    Ne "¡Porque se supone que debo estar encerrada en el Palacio, y la simple idea de que esté en otro lugar que no sea mi trono haría colapsar el mundo!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3891
translate spanish d19e178x12_99c0f0e2:

    # Ne "I just wanted to do something useful, something real! Instead I am stuck being under constant supervision at all times, except in the Thermae, where I can have a little fun.... My steamy go"
    Ne "¡Solo quería hacer algo útil, algo real! En cambio, estoy atrapada bajo constante supervisión en todo momento, salvo en las Termas, donde puedo divertirme un poco... Mi vaporoso go—"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3893
translate spanish d19e178x12_a61b2c03:

    # S "Uhm... about that last part..."
    S "Uhm... sobre esa última parte..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3894
translate spanish d19e178x12_381c4666:

    # Ne "Shut up, [S]!"
    Ne "¡Cállate, [S]!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3897
translate spanish d19e178x12_24b716a4:

    # Ne "This is not what I imagined. Maybe I should just go home and leave you two to it."
    Ne "Esto no es lo que imaginaba. Quizá debería irme a casa y dejaros a vosotros con ello."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3900
translate spanish d19e178x12_d3b6f6e2:

    # S "Come on, Neith... don't be like this."
    S "Vamos, Neith... no seas así."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3903
translate spanish d19e178x12_1ce564e3:

    # Z "Let's rethink the situation. These ruins won't be the only place where...-"
    Z "Replanteemos la situación. Estas ruinas no serán el único lugar donde...—"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3906
translate spanish d19e178x12_bf033527:

    # Ne "{i}*gasp*{/i}"
    Ne "{i}*jadeo*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3907
translate spanish d19e178x12_eb59eb18:

    # S "...Neith?"
    S "... ¿Neith?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3910
translate spanish d19e178x12_080e7ec1:

    # S "Is everything okay?"
    S "¿Está todo bien?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3913
translate spanish d19e178x12_b3d695a2:

    # Ne "This... looks like something."
    Ne "Esto... parece algo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3916
translate spanish d19e178x12_dbabf04b:

    # Ne "I found... something?"
    Ne "He encontrado... ¿algo?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3919
translate spanish d19e178x12_681a66ef:

    # Ne "I found something!"
    Ne "¡He encontrado algo!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3922
translate spanish d19e178x12_9f0a7d78:

    # Z "Where, what? I can't see anything from here."
    Z "¿Dónde, qué? No puedo ver nada desde aquí."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3923
translate spanish d19e178x12_41b83843:

    # S "She means up there! Look, you can see it from there!"
    S "¡Se refiere allá arriba! Mira, puedes verlo desde aquí."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3926
translate spanish d19e178x12_40b0aed4:

    # "Minutes later..."
    "Minutos después..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3929
translate spanish d19e178x12_aa955317:

    # Z "Well, I'll be damned! Well done, girl, it looks like you found yourself your first treasure."
    Z "¡Vaya, me dejaré sorprender! Bien hecho, chica, parece que encontraste tu primer tesoro."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3930
translate spanish d19e178x12_32a92993:

    # Ne "Oh I didn't, it was all of us together!"
    Ne "Oh, no fui yo sola, lo encontramos entre todos."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3932
translate spanish d19e178x12_25124ee8:

    # Ne "...hehe. I did!"
    Ne "...jeje. ¡Fui yo!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3933
translate spanish d19e178x12_1d0b827e:

    # S "If it even is a treasure. It looks like a chest, but how do we know it hasn't been looted already?"
    S "Si es que realmente es un tesoro. Parece un cofre, pero ¿cómo sabemos que no lo saquearon ya?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3934
translate spanish d19e178x12_7b781131:

    # Ne "How do we get up there?"
    Ne "¿Cómo subimos hasta ahí?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3937
translate spanish d19e178x12_ffaa2389:

    # S "Do you want to try climbing those pillars?"
    S "¿Quieres intentar trepar por esos pilares?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3938
translate spanish d19e178x12_b8d290c7:

    # Ne "No, thank you."
    Ne "No, gracias."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3941
translate spanish d19e178x12_fb4ed13f:

    # Z "Check the other wall. I could give you a boost, [S]."
    Z "Mira la otra pared. Podría darte un empujón, [S]."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3944
translate spanish d19e178x12_25f9115f:

    # Ne "It does lead straight up there. Sort of..."
    Ne "Sí que lleva directo hacia arriba. Más o menos..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3945
translate spanish d19e178x12_426227df:

    # S "Wait, what? Why me? You're the one who found it!"
    S "¿Eh? ¿Por qué yo? ¡Tú fuiste la que lo encontró!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3946
translate spanish d19e178x12_218a8c3c:

    # Ne "[S]! [S]! [S]!"
    Ne "¡[S]! ¡[S]! ¡[S]!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3947
translate spanish d19e178x12_c8cbd103:

    # "Sighing, [S] gives in to the young Queen who is squeeling like a toddler with a piece of candy."
    "Suspirando, [S] cede ante la joven Reina, que chilla como una niña con un caramelo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3948
translate spanish d19e178x12_137eff8c:

    # S "{i}*sigh*{/i} Fine..."
    S "{i}*suspiro*{/i} Está bien..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3951
translate spanish d19e178x12_8a34f0fb:

    # "You proceed with your plan, and [S] manages to climb on top of the pillar between the temple walls..."
    "Sigues con tu plan, y [S] consigue trepar hasta lo alto del pilar entre las paredes del templo..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3954
translate spanish d19e178x12_f375f4b6:

    # S "Urgh... What exactly happens if you land on sand from this height?!"
    S "Ugh... ¿qué pasa exactamente si caes sobre arena desde esta altura?!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3955
translate spanish d19e178x12_0990dcf8:

    # Z "Don't do that."
    Z "No lo intentes."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3958
translate spanish d19e178x12_a9209b39:

    # Ne "Whoa... you're really up there. This is so exciting!!"
    Ne "Wow... estás muy arriba. ¡¡Esto es tan emocionante!!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3964
translate spanish d19e178x12_93f545cb:

    # Ne "Um..."
    Ne "Eh..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3967
translate spanish d19e178x12_91b0e0fd:

    # Ne "...I mean, this is nothing special. Just take a small careful jump and come down!"
    Ne "...digo, tampoco es nada especial. Solo da un pequeño salto con cuidado y baja."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3970
translate spanish d19e178x12_2113607e:

    # S "I appreciate your concern, [Ne]!"
    S "Gracias por tu preocupación, [Ne]!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3973
translate spanish d19e178x12_e3481ba7:

    # Z "I can try to catch you if you want?"
    Z "¿Quieres que intente atraparte?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3974
translate spanish d19e178x12_585a1cf1:

    # S "Nah, I will be fine!"
    S "Nah, estaré bien."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3977
translate spanish d19e178x12_62477417:

    # Z "I know. You're a big girl, just time it right..."
    Z "Lo sé. Ya eres toda una chica grande, solo calcula bien el momento..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3980
translate spanish d19e178x12_6a2db643:

    # S "Timing... got it."
    S "El momento... lo tengo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3983
translate spanish d19e178x12_e6cb63ee:

    # St "Don't look down, focus on the objective..."
    St "No mires abajo, concéntrate en el objetivo..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3986
translate spanish d19e178x12_c6d24a41:

    # St "Here goes..."
    St "Allá vamos..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3989
translate spanish d19e178x12_f5aae5b1:

    # St "... a small leap."
    St "...un pequeño salto."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3992
translate spanish d19e178x12_befcb131:

    # Ne "Oh gods!"
    Ne "¡Oh, dioses!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3994
translate spanish d19e178x12_7504e284:

    # Ne "[persistent.player_name], did you see that?!"
    Ne "¡[persistent.player_name], ¿viste eso?!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:3997
translate spanish d19e178x12_19e1ad1f:

    # Ne "I... knew you could do it. I mean, with those legs, I would make it too, of course!"
    Ne "Yo... sabía que podías hacerlo. Digo, con esas piernas, yo también lo lograría, ¡por supuesto!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4000
translate spanish d19e178x12_2a88a2e2:

    # St "You're mine now, little chest..."
    St "Ahora eres mío, pequeño cofre..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4003
translate spanish d19e178x12_585c0fcc:

    # Z "So, how does it look?"
    Z "Entonces, ¿cómo se ve?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4004
translate spanish d19e178x12_2b2f2f8b:

    # S "It looks old! It's all rusty, but it looks still sealed shut!"
    S "¡Se ve viejo! Está todo oxidado, pero parece que aún está sellado."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4007
translate spanish d19e178x12_b71ec583:

    # Z "You think you can toss it down? Might be better than trying to jump with it."
    Z "¿Crees que puedes lanzarlo abajo? Podría ser mejor que intentar saltar con él."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4010
translate spanish d19e178x12_ea8939be:

    # S "Who says you'll be getting your hands on it? I'm going to ditch you two and become rich!"
    S "¿Quién dice que vais a echarle el guante? ¡Voy a dejaros tirados a los dos y hacerme rico!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4013
translate spanish d19e178x12_507c6d22:

    # Ne "[S] [persistent.da] of [persistent.player_name], need I remind you that I am your Queen and the only reason you're up there is because I saw the chest?"
    Ne "[S], [persistent.da] de [persistent.player_name], ¿debo recordarte que soy tu Reina y la única razón por la que estás ahí arriba es porque yo vi el cofre?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4016
translate spanish d19e178x12_d148140a:

    # S "Yeah, yeah, don't get all worked up..."
    S "Sí, sí, no te pongas así..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4021
translate spanish d19e178x12_4bb201c4:

    # "Later, back at your vehicle..."
    "Más tarde, de vuelta en tu vehículo..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4024
translate spanish d19e178x12_7aa3d19a:

    # Z "[S], you retrieved it, so to you goes the honor of opening it."
    Z "[S], tú lo recuperaste, así que el honor de abrirlo es tuyo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4025
translate spanish d19e178x12_ce9fcccf:

    # S "Now I am curious. Whatever is in here seems pretty light."
    S "Ahora tengo curiosidad. Lo que sea que hay aquí dentro parece bastante ligero."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4028
translate spanish d19e178x12_50fea020:

    # Ne "Well, whatever's in there is mine. But if you're really nice to me, maybe I will let you hold it for a while."
    Ne "Bueno, lo que sea que haya ahí es mío. Pero si eres muy amable conmigo, quizá te deje sostenerlo un rato."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4031
translate spanish d19e178x12_2bcc23ba:

    # S "Say, [persistent.dad], what do you think would happen if we just dumped her in the desert and took this home?"
    S "Oye, [persistent.dad], ¿qué crees que pasaría si la dejamos tirada en el desierto y nos llevamos esto a casa?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4034
translate spanish d19e178x12_a9ef8289:

    # Ne "I am not sure I like you when you're mean..."
    Ne "No estoy segura de que me gustes cuando te pones cruel..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4039
translate spanish d19e178x12_8a82a22c:

    # Ne "So, what is it?"
    Ne "Entonces, ¿qué es?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4042
translate spanish d19e178x12_b292c889:

    # Ne "Aw... a tiny necklace, or bracelet?"
    Ne "Ay... ¿un pequeño collar o una pulsera?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4043
translate spanish d19e178x12_e7088345:

    # S "...and a scroll. Most likely a letter?"
    S "... y un pergamino. ¿Seguramente una carta?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4044
translate spanish d19e178x12_2960f056:

    # Z "A good way to hide a keepsake, I guess. Easy to remember, hard to find."
    Z "Una buena forma de esconder un recuerdo, supongo. Fácil de recordar, difícil de encontrar."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4045
translate spanish d19e178x12_5a1701d8:

    # Z "One thing is for sure, though. Whatever this is, it can't be four hundred years old."
    Z "Aunque hay algo seguro: sea lo que sea, no puede tener cuatrocientos años."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4046
translate spanish d19e178x12_f43cd217:

    # Z "I suggest we carefully unwrap the scroll at our camp while we prepare for the next location. [S], you're better at this than me."
    Z "Sugiero que abramos el pergamino con cuidado en el campamento mientras nos preparamos para el siguiente destino. [S], se te da mejor que a mí."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4047
translate spanish d19e178x12_73cb7816:

    # S "I will be careful."
    S "Tendré cuidado."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4048
translate spanish d19e178x12_62826654:

    # Ne "Let's go back. I could use a snack after this."
    Ne "Volvamos. Después de esto me vendría bien un tentempié."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4061
translate spanish d19e178x12_6b6be68b:

    # "The winds are getting stronger as you approach the ruins, which means you're getting closer to the storm."
    "Los vientos se intensifican a medida que te acercas a las ruinas, lo que significa que estás más cerca de la tormenta."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4064
translate spanish d19e178x12_878dfbaf:

    # Ne "{i}*cough*{/i} It's so... dusty!"
    Ne "{i}*cof*{/i} ¡Está tan... polvoriento!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4065
translate spanish d19e178x12_5eceb20a:

    # Z "Take the gas mask. I told you girls it wasn't a good idea to stay in the trunk."
    Z "Toma la máscara de gas. Os dije que no era buena idea quedarse en el maletero."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4066
translate spanish d19e178x12_165cf200:

    # S "Here... put this on, Neith."
    S "Toma... ponte esto, Neith."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4067
translate spanish d19e178x12_8f39a008:

    # Ne "Like... this? {i}*breathes*{/i}"
    Ne "¿Así...? {i}*respira*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4068
translate spanish d19e178x12_bf5bf57c:

    # Ne "Much better..."
    Ne "Mucho mejor..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4071
translate spanish d19e178x12_4c865481:

    # "She jumps out, gazing into the thick dust..."
    "Ella salta fuera, mirando hacia el espeso polvo..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4074
translate spanish d19e178x12_ad1cc896:

    # Ne "I... don't see us finding anything in there."
    Ne "Yo... no creo que encontremos nada ahí dentro."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4075
translate spanish d19e178x12_aaf79836:

    # Z "The winds are too strong. But it's your call; we can always give it a try."
    Z "Los vientos son demasiado fuertes. Pero es tu decisión; siempre podemos intentarlo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4078
translate spanish d19e178x12_5f61accc:

    # S "We already know where to possibly find that temple, Neith."
    S "Ya sabemos dónde podríamos encontrar ese templo, Neith."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4081
translate spanish d19e178x12_99d53df2:

    # Ne "I hoped for hidden chambers underneath these ruins, but..."
    Ne "Esperaba cámaras ocultas bajo estas ruinas, pero..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4084
translate spanish d19e178x12_473d9b59:

    # Ne "Start the machine, [persistent.player_name]. This is not worth the risk."
    Ne "Enciende la máquina, [persistent.player_name]. No vale la pena arriesgarse."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4087
translate spanish d19e178x12_3b22ca2c:

    # Z "As you wish, my Queen. Hop inside, let's get you out of the dust."
    Z "Como desees, mi Reina. Sube, vamos a sacarte de este polvo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4106
translate spanish d19e_old_man_aeec9888:

    # "You approach what looks like a few shacks huddled together, their respective walls leaning against each other"
    "Te acercas a lo que parecen ser unas chozas apiñadas, con sus muros apoyándose unos en otros."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4112
translate spanish d19e_old_man_a6a1973c:

    # Zt "Let's see if the rumors are true."
    Zt "Veamos si los rumores son ciertos."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4119
translate spanish d19e_old_man_de8d27db:

    # OMan "Can I help you, stranger?"
    OMan "¿Puedo ayudarte, forastero?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4122
translate spanish d19e_old_man_6795f625:

    # "His voice is old and raspy, but calm. His expression is friendly."
    "Su voz es vieja y ronca, pero tranquila. Su expresión es amigable."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4123
translate spanish d19e_old_man_17aa8cfe:

    # Z "I think so. I come from the city, and I was told to seek you out."
    Z "Creo que sí. Vengo de la ciudad, y me dijeron que te buscara."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4126
translate spanish d19e_old_man_7e077aaf:

    # OMan "Come in then, young man."
    OMan "Entra entonces, joven."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4129
translate spanish d19e_old_man_16c0932b:

    # "He leads you inside..."
    "Te guía hacia dentro..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4132
translate spanish d19e_old_man_f892de6a:

    # Zt "I almost can't see in here, why keep this place so dark?"
    Zt "Casi no puedo ver aquí dentro, ¿por qué mantener este lugar tan oscuro?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4135
translate spanish d19e_old_man_2b316d6b:

    # OMan "Tell me, stranger, have the desert winds brought me another adventurer looking for riches?"
    OMan "Dime, forastero, ¿me han traído los vientos del desierto a otro aventurero en busca de riquezas?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4136
translate spanish d19e_old_man_f8d2216d:

    # OMan "Or do you seek something different?"
    OMan "¿O buscas algo diferente?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4139
translate spanish d19e_old_man_45bf5514:

    # "The darkness inside is dotted by tallow candles that create little pockets of light, dangerously close to stacks of parchments that fill every available shelf."
    "La oscuridad interior está salpicada por velas de sebo que crean pequeños bolsillos de luz, peligrosamente cerca de montones de pergaminos que llenan cada estante disponible."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4142
translate spanish d19e_old_man_5b63a22c:

    # OMan "You must forgive me, but the darkness is soothing to me. Sunlight hurts my eyes."
    OMan "Debes perdonarme, pero la oscuridad me resulta reconfortante. La luz del sol lastima mis ojos."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4143
translate spanish d19e_old_man_b178543b:

    # Z "How could you know what I was-"
    Z "¿Cómo sabías lo que yo estaba—"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4144
translate spanish d19e_old_man_5fcca1fd:

    # OMan "Oh, that... I am, people tell me, a very wise man."
    OMan "Oh, eso... Me dicen que soy un hombre muy sabio."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4145
translate spanish d19e_old_man_f334e43c:

    # "You hear him chuckle quietly..."
    "Lo escuchas reírse en voz baja..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4147
translate spanish d19e_old_man_0b79f90f:

    # OMan "And they keep asking me about it."
    OMan "Y nunca dejan de preguntarme sobre ello."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4148
translate spanish d19e_old_man_b52f11ce:

    # Z "That's fair."
    Z "Es justo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4151
translate spanish d19e_old_man_e8f1fd49:

    # Z "Peace on this house, uncle."
    Z "Paz en esta casa, tío."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4154
translate spanish d19e_old_man_ec6e77b1:

    # OMan "Hm. The rules of hospitality."
    OMan "Hm. Las reglas de la hospitalidad."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4155
translate spanish d19e_old_man_954525ad:

    # OMan "I am not seeing that often these days."
    OMan "No suelo ver eso a menudo estos días."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4158
translate spanish d19e_old_man_87497e50:

    # "As the formal greetings are exchanged, you see the old man visibly relax, as he recognises that you have bound yourself by the rules of hospitality."
    "Al intercambiar los saludos formales, ves al anciano relajarse visiblemente, al reconocer que te has atado a las reglas de la hospitalidad."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4161
translate spanish d19e_old_man_dfbf62b5:

    # OMan "Peace be with you, as a guest to this house."
    OMan "La paz sea contigo, como huésped de esta casa."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4162
translate spanish d19e_old_man_6757ec8f:

    # OMan "You seek knowledge. Speak."
    OMan "Buscas conocimiento. Habla."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4170
translate spanish d19e_old_man_d2c9a8df:

    # "While the storm is not close enough to become life threatening, the darkened sky and whirling sands make it hard to see what's in front of you."
    "Aunque la tormenta no está lo bastante cerca como para ser mortal, el cielo oscurecido y las arenas girando dificultan ver lo que tienes delante."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4171
translate spanish d19e_old_man_f6cdf10d:

    # "You eventually spot the shack you are looking for partially hidden by the dunes, and rush to the front door."
    "Finalmente distingues la choza que buscas, parcialmente oculta por las dunas, y corres hacia la puerta principal."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4174
translate spanish d19e_old_man_c154f2d8:

    # Z "Is anyone here? Open please, I require shelter!"
    Z "¿Hay alguien aquí? ¡Abran, por favor, necesito refugio!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4176
translate spanish d19e_old_man_09bdb907:

    # Zt "Nothing..."
    Zt "Nada..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4179
translate spanish d19e_old_man_ac6a844c:

    # "You try to open the door, and it makes a grinding sound, barely audible over the whistle of the wind..."
    "Intentas abrir la puerta, y esta emite un chirrido, apenas audible sobre el silbido del viento..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4182
translate spanish d19e_old_man_bbe11cd4:

    # C2 "Winds of the old world, blind your eyes from me, I am but dust and breath and devotion, let the storm pass me by."
    C2 "Vientos del viejo mundo, cegad vuestros ojos ante mí, no soy más que polvo, aliento y devoción, dejad que la tormenta me pase de largo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4183
translate spanish d19e_old_man_192aee9f:

    # Zt "It's dark in here, but... is that the hermit praying?"
    Zt "Está oscuro aquí dentro, pero... ¿es ese el ermitaño rezando?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4186
translate spanish d19e_old_man_4c922576:

    # Z "There he is."
    Z "Ahí está."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4189
translate spanish d19e_old_man_e8f1fd49_1:

    # Z "Peace on this house, uncle."
    Z "Paz en esta casa, tío."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4190
translate spanish d19e_old_man_2b54684a:

    # "You call out in the dark, trying not to cause undue alarm."
    "Llamas en la oscuridad, intentando no causar alarma innecesaria."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4193
translate spanish d19e_old_man_5234ea71:

    # "You see a range of parchments gently lit by a scattering of candles."
    "Ves una serie de pergaminos suavemente iluminados por un puñado de velas."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4196
translate spanish d19e_old_man_1e472bcf:

    # OMan "A visitor?"
    OMan "¿Un visitante?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4199
translate spanish d19e_old_man_7cb0c156:

    # Z "My name is [persistent.player_name], uncle... I sought shelter from the storm."
    Z "Mi nombre es [persistent.player_name], tío... Busco refugio de la tormenta."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4202
translate spanish d19e_old_man_c5518b98:

    # OMan "You have found it. Be welcome to my house, guest. Peace be with you."
    OMan "Lo has encontrado. Sé bienvenido a mi casa, huésped. La paz sea contigo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4205
translate spanish d19e_old_man_87497e50_1:

    # "As the formal greetings are exchanged, you see the old man visibly relax, as he recognises that you have bound yourself by the rules of hospitality."
    "Mientras se intercambian los saludos formales, ves al anciano relajarse visiblemente, al reconocer que te has atado a las reglas de la hospitalidad."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4208
translate spanish d19e_old_man_0d410a77:

    # "You look around and see nothing but writing implements, books and scrolls."
    "Miras a tu alrededor y no ves más que útiles de escritura, libros y pergaminos."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4209
translate spanish d19e_old_man_b9414e18:

    # OMan "We hide in the dark, from the fury of the desert, but we endure."
    OMan "Nos ocultamos en la oscuridad, de la furia del desierto, pero resistimos."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4212
translate spanish d19e_old_man_465de4ce:

    # OMan "Tell me, is shelter all you come for?"
    OMan "Dime, ¿solo vienes por refugio?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4215
translate spanish d19e_old_man_d421f689:

    # Z "It is not. I was advised to seek your counsel. A place I seek is rumoured to be not far from here."
    Z "No es así. Me aconsejaron buscar tu consejo. El lugar que busco se rumorea que no está lejos de aquí."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4217
translate spanish d19e_old_man_d85490be:

    # Z "I have heard that in this area there used to be an ancient temple that goes back many centuries or more. I was told it is a holy place."
    Z "He oído que en esta zona solía haber un templo antiguo, de hace muchos siglos o más. Me dijeron que es un lugar sagrado."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4218
translate spanish d19e_old_man_a8da2c01:

    # Z "A place of such great importance that one of the founding Elders made it his personal residence, maybe to commune with the gods in isolation."
    Z "Un lugar de tal importancia que uno de los Ancianos fundadores lo convirtió en su residencia personal, quizá para comunicarse con los dioses en aislamiento."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4221
translate spanish d19e_old_man_cae41d29:

    # OMan "I cannot say if what you have heard holds any truth. Stories have a way of shifting like sand with each passing year."
    OMan "No puedo decir si lo que has oído tiene algo de verdad. Las historias tienden a cambiar como la arena con cada año que pasa."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4222
translate spanish d19e_old_man_4df6997d:

    # OMan "Though you should know that when Zeta was first founded, the land was inhabited more than it is now."
    OMan "Aunque deberías saber que cuando Zeta fue fundada por primera vez, la tierra estaba más habitada que ahora."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4225
translate spanish d19e_old_man_288368f3:

    # OMan "That was until my own grandfather's infancy when one of the mightiest Holy Storms ever to strike these lands descended from the heavens."
    OMan "Eso fue hasta la infancia de mi propio abuelo, cuando una de las Tormentas Sagradas más poderosas que jamás azotaron estas tierras descendió de los cielos."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4226
translate spanish d19e_old_man_c954d606:

    # OMan "For weeks the winds howled without mercy, and when they finally stilled, little remained of the settlements."
    OMan "Durante semanas los vientos aullaron sin piedad, y cuando finalmente se calmaron, poco quedaba de los asentamientos."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4227
translate spanish d19e_old_man_7b1a5483:

    # Z "So that's why my search has been so difficult. I have a few old maps, but the landmarks they show are lost to me."
    Z "Así que por eso mi búsqueda ha sido tan difícil. Tengo algunos mapas antiguos, pero los puntos de referencia que muestran se me han perdido."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4228
translate spanish d19e_old_man_55adf695:

    # OMan "But not to me. A few do still remain."
    OMan "Pero no para mí. Algunos aún permanecen."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4231
translate spanish d19e_old_man_abf79d28:

    # OMan "Did you bring these parchments? Perhaps I can help decipher the landmarks you speak of."
    OMan "¿Has traído esos pergaminos? Quizás pueda ayudarte a descifrar los lugares de los que hablas."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4234
translate spanish d19e_old_man_6c764800:

    # "You show the old man the notes you took from the Queen's archives."
    "Le muestras al anciano las notas que tomaste de los archivos de la Reina."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4235
translate spanish d19e_old_man_a29a1fe6:

    # "His finger traces a sketch of a path flanked by stone pillars, all leading to a towering arch."
    "Su dedo recorre un dibujo de un camino flanqueado por pilares de piedra, todos conduciendo a un arco imponente."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4236
translate spanish d19e_old_man_83fb23f8:

    # OMan "These stones... These are what you need to find."
    OMan "Esas piedras... Son lo que necesitas encontrar."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4239
translate spanish d19e_old_man_0541e6df:

    # OMan "Not far from here indeed, though they do not rise from the earth as they once did. Very easy to miss."
    OMan "En efecto, no muy lejos de aquí, aunque ya no se alzan de la tierra como antes. Son muy fáciles de pasar por alto."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4240
translate spanish d19e_old_man_203d0398:

    # OMan "Though what your map shows is only a fraction of this temple. A sliver. The greater part lies hidden below, not claimed by storm or sand, but buried by design."
    OMan "Aunque lo que muestra tu mapa es solo una fracción de este templo. Una parte mínima. La mayor parte yace oculta debajo, no reclamada por la tormenta ni por la arena, sino enterrada a propósito."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4243
translate spanish d19e_old_man_96624bf4:

    # "From the description he gives you, you realise he's talking about the place you seek. The hidden refuge of the Elder."
    "Por la descripción que te da, comprendes que habla del lugar que buscas. El refugio oculto del Anciano."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4249
translate spanish d19e_old_man_a7ccb44a:

    # Z "Do you know if this bracelet has any connection to the Elder?"
    Z "¿Sabes si este brazalete tiene alguna conexión con el Anciano?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4250
translate spanish d19e_old_man_d5e4a520:

    # "You hold out the bracelet you found on top of the ruinous columns. A clear look of recognition crosses the old man's face."
    "Extiendes el brazalete que encontraste sobre las columnas en ruinas. Una clara expresión de reconocimiento cruza el rostro del anciano."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4251
translate spanish d19e_old_man_705811a2:

    # OMan "Gods above!"
    OMan "¡Dioses del cielo!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4254
translate spanish d19e_old_man_5b4e4eaf:

    # OMan "That is my sister's bracelet! How do you come by it?"
    OMan "¡Ese es el brazalete de mi hermana! ¿Cómo lo conseguiste?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4257
translate spanish d19e_old_man_68d2f3f7:

    # Z "I found it on top of an old ruin, fairly well hidden. There was also a scroll."
    Z "Lo encontré sobre una vieja ruina, bastante bien escondido. También había un pergamino."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4260
translate spanish d19e_old_man_7c1dec3d:

    # "As you show the old man the scroll that was in the same box as the bracelet, he looks at it for a few moments..."
    "Cuando le muestras al anciano el pergamino que estaba en la misma caja que el brazalete, lo observa durante unos momentos..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4263
translate spanish d19e_old_man_a8928c65:

    # OMan "Well, I don't know what to make of this. I know it has nothing to do with my sister."
    OMan "Bueno, no sé qué pensar de esto. Sé que no tiene nada que ver con mi hermana."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4266
translate spanish d19e_old_man_d8ba9280:

    # "You both dismiss the scroll as unimportant, albeit for different reasons."
    "Ambos desestiman el pergamino como algo sin importancia, aunque por diferentes motivos."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4269
translate spanish d19e_old_man_fc0b2760:

    # OMan "My sister was kidnapped many decades ago, when we were both young. She was never found again. Have you perhaps found any trace of a woman, or rather, a child around the bracelet?"
    OMan "Mi hermana fue secuestrada hace muchas décadas, cuando ambos éramos jóvenes. Nunca se la volvió a encontrar. ¿Has hallado quizá algún rastro de una mujer, o más bien de una niña, cerca del brazalete?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4272
translate spanish d19e_old_man_feff6078:

    # Z "I'm afraid this is all there was. It was stashed away in a hiding place. I do not know by what twists of fate she was separated from it and how it found its way there, nor do I know who might have hidden it."
    Z "Me temo que esto es todo lo que había. Estaba guardado en un escondite. No sé por qué giros del destino se separó de él ni cómo acabó allí, ni tampoco quién pudo haberlo ocultado."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4275
translate spanish d19e_old_man_ca2e3c94:

    # OMan "If I have correctly interpreted what you're looking for, you now have the means to reach the place."
    OMan "Si he interpretado bien lo que buscas, ahora tienes los medios para llegar al lugar."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4278
translate spanish d19e_old_man_77cd3cf8:

    # OMan "I may have knowledge of a secret alcove inside the ruins where certain treasures might still be buried."
    OMan "Puede que tenga conocimiento de un escondrijo secreto dentro de las ruinas donde aún podrían yacer ciertos tesoros."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4279
translate spanish d19e_old_man_480e47ac:

    # OMan "Would you be willing to trade the bracelet for its location?"
    OMan "¿Estarías dispuesto a intercambiar el brazalete por su ubicación?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4282
translate spanish d19e_old_man_0624108a:

    # Z "The bracelet is of no value to me, I accept."
    Z "El brazalete no tiene valor para mí, acepto."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4285
translate spanish d19e_old_man_d556b68b:

    # "You hand the bracelet over..."
    "Entregas el brazalete..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4288
translate spanish d19e_old_man_b37ba5ef:

    # OMan "Oh, how many years it has been since..."
    OMan "Oh... cuántos años han pasado desde entonces..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4292
translate spanish d19e_old_man_47bc9c3d:

    # "The man leans in closer and speaks in barely more than a whisper."
    "El hombre se inclina más cerca y habla apenas por encima de un susurro."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4295
translate spanish d19e_old_man_6c044c13:

    # OMan "If you manage to locate the Elder's library, take the path that leads further underground..."
    OMan "Si logras localizar la biblioteca del Anciano, toma el sendero que conduce más abajo, hacia el subsuelo..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4296
translate spanish d19e_old_man_a4a0b95a:

    # OMan "Head through the lower level until the air grows colder and the way narrows. You will find a hollow in the stone at the end, no larger than a prison cell."
    OMan "Sigue por el nivel inferior hasta que el aire se vuelva más frío y el camino se estreche. Encontrarás un hueco en la roca al final, no más grande que una celda de prisión."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4297
translate spanish d19e_old_man_f2355356:

    # OMan "The treasure is said to be there, hidden underneath a loose stone on the floor."
    OMan "Se dice que el tesoro está allí, oculto bajo una piedra suelta en el suelo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4300
translate spanish d19e_old_man_87a89121:

    # "With this new information and the bracelet handed over, you bid farewell to the old man and return to the women waiting at your camp."
    "Con esta nueva información y tras entregar el brazalete, te despides del anciano y regresas con las mujeres que esperan en tu campamento."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4304
translate spanish d19e_old_man_d217fbc7:

    # Z "Is there anything else I need to know?"
    Z "¿Hay algo más que deba saber?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4307
translate spanish d19e_old_man_15bd8afd:

    # OMan "Nothing that I can tell you. Find the stones, and you find the location of the Elder's refuge."
    OMan "Nada que yo pueda decirte. Encuentra las piedras, y encontrarás la ubicación del refugio del Anciano."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4312
translate spanish d19e_old_man_5adcf94e:

    # "Finally, you leave him a few loaves of bread and a candle you happen to have in your pack, before taking your leave."
    "Finalmente, le dejas unos panes y una vela que llevabas en tu mochila, antes de despedirte."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4314
translate spanish d19e_old_man_f212db32:

    # "You believe that you now have a clearer idea as to where to look for the Elder's residence."
    "Crees que ahora tienes una idea más clara de dónde buscar la residencia del Anciano."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4323
translate spanish d19f_09258ef3:

    # "Night has come, and the three of you are refreshing yourselves, relaxing, and preparing for whatever awaits you tomorrow."
    "Ha caído la noche, y los tres os refrescáis, os relajáis y os preparáis para lo que os espere mañana."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4329
translate spanish d19f_342c2267:

    # Z "{i}*yawn*{/i}"
    Z "{i}*bostezo*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4330
translate spanish d19f_1d2c2e77:

    # Zt "We've had a day... But if we make it to the temple tomorrow, we could be home by the day after."
    Zt "Vaya día... Pero si llegamos al templo mañana, podríamos estar en casa pasado mañana."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4333
translate spanish d19f_dd2471ca:

    # "You stare into the night..."
    "Contemplas la noche..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4334
translate spanish d19f_f2de6a21:

    # Zt "I wonder what the others are doing at this moment. Must be different for them too, now that both [S] and me are out here."
    Zt "Me pregunto qué estarán haciendo los demás ahora mismo. Debe de ser diferente para ellos también, ahora que tanto [S] como yo estamos aquí fuera."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4337
translate spanish d19f_f6a9776b:

    # Z "I guess our Queen is still getting ready for bed?"
    Z "Imagino que nuestra Reina todavía se está preparando para dormir, ¿no?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4340
translate spanish d19f_065ed3da:

    # S "I guess she doesn't have a gaggle of servants assisting her now."
    S "Supongo que ahora no tiene un séquito de sirvientes que la asistan."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4343
translate spanish d19f_497e6f27:

    # Q "I heard that...!"
    Q "¡He oído eso...!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4347
translate spanish d19f_43ca57be:

    # S "Hm..."
    S "Hm..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4354
translate spanish d19f_5a463aed:

    # "You lean back, closing your eyes..."
    "Te recuestas, cerrando los ojos..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4356
translate spanish d19f_43ca57be_1:

    # S "Hm..."
    S "Hm..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4357
translate spanish d19f_116138f8:

    # S "Do you think it is safe for the both of us to be away from home and leave it unprotected?"
    S "¿Crees que es seguro que nos vayamos y lo dejemos desprotegido?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4360
translate spanish d19f_9e06d3b5:

    # Z "I was thinking about it just a few minutes ago. I am fairly confident our house is secure. If I didn't think so, I wouldn't have left you alone when you yourself were younger."
    Z "Estaba pensando en eso hace apenas unos minutos. Estoy bastante seguro de que nuestra casa está protegida. Si no lo creyera, no te habría dejado sola cuando tú misma eras más joven."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4361
translate spanish d19f_efe97f48:

    # Z "You know I have friends in the city. Back then, I had some of them keep a discreet eye on the house in my absence."
    Z "Sabes que tengo amigos en la ciudad. En aquel entonces, hacía que algunos de ellos vigilaran la casa discretamente en mi ausencia."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4364
translate spanish d19f_488273e4:

    # S "Is that why uncle Igor used to come by so often?"
    S "¿Es por eso que el tío Igor venía tan a menudo?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4367
translate spanish d19f_5f51b370:

    # Z "I guess discretion isn't really his best attribute, but yes."
    Z "Supongo que la discreción no es precisamente su mejor atributo, pero sí."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4368
translate spanish d19f_11dfde47:

    # Z "When you started being able to defend the house, it became less necessary. I guess I will have to knock on a few doors again, if we are both going to be absent for long."
    Z "Cuando empezaste a poder defender la casa, dejó de ser tan necesario. Supongo que tendré que llamar a unas cuantas puertas de nuevo si vamos a estar ausentes mucho tiempo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4371
translate spanish d19f_9f6a1623:

    # Z "It's funny... I haven't heard you call him uncle in a long time."
    Z "Es curioso... hacía mucho que no te oía llamarlo tío."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4374
translate spanish d19f_b3c6f657:

    # S "You're right. I guess you got me thinking about the past. That's how I used to address him back then."
    S "Tienes razón. Supongo que me hiciste pensar en el pasado. Así era como lo llamaba entonces."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4377
translate spanish d19f_b121f330:

    # Z "Anyway, I will rest for a bit. Keep watch, will you?"
    Z "En fin, voy a descansar un rato. Haz guardia, ¿quieres?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4378
translate spanish d19f_b7bbae10:

    # Z "Wake me up in a bit. And tell Neith her massage will have to wait for another day."
    Z "Despiértame dentro de un rato. Y dile a Neith que su masaje tendrá que esperar a otro día."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4381
translate spanish d19f_7de6ebcc:

    # S "Will do, [persistent.dad]."
    S "Así lo haré, [persistent.dad]."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4387
translate spanish d19f_b2c0fc28:

    # "You fall asleep..."
    "Te quedas dormido..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4389
translate spanish d19f_5c0dbb47:

    # "A little time passes..."
    "Pasa un poco de tiempo..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4394
translate spanish d19f_5a972ba2:

    # Z "{i}*snoozing*{/i}"
    Z "{i}*ronquidos*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4398
translate spanish d19f_570568f8:

    # New "Psst...!"
    New "¡Psst...!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4401
translate spanish d19f_e9425219:

    # Sw "...?"
    Sw "¿...?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4404
translate spanish d19f_7aa32e32:

    # New "Is he already out?"
    New "¿Ya está dormido?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4405
translate spanish d19f_efa0aaad:

    # Sw "It seems like it."
    Sw "Parece que sí."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4406
translate spanish d19f_a7bd0aeb:

    # New "It must have been a long day for him as well, then..."
    New "Entonces también debió de ser un día largo para él..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4409
translate spanish d19f_ddd04c56:

    # New "I don't know about you, [S], but I'm not tired at all."
    New "No sé tú, [S], pero yo no tengo nada de sueño."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4411
translate spanish d19f_dcd1af2b:

    # New "Today was amazing. That trip to the ruins was so exciting, you really showed up!"
    New "Hoy fue increíble. Esa excursión a las ruinas fue tan emocionante, ¡te luciste de verdad!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4413
translate spanish d19f_00d5941a:

    # New "Today was very exciting. To just be in a camp out here, with no one around!"
    New "Hoy fue muy emocionante. Estar en un campamento aquí, ¡con nadie alrededor!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4416
translate spanish d19f_ef215385:

    # New "It was so cool to drive in that machine too! I didn't know they could go that fast!"
    New "¡También fue genial conducir esa máquina! ¡No sabía que podían ir tan rápido!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4419
translate spanish d19f_b969d9e4:

    # Sw "Speed is very liberating, but it's a controlled speed. The dunes can be treacherous. Oh, you haven't even seen my new two-wheeler!"
    Sw "La velocidad es muy liberadora, pero es una velocidad controlada. Las dunas pueden ser traicioneras. ¡Ah, y ni siquiera has visto mi nueva moto de dos ruedas!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4422
translate spanish d19f_86ac53ee:

    # New "Maybe another time? I could always find reasons to visit your home again."
    New "¿Quizá en otra ocasión? Siempre puedo encontrar razones para volver a visitar tu casa."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4425
translate spanish d19f_d0f8a89e:

    # New "...but... I will be honest. Your [persistent.mom] is scary. I am the Queen, I rule everywhere the shadow of Zeta reaches, but she wasn't the least bit concerned."
    New "...pero... seré sincera. Tu [persistent.mom] da miedo. Yo soy la Reina, gobierno en todo donde llega la sombra de Zeta, ¡y a ella no le importó lo más mínimo!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4426
translate spanish d19f_3d72597f:

    # New "She looked ready to punch me, actually."
    New "Parecía lista para darme un puñetazo, la verdad."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4429
translate spanish d19f_9aa51177:

    # Sw "You've met her? I didn't know! But yes, she can be very intimidating. You have come to know my [persistent.dad]...."
    Sw "¿La has conocido? ¡No lo sabía! Pero sí, puede ser muy intimidante. Has llegado a conocer a mi [persistent.dad]..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4430
translate spanish d19f_30cb880c:

    # Sw "He can be brutal in battle, and... well, you've seen him. But it's my [persistent.mom] you need to be wary about. She will make you feel bad about yourself and sorry for having disappointed her, all at the same time."
    Sw "Puede ser brutal en la batalla y... bueno, ya lo has visto. Pero de quien debes tener cuidado es de mi [persistent.mom]. Ella conseguirá que te sientas mal contigo misma y arrepentida de haberla decepcionado, todo al mismo tiempo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4433
translate spanish d19f_864f78d5:

    # "The young queen remains pensive for a moment, before speaking again, in hushed tones."
    "La joven reina permanece pensativa un momento, antes de volver a hablar en voz baja."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4434
translate spanish d19f_1a06f424:

    # New "... I think I have to tell you something."
    New "... Creo que tengo que decirte algo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4437
translate spanish d19f_95841feb:

    # Sw "Is it about [persistent.dad]?"
    Sw "¿Es sobre [persistent.dad]?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4440
translate spanish d19f_a9d2efdf:

    # New "It's... a long story, but..."
    New "Es... una larga historia, pero..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4443
translate spanish d19f_f7167c7f:

    # New "...he might have done something that would get him crucified, if the Elders found out..."
    New "... puede que haya hecho algo que lo crucificaría, si los Ancianos llegaran a enterarse..."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4444
translate spanish d19f_10e5c570:

    # Sw "Are you saying you two did it?"
    Sw "¿Estás diciendo que los dos lo hicisteis?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4445
translate spanish d19f_41887886:

    # New "...How... Why would you guess that?"
    New "... ¿Cómo...? ¿Por qué supondrías eso?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4446
translate spanish d19f_96b21f0b:

    # Sw "Oh please! I saw how you were looking at him, when we were at the Thermae."
    Sw "¡Oh, por favor! Vi cómo lo mirabas cuando estábamos en las Termas."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4449
translate spanish d19f_36664b9b:

    # New "I think you're imagining something. Why would I be looking..."
    New "Creo que te lo estás imaginando. ¿Por qué habría de mirarlo yo así...?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4452
translate spanish d19f_eb791b95:

    # Sw "Hm... right. You're a bad liar, Neith."
    Sw "Hm... claro. Eres una pésima mentirosa, Neith."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4453
translate spanish d19f_5b91d6b0:

    # Sw "Be honest, what happened?"
    Sw "Sé honesta, ¿qué pasó?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4456
translate spanish d19f_a9952675:

    # New "Okay, yes, we did it. I wasn't really planning on it, I swear."
    New "Vale, sí, lo hicimos. No lo tenía planeado, lo juro."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4459
translate spanish d19f_3cb5becc:

    # Sw "You don't need to justify yourself. I didn't plan my first time either."
    Sw "No necesitas justificarte. Yo tampoco planeé mi primera vez."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4462
translate spanish d19f_4d49942e:

    # Sw "It was the night before I entered the Zone, and it was all cozy and romantic. It was an emotional time, and it just felt right."
    Sw "Fue la noche antes de entrar en la Zona, todo fue acogedor y romántico. Era un momento muy emocional, y simplemente se sintió correcto."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4465
translate spanish d19f_d2a30119:

    # New "Yeah... it wasn't as romantic, at all, at least at first."
    New "Sí... no fue nada romántico, al menos al principio."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4468
translate spanish d19f_c8eb1a5a:

    # New "Do you want me to just... tell you?"
    New "¿Quieres que simplemente... te lo cuente?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4471
translate spanish d19f_8d4bc808:

    # Sw "Of course!"
    Sw "¡Por supuesto!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4474
translate spanish d19f_4d042cb9:

    # New "So... it all started with me being like super mad at him."
    New "Pues... todo empezó con que yo estaba súper enfadada con él."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4476
translate spanish d19f_a55cd10a:

    # New "I don't know what it was about him, but ever since I first summoned him in court, he was always very disrespectful, stubborn!"
    New "No sé qué tenía él, pero desde la primera vez que lo llamé a la corte, siempre fue muy irrespetuoso, ¡terco!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4479
translate spanish d19f_95240687:

    # Sw "In what way?"
    Sw "¿En qué sentido?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4482
translate spanish d19f_729ca3b1:

    # New "He was too proud to kneel, for example, and didn't even care that I was the Queen. And when I scolded him, he just got up and confronted me, got right in my face!!"
    New "Demasiado orgulloso para arrodillarse, por ejemplo, y ni siquiera le importaba que yo fuera la Reina. ¡Y cuando lo reprendía, se levantaba y me enfrentaba, poniéndose cara a cara conmigo!"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4485
translate spanish d19f_e2a1fb45:

    # Sw "In open court?!"
    Sw "¿¡En plena corte!?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4488
translate spanish d19f_0ab9fc2a:

    # New "Yes! Normally, I would have banished someone for an act like that, or worse, but... I remember thinking I needed him, his services."
    New "¡Sí! Normalmente, habría desterrado a alguien por un acto así, o algo peor, pero... recuerdo haber pensado que lo necesitaba, necesitaba sus servicios."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4491
translate spanish d19f_31a6db35:

    # New "I think it was his demeanor... Something about the way he approached me everytime was... destabilising, confronting, but also... comforting?"
    New "Creo que era su forma de ser... Algo en la manera en que se me acercaba cada vez era... desestabilizador, desafiante, pero también... ¿consolador?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4492
translate spanish d19f_dc46e1ae:

    # New "It made me feel small, like my title didn't matter. Do you know what I mean?"
    New "Me hacía sentir pequeña, como si mi título no importara. ¿Sabes a lo que me refiero?"

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4496
translate spanish d19f_36e9053c:

    # New "I don't know why, but at first, he was just like any other servant."
    New "No sé por qué, pero al principio era como cualquier otro sirviente."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4497
translate spanish d19f_7141c8bb:

    # New "I think it was the way he conducted himself. Serious, experienced, but also loyal and gentle."
    New "Creo que era su forma de comportarse. Serio, experimentado, pero también leal y tierno."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4500
translate spanish d19f_6fe0a337:

    # Sw "That sounds like him. When he wants to."
    Sw "Eso suena a él. Cuando quiere."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4503
translate spanish d19f_a93a9817:

    # New "I think that was it. Maybe his experience... but I quickly came to trust him."
    New "Creo que fue eso. Quizá su experiencia... pero pronto llegué a confiar en él."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4506
translate spanish d19f_2fc9cd40:

    # New "It wasn't only that, though... He also did things he wasn't allowed to do, all the time."
    New "Aunque no fue solo eso... También hacía cosas que no tenía permitido hacer, todo el tiempo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4507
translate spanish d19f_2f1a0879:

    # New "It... felt more personal than whenever I talked to my other servants, you know. He was always straddling the line, or crossing it altogether."
    New "Se... sentía más personal que cuando hablaba con mis otros sirvientes, ¿sabes? Siempre estaba bordeando el límite, o cruzándolo del todo."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4511
translate spanish d19f_dbbe5adb:

    # Sw "I can imagine. Now that day in the thermae makes much more sense."
    Sw "Me lo imagino. Ahora ese día en las termas tiene mucho más sentido."

# game/scripts/day19.rpy:4514
